function xNv takes location xbv,real xBv,real xcv returns location
return Location(GetLocationX(xbv)+xBv*Cos(xcv*bj_DEGTORAD),GetLocationY(xbv)+xBv*Sin(xcv*bj_DEGTORAD))
endfunction
function xCv takes nothing returns boolean
local real dx=GetDestructableX(GetFilterDestructable())-xEv
local real dy=GetDestructableY(GetFilterDestructable())-xXv
return(dx*dx+dy*dy<=bj_enumDestructableRadius)
endfunction
function xdv takes rect r,boolexpr xDv returns group
set xOv=CreateGroup()
call GroupEnumUnitsInRect(xOv,r,xDv)
call DestroyBoolExpr(xDv)
return xOv
endfunction
function xfv takes rect r returns group
set xOv=CreateGroup()
call GroupEnumUnitsInRect(xOv,r,xIv)
return xOv
endfunction
function xFv takes real xgv,location xGv,boolexpr xDv returns group
set xOv=CreateGroup()
call GroupEnumUnitsInRangeOfLoc(xOv,xGv,xgv,xDv)
return xOv
endfunction
function xhv takes itemtype xHv,integer xjv returns nothing
local group g
set bj_stockPickedItemType=xHv
set bj_stockPickedItemLevel=xjv
set g=CreateGroup()
call GroupEnumUnitsOfType(g,"marketplace",xIv)
call ForGroup(g,function UpdateEachStockBuildingEnum)
call DestroyGroup(g)
set g=null
endfunction
function xJv takes nothing returns nothing
local integer pickedItemId
local itemtype xkv
local integer xKv=0
local integer xlv=0
local integer xjv
set xjv=1
loop
if(bj_stockAllowedPermanent[xjv])then
set xlv=xlv+1
if(GetRandomInt(1,xlv)==1)then
set xkv=ITEM_TYPE_PERMANENT
set xKv=xjv
endif
endif
if(bj_stockAllowedCharged[xjv])then
set xlv=xlv+1
if(GetRandomInt(1,xlv)==1)then
set xkv=ITEM_TYPE_CHARGED
set xKv=xjv
endif
endif
if(bj_stockAllowedArtifact[xjv])then
set xlv=xlv+1
if(GetRandomInt(1,xlv)==1)then
set xkv=ITEM_TYPE_ARTIFACT
set xKv=xjv
endif
endif
set xjv=xjv+1
exitwhen xjv>$A
endloop
if(xlv==0)then
set xkv=null
return
endif
call xhv(xkv,xKv)
set xkv=null
endfunction
function xLv takes nothing returns nothing
call xJv()
call TimerStart(bj_stockUpdateTimer,bj_STOCK_RESTOCK_INTERVAL,true,function xJv)
endfunction
function xMv takes nothing returns boolean
return true
endfunction
function xQv takes nothing returns integer
local integer xsv=kj
if(xsv!=0)then
set kj=lj[xsv]
else
set Kj=Kj+1
set xsv=Kj
endif
if(xsv>8190)then
return 0
endif
set lj[xsv]=-1
return xsv
endfunction

function x5v takes nothing returns integer
local integer xsv=Mm
if(xsv!=0)then
set Mm=Pm[xsv]
else
set pm=pm+1
set xsv=pm
endif
if(xsv>8190)then
return 0
endif
set sm[xsv]=Qm
set Sm[xsv]=Qm
set Ep[xsv]=0
set Iq[xsv]=null
set As[xsv]=null
set Bt[xsv]=null
set Du[xsv]=null
set Fw[xsv]=null
set gy[xsv]=null
set gz[xsv]=null
set J0[xsv]=null
set p2[xsv]=null
set Q4[xsv]=0
set s6[xsv]=.0
set s8[xsv]=false
set T8[xsv]=false
set Pm[xsv]=-1
return xsv
endfunction

endfunction

function ihv takes nothing returns boolean
return IsUnitEnemy(GetFilterUnit(),E)and GetUnitState(GetFilterUnit(),UNIT_STATE_LIFE)>0
endfunction
function iHv takes unit ijv,real x,real y,real xgv,real iJv,attacktype ikv,damagetype iKv returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(ijv)))
local real iLv=iJv
local group g=CreateGroup()
local unit u
set E=GetOwningPlayer(ijv)
call GroupEnumUnitsInRange(g,x,y,xgv,V)
set E=null
loop
set u=FirstOfGroup(g)
exitwhen u==null
call UnitDamageTarget(ijv,u,iLv,true,false,ikv,iKv,WEAPON_TYPE_WHOKNOWS)
call GroupRemoveUnit(g,u)
endloop
call DestroyGroup(g)
set g=null
endfunction
function iMv takes unit ijv,real iJv,real xgv,real x,real y returns nothing
call iHv(ijv,x,y,xgv,iJv,ATTACK_TYPE_NORMAL,DAMAGE_TYPE_MAGIC)
endfunction

function iPv takes nothing returns nothing
local real iqv=.6
local integer i=0
call DestroyTimerDialog(O[0])
set O[0]=null
call DestroyTimer(GetExpiredTimer())
set i=0
loop
set i=i+1
set gi[i]=gi[i]-iqv
exitwhen i>=$C
endloop
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFFD36EEC효과 종료!")
set X[0]=false
endfunction
function iQv takes player p returns boolean
local timer t
local real iqv=.6
local integer i=0
if X[0]then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(p,0,0,"|CFFD36EEC이미 지속 중인 효과가 있으므로 사용이 취소 되었습니다.")
return false
else
set i=0
loop
set i=i+1
set gi[i]=gi[i]+iqv
exitwhen i>=$C
endloop
if p!=GetLocalPlayer()then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,GetPlayerName(p)+" |CFFD36EEC님이 '"+GetObjectName((('%��'+'�n�')))+"|CFFD36EEC' 아이템을 사용하셨습니다.")
endif
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFFD36EEC모든 플레이어의 확률이 |CFFFF0000"+I2S(S2I(R2S(iqv*'d')))+"%|CFFD36EEC 만큼 증가합니다.")
set X[0]=true
set t=CreateTimer()
call TimerStart(t,1800.,false,function iPv)
set O[0]=CreateTimerDialog(t)
call TimerDialogSetTitle(O[0],GetObjectName((('x:J'+'��'))))
call TimerDialogDisplay(O[0],true)
set t=null
return true
endif
endfunction
function isv takes nothing returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local item i
if iQv(p)then
if p==GetLocalPlayer()then
call TriggerEvaluate(Xj)
endif
else
set i=CreateItem(GetItemTypeId(GetManipulatedItem()),GetUnitX(u),GetUnitY(u))
call SetItemPlayer(i,p,false)
call UnitAddItem(u,i)
set i=null
endif
endfunction
function iSv takes nothing returns boolean
return GetItemTypeId(GetManipulatedItem())==(('��5'+'{�V)'))
endfunction
function itv takes nothing returns nothing
local trigger iTv=CreateTrigger()
call TriggerRegisterAnyUnitEventBJ(iTv,EVENT_PLAYER_UNIT_USE_ITEM)
call TriggerAddCondition(iTv,Condition(function iSv))
call TriggerAddAction(iTv,function isv)
set iTv=null
endfunction

function acv takes integer ilv,integer xPv returns string
local string aBv=N[ilv]
local string iwv=StringCase(aBv,false)
if iwv=="maste" and xPv>8 then
return null
endif
if iwv=="melonaid" and xPv>9 then
return null
endif
if(iwv=="crescent" or iwv=="nisekr" or iwv=="angel_kanade" or iwv=="sensesfail" or iwv=="데토")and xPv>1 then
return null
endif
if iwv=="ani_angry" or iwv=="warcraft" or iwv=="cycling" or iwv=="blackshining" then
return null
endif
if iwv=="데토" then
set aBv="_DETO_"
elseif iwv=="루시" then
set aBv="_LUCY_"
elseif iwv=="하늘#3730" then
set aBv="_SKY_"
elseif iwv=="스팅#3993" then
set aBv="_OTL_"
elseif iwv=="xelloss#31604" then
set aBv="_XellosS_"
elseif iwv=="1skfotnvj" then
set aBv="_YeonHwa_"
elseif iwv=="포탑#31557" then
set aBv="_Turret_"
elseif iwv=="진해팡야#3290" then
set aBv="_Bini_"
elseif iwv=="제독스#3600" then
set aBv="_JeDocCe_"
elseif iwv=="령" then
set aBv="_Ryujo_"
elseif iwv=="설사#31869" then
set aBv="_SeolSa_"
endif
if C[ilv]>0 and xPv<=C[ilv]then
return"Eden\\GlobalDonate_"+aBv+"_"+I2S(xPv)+".mdl"
endif
return null
endfunction
function aCv takes player p,integer xPv returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local string adv=acv(ilv,xPv)
if C[ilv]>0 then
if aj[ilv]!=null then
call DestroyEffect(aj[ilv])
endif
set ij[ilv]=adv
if adv!=null then
set rj[ilv]=1+xPv
set aj[ilv]=AddSpecialEffectTarget(adv,hv[ilv],"overhead")
else
set rj[ilv]=1
set aj[ilv]=null
endif
endif
endfunction
function aDv takes nothing returns nothing
local string afv=GetEventPlayerChatString()
local string aFv
local integer xPv=1
if SubString(afv,0,16)=="-로얄패밀리" then
set aFv=SubString(afv,16,20)
if StringLength(aFv)!=0 then
set xPv=S2I(aFv)
if xPv==0 then
set xPv=-1
endif
else
set xPv=1
endif
call aCv(GetTriggerPlayer(),xPv)
endif
endfunction
function agv takes nothing returns nothing
local real iqv=.08
local integer i=0
local integer array aGv
local integer abv
local integer ahv=0
local real aHv=0
loop
set i=i+1
set abv=C[i]
set gi[i]=gi[i]-f
if abv>0 then
set aGv[abv]=aGv[abv]+1
if ahv<abv then
set ahv=abv
endif
endif
exitwhen i>=$C
endloop
set iqv=.12
loop
if aGv[ahv]>0 then
set aHv=aHv+ahv*iqv
if iqv>.02 then
set iqv=iqv/ 2
endif
set aGv[ahv]=aGv[ahv]-1
endif
if aGv[ahv]==0 then
set ahv=ahv-1
endif
exitwhen ahv<=0
endloop
if aHv>0 then
set i=0
loop
set i=i+1
set gi[i]=gi[i]+aHv
exitwhen i>=$C
endloop
set f=aHv
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFFD36EEC모든 플레이어의 확률이 |CffFF0000"+I2S(S2I(R2S(aHv*'d')))+"% |R 만큼 증가합니다.")
endif
endfunction
function ajv takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
if C[ilv]>0 then
set C[ilv]=0
call agv()
endif
endfunction
function aJv takes nothing returns nothing
local integer i=0
local player p
local trigger akv=CreateTrigger()
local trigger aKv=CreateTrigger()
loop
set p=Player(i)
call TriggerRegisterPlayerEvent(akv,p,EVENT_PLAYER_LEAVE)
call TriggerRegisterPlayerChatEvent(aKv,p,"-로얄패밀리",false)
set i=i+1
if GetPlayerSlotState(p)==PLAYER_SLOT_STATE_PLAYING and GetPlayerController(p)==MAP_CONTROL_USER then
set N[i]=GetPlayerName(p)
set C[i]=aNv(i)
if C[i]>0 then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFFFF6E6E"+N[i]+"|R님은 |CffFFD200 로얄 패밀리|R "+I2S(C[i])+"단계 입니다.")
endif
endif
exitwhen i>=$C
endloop
call TriggerAddAction(akv,function ajv)
call TriggerAddAction(aKv,function aDv)
call agv()
call DestroyTimer(GetExpiredTimer())
set p=null
endfunction
function alv takes nothing returns nothing
call TimerStart(CreateTimer(),1.,false,function aJv)
endfunction
function aLv takes nothing returns nothing
call AddSpecialEffectTarget("Eden\\Season Aura Whole 2nd.mdx",zh,"origin")
call TimerStart(J,S2R("10000000"),false,null)
endfunction
function JNGetEventAttackType takes nothing returns attacktype
return BlzGetEventAttackType()
endfunction
function JNGetEventDamageType takes nothing returns damagetype
return BlzGetEventDamageType()
endfunction
function JNGetEventWeaponType takes nothing returns weapontype
return BlzGetEventWeaponType()
endfunction
function JNGetEventIsAttack takes nothing returns boolean
return BlzGetEventIsAttack()
endfunction
function amv takes unit ijv,integer aMv,real apv returns nothing
if aMv==1 then
call BlzSetUnitWeaponRealField(ijv,UNIT_WEAPON_RF_ATTACK_RANGE,1,BlzGetUnitWeaponRealField(ijv,UNIT_WEAPON_RF_ATTACK_RANGE,1)-BlzGetUnitWeaponRealField(ijv,UNIT_WEAPON_RF_ATTACK_RANGE,0)+apv)
else
call BlzSetUnitWeaponRealField(ijv,UNIT_WEAPON_RF_ATTACK_RANGE,aMv,apv)
endif
endfunction
function aPv takes trigger t returns integer
local integer xsv=xQv()
set Lj[xsv]=t
set mj[Pj]=xsv
set Mj[xsv]=Pj
set Pj=xsv
call SaveInteger(K,0,GetHandleId((t)),(xsv))
return xsv
endfunction
function aqv takes integer xsv returns nothing
call RemoveSavedInteger(K,0,GetHandleId((Lj[xsv])))
set mj[Mj[xsv]]=mj[xsv]
set Mj[mj[xsv]]=Mj[xsv]
if Pj==xsv then
set Pj=Mj[xsv]
endif
set mj[xsv]=0
set Mj[xsv]=0
set Lj[xsv]=null
endfunction
function aQv takes integer xsv returns nothing
if IsTriggerEnabled(Lj[xsv])then
call ConditionalTriggerExecute(Lj[xsv])
endif
endfunction
function asv takes nothing returns nothing
local integer xsv=pj
loop
set xsv=mj[xsv]
exitwhen xsv==pj
call aQv(xsv)
endloop
endfunction
function aSv takes trigger t returns nothing
local integer xsv=(LoadInteger(K,0,GetHandleId((t))))
if xsv!=0 then
call aqv(xsv)
endif
endfunction
function atv takes trigger iTv,playerunitevent aTv returns nothing
if aTv!=EVENT_PLAYER_UNIT_DAMAGED then
call iDv(1,iTv,aTv)
else
call aPv(iTv)
endif
endfunction
function auv takes trigger iTv,playerunitevent aTv returns nothing
local integer xPv
set xPv=0
loop
call TriggerRegisterPlayerUnitEvent(iTv,Player(xPv),aTv,null)
set xPv=xPv+1
exitwhen xPv==16
endloop
endfunction
function aUv takes nothing returns nothing
local integer xsv=Qj
loop
set qj[xsv]=xsv+1
set xsv=xsv+1
exitwhen xsv>=8192
endloop
endfunction
function awv takes nothing returns integer
local integer xsv=Qj
set Qj=qj[xsv]
return xsv
endfunction
function aWv takes integer xsv returns nothing
set qj[xsv]=Qj
set Qj=xsv
endfunction
function ayv takes nothing returns boolean
call asv()
return true
endfunction
function aYv takes nothing returns boolean
local integer xsv
local unit u=GetFilterUnit()
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'Aloc')>0 or(LoadInteger(K,0,GetHandleId((u))))!=0 then
set u=null
return false
endif
call UnitAddAbility(u,'AIDX')
call UnitMakeAbilityPermanent(u,true,'AIDX')
set xsv=awv()
call SaveInteger(K,0,GetHandleId((u)),(xsv))
set sj[xsv]=CreateTrigger()
call TriggerRegisterUnitEvent(sj[xsv],u,EVENT_UNIT_DAMAGED)
call TriggerAddCondition(sj[xsv],Condition(function ayv))
set u=null
return true
endfunction
function azv takes nothing returns boolean
local integer xsv
local unit u=GetFilterUnit()
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'AIDX')==0 and(LoadInteger(K,0,GetHandleId((u))))!=0 then
set xsv=(LoadInteger(K,0,GetHandleId((u))))
call iGv(sj[xsv])
call RemoveSavedInteger(K,0,GetHandleId((u)))
call aWv(xsv)
endif
set u=null
return true
endfunction
function aZv takes nothing returns nothing
local group g=CreateGroup()
local rect r=GetWorldBounds()
local region a_v=CreateRegion()
local integer i=0
call GroupEnumUnitsInRect(g,r,Condition(function aYv))
call RegionAddRect(a_v,r)
call TriggerRegisterEnterRegion(Sj,a_v,Condition(function aYv))
loop
call TriggerRegisterPlayerUnitEvent(tj,Player(i),EVENT_PLAYER_UNIT_ISSUED_ORDER,Condition(function azv))
call SetPlayerAbilityAvailable(Player(i),'AIDX',false)
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=16
endloop
call DestroyGroup(g)
call RemoveRect(r)
set r=null
set g=null
endfunction
function a0v takes nothing returns nothing
call DestroyTimer(GetExpiredTimer())
call aZv()
endfunction
function a1v takes nothing returns nothing
call TimerStart(CreateTimer(),0,false,function a0v)
endfunction

endloop
endfunction

function nOv takes player nRv,real nIv,string nAv,real r0,real g0,real b0,real a0,real r1,real g1,real b1,real a1 returns nothing
if GetLocalPlayer()==nRv then
call CinematicFilterGenericBJ(nIv,BLEND_MODE_BLEND,nAv,r0,g0,b0,a0,r1,g1,b1,a1)
endif
endfunction
function nNv takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
if GetLocalPlayer()==LoadPlayerHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$A59BB4C6)then
call CinematicFilterGenericBJ(LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$6B54C545),BLEND_MODE_BLEND,LoadStr(F,GetHandleId(t),$4C0351EB),'d','d','d',0,'d','d','d','d')
endif
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
set t=null
endfunction
function nbv takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
call RemoveUnit(LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$B6A6EBAA))
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
set t=null
endfunction
function nBv takes unit ijv,real ncv returns nothing
local timer t=CreateTimer()
call SaveUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$B6A6EBAA,ijv)
call TimerStart(t,ncv,false,function nbv)
set t=null
endfunction
function nCv takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
call KillUnit(LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$B6A6EBAA))
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
set t=null
endfunction
function ndv takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local unit nDv=LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$FDD6E38E)
local real nfv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),'GRsy')
local real nFv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$BFC6BD9B)
local real xcv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$9966AD24)
if nfv>0 then
call SetUnitPosition(nDv,GetUnitX(nDv)+nFv*Cos(xcv*bj_DEGTORAD),GetUnitY(nDv)+nFv*Sin(xcv*bj_DEGTORAD))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),'GRsy',nfv-nFv)
else
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
endif
set nDv=null
set t=null
endfunction
function ngv takes unit ijv,location c,real d,real e returns nothing
local timer t=CreateTimer()
local location nGv=GetUnitLoc(ijv)
local real nfv=DistanceBetweenPoints(nGv,c)
call SaveUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$FDD6E38E,ijv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$9966AD24,AngleBetweenPoints(nGv,c))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),'GRsy',nfv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$BFC6BD9B,nfv/(d/ e))
call TimerStart(t,e,true,function ndv)
call RemoveLocation(nGv)
set nGv=null
set t=null
endfunction
function nhv takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local real nHv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$B54F5BCB)
if nHv<LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$8EBEB15B)then
set nHv=nHv+LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$A1E69E62)
call SetUnitScalePercent(LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$FDD6E38E),nHv,nHv,nHv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$B54F5BCB,nHv)
else
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
endif
set t=null
endfunction
function njv takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local real nJv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6C870C7A)
if nJv<LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$E5862439)then
set nJv=nJv+LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$234CA5CF)
call SetUnitVertexColor(LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$FDD6E38E),$FF,$FF,$FF,PercentToInt('d'-(LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$400B680E)-nJv),$FF))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6C870C7A,nJv)
else
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
endif
set t=null
endfunction
function nkv takes unit ijv,real nKv,real nlv,real nLv,real nmv returns nothing
local timer t=CreateTimer()
set nlv=nKv-nlv
call SaveUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$FDD6E38E,ijv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$400B680E,nKv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$E5862439,nlv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$234CA5CF,nlv/(nLv/ nmv))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6C870C7A,0)
call TimerStart(t,nmv,true,function njv)
set t=null
endfunction
function nMv takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local real nJv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6C870C7A)
local real nKv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$400B680E)
if nJv<LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$E5862439)-nKv then
set nJv=nJv+LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$234CA5CF)
call SetUnitVertexColor(LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$FDD6E38E),$FF,$FF,$FF,PercentToInt('d'-(nKv+nJv),$FF))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6C870C7A,nJv)
else
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
endif
set t=null
endfunction
function npv takes unit ijv,real nKv,real nlv,real nLv,real nmv returns nothing
local timer t=CreateTimer()
call SaveUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$FDD6E38E,ijv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$400B680E,nKv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$E5862439,nlv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$234CA5CF,(nlv-nKv)/(nLv/ nmv))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6C870C7A,0)
call TimerStart(t,nmv,true,function nMv)
set t=null
endfunction
function nPv takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local real nHv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$B54F5BCB)
if nHv>LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$8EBEB15B)then
set nHv=nHv-LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$A1E69E62)
call SetUnitScalePercent(LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$ED5EA1E7),nHv,nHv,nHv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$B54F5BCB,nHv)
else
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
endif
set t=null
endfunction
function nqv takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local player p=LoadPlayerHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$ECC34823)
call CameraClearNoiseForPlayer(p)
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call FlushChildHashtable(F,StringHash("Timer"+I2S((1+GetPlayerId(p)))))
call DestroyTimer(t)
set p=null
set t=null
endfunction
function nQv takes player nRv,real nsv,real nSv returns nothing
local timer t=CreateTimer()
local integer ntv=StringHash("Timer"+I2S((1+GetPlayerId(nRv))))
if HaveSavedHandle(F,ntv,0)then
call CameraClearNoiseForPlayer(nRv)
call DestroyTimer(LoadTimerHandle(F,ntv,0))
call FlushChildHashtable(F,ntv)
endif
call CameraSetEQNoiseForPlayer(nRv,nsv)
call SavePlayerHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$ECC34823,nRv)
call SaveTimerHandle(F,ntv,0,t)
call TimerStart(t,nSv,false,function nqv)
set t=null
endfunction
function nTv takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local unit ijv=LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$E555862D)
local real nuv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$A69B90F4)
local real nUv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$BD83761A)
local real nwv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$704DDED4)
local real nfv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),'GRsy')
local real xcv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$9966AD24)
local real nWv=bj_RADTODEG*Atan2(GetUnitY(ijv)-nUv,GetUnitX(ijv)-nuv)
if nwv<LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6C870C7A)then
call SetUnitX(ijv,nuv+nfv*Cos((nWv+xcv)*bj_DEGTORAD))
call SetUnitY(ijv,nUv+nfv*Sin((nWv+xcv)*bj_DEGTORAD))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$704DDED4,nwv+1)
else
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
call RemoveUnit(ijv)
endif
set ijv=null
set t=null
endfunction
function nyv takes unit ijv,real nYv,location nzv,real nfv,real nJv,real nmv,boolean nZv returns nothing
local timer t=CreateTimer()
local real nuv=GetLocationX(nzv)
local real nUv=GetLocationY(nzv)
local real xcv=360/(nfv/ nYv)
local real nWv=bj_RADTODEG*Atan2(GetUnitY(ijv)-nUv,GetUnitX(ijv)-nuv)
call SaveUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$E555862D,ijv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),'GRsy',nfv)
if not nZv then
set xcv=-xcv
endif
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$9966AD24,xcv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$A69B90F4,nuv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$BD83761A,nUv)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6C870C7A,nJv/ nmv)
call SetUnitX(ijv,nuv+nfv*Cos((nWv+xcv)*bj_DEGTORAD))
call SetUnitY(ijv,nUv+nfv*Sin((nWv+xcv)*bj_DEGTORAD))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$704DDED4,1)
call TimerStart(t,nmv,true,function nTv)
set ijv=null
set t=null
endfunction
function n_v takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local unit ijv=LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$FDD6E38E)
local real nfv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),'GRsy')
local real n0v=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$13B436D5)
local real n1v=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$201FDFAF)
local real n2v=(n1v+-(n0v*n0v/ nfv)*LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$41046ADF))+LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$A8E3A26B)
if n0v*2<nfv then
if n2v>n1v then
call SetUnitFlyHeight(ijv,n2v,0)
else
call SetUnitFlyHeight(ijv,n1v,0)
endif
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$13B436D5,n0v+LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$FB6E8B46))
else
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
call SetUnitFlyHeight(ijv,n1v,0)
endif
set ijv=null
set t=null
endfunction
function n3v takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local unit ijv=LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$FDD6E38E)
local real n4v=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$FB6E8B46)
local real nfv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),'GRsy')
local real n0v=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$13B436D5)
local real aav=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$BEFD8BE8)
local real n5v=GetUnitFacing(ijv)
local real n6v
if n0v*2<nfv then
set n0v=n0v+n4v
set n6v=aav-(Pow(n0v,2)/ nfv*LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$41046ADF))+LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$A8E3A26B)
if n6v>aav then
call SetUnitFlyHeight(ijv,n6v,0)
else
call SetUnitFlyHeight(ijv,aav,0)
endif
call SetUnitX(ijv,GetUnitX(ijv)+n4v*Cos(n5v*bj_DEGTORAD))
call SetUnitY(ijv,GetUnitY(ijv)+n4v*Sin(n5v*bj_DEGTORAD))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$13B436D5,n0v)
else
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
call SetUnitFlyHeight(ijv,aav,0)
endif
set ijv=null
set t=null
endfunction
function n7v takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
call DestroyEffect(LoadEffectHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6707A4AC))
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
set t=null
endfunction
function n8v takes effect n9v,real ncv returns nothing
local timer t=CreateTimer()
call SaveEffectHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6707A4AC,n9v)
call TimerStart(t,ncv,false,function n7v)
set t=null
endfunction
function Vvv takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local unit ijv=LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),-$2291C72)
local unit Vev=LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),-$3B27D8A)
local string Vxv=LoadStr(F,GetHandleId(t),$58FF5E62)
local integer nwv=LoadInteger(F,GetHandleId(t),$704DDED4)
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(ijv)))
if nwv<LoadInteger(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6C870C7A)and GetUnitState(Vev,UNIT_STATE_LIFE)>0 then
call UnitDamageTarget(ijv,Vev,LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$40AA7251),true,false,ATTACK_TYPE_NORMAL,DAMAGE_TYPE_MAGIC,WEAPON_TYPE_WHOKNOWS)
if Vxv!=null and Vxv!="" then
call n8v(AddSpecialEffectTarget(Vxv,Vev,LoadStr(F,GetHandleId(t),$A5F1A2)),LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$10D8B4D1))
endif
call SaveInteger(F,GetHandleId(t),$704DDED4,nwv+1)
else
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
endif
set t=null
endfunction
function Vov takes unit ijv,unit Vev,real iJv,real Vrv,real nmv,real Viv,string Vxv,string Vav returns nothing
local timer t
local integer Vnv=S2I(R2S(Vrv))
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(ijv)))
call UnitDamageTarget(ijv,Vev,iJv,true,false,ATTACK_TYPE_NORMAL,DAMAGE_TYPE_MAGIC,WEAPON_TYPE_WHOKNOWS)
if Vxv!=null and Vxv!="" then
call n8v(AddSpecialEffectTarget(Vxv,Vev,Vav),Viv)
endif
if Vnv>1 then
set t=CreateTimer()
call SaveUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),-$2291C72,ijv)
call SaveUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),-$3B27D8A,Vev)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$40AA7251,iJv)
call SaveInteger(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6C870C7A,Vnv)
call SaveInteger(F,GetHandleId(t),$704DDED4,1)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$10D8B4D1,Viv)
call SaveStr(F,GetHandleId(t),$58FF5E62,Vxv)
call SaveStr(F,GetHandleId(t),$A5F1A2,Vav)
call TimerStart(t,nmv,true,function Vvv)
set t=null
endif
endfunction
function VVv takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local unit ijv=LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),-$2291C72)
local integer nwv=LoadInteger(F,GetHandleId(t),$704DDED4)
if nwv<LoadInteger(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6C870C7A)and GetUnitState(ijv,UNIT_STATE_LIFE)>0 then
call SetWidgetLife(ijv,GetUnitState(ijv,UNIT_STATE_LIFE)+LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$40AA7251))
call n8v(AddSpecialEffectTarget(LoadStr(F,GetHandleId(t),$58FF5E62),ijv,LoadStr(F,GetHandleId(t),$A5F1A2)),LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$10D8B4D1))
call SaveInteger(F,GetHandleId(t),$704DDED4,nwv+1)
else
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
endif
set ijv=null
set t=null
endfunction
function VEv takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local unit ijv=LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),-$2291C72)
local unit Vev=LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),-$3B27D8A)
local real nwv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$704DDED4)
local real nfv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),'GRsy')
local real VXv
local real xcv=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),-$669952DC)
local real x=GetUnitX(Vev)
local real y=GetUnitY(Vev)
if nwv<LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),-$6C870C7A)then
set VXv=bj_RADTODEG*Atan2(GetUnitY(ijv)-y,GetUnitX(ijv)-x)
call SetUnitX(ijv,x+nfv*Cos((VXv+xcv)*bj_DEGTORAD))
call SetUnitY(ijv,y+nfv*Sin((VXv+xcv)*bj_DEGTORAD))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$704DDED4,nwv+1)
else
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
call RemoveUnit(ijv)
endif
set ijv=null
set Vev=null
set t=null
endfunction
function Enemy takes nothing returns boolean
return IsUnitEnemy(GetFilterUnit(),GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit()))
endfunction
function Thunderbolt takes nothing returns nothing
call IssueTargetOrderById(bj_lastCreatedUnit,$D007F,GetEnumUnit())
endfunction
function VOv takes integer apv returns timer
if(q==0)then
if(not s)then
call TriggerEvaluate(eyv[(1)])
set q=q-1
else
set egv[0]=CreateTimer()
endif
else
set q=q-1
endif
call SaveInteger(P,0,GetHandleId((egv[q])),(apv))
return egv[q]
endfunction
function NewTimer takes nothing returns timer
return VOv(0)
endfunction
function VRv takes timer t returns nothing
if(t==null)then
return
endif
if(q==8190)then
call DestroyTimer(t)
else
call PauseTimer(t)
if((LoadInteger(P,0,GetHandleId((t))))==Q)then
return
endif
call SaveInteger(P,0,GetHandleId((t)),(Q))
set egv[q]=t
set q=q+1
endif
endfunction
function VIv takes nothing returns nothing
local integer i=0
local integer o=-1
local boolean oops=false
if(s)then
return
else
set s=true
endif
set P=InitHashtable()
loop
exitwhen(i==M)
set egv[i]=CreateTimer()
call SaveInteger(P,0,GetHandleId((egv[i])),(Q))
set i=i+1
endloop
set q=M
endfunction
function VAv takes nothing returns nothing
local integer VNv=(GetHandleId((BlzGetOriginFrame(ORIGIN_FRAME_GAME_UI,0))))
local integer Vbv
local integer VBv
local integer nwv=0
local integer Vcv=0
call DestroyTimer(GetExpiredTimer())
set VBv=(GetHandleId((BlzGetOriginFrame(ORIGIN_FRAME_MINIMAP_BUTTON,(0)))))
call BlzFrameClearAllPoints(iuv((VBv)))
call i0v(VBv,0,(GetHandleId((BlzGetOriginFrame(ORIGIN_FRAME_MINIMAP,0)))),2,-.5,-.002)
set Vbv=VBv
set nwv=1
loop
exitwhen nwv>4
set VBv=(GetHandleId((BlzGetOriginFrame(ORIGIN_FRAME_MINIMAP_BUTTON,(nwv)))))
call BlzFrameClearAllPoints(iuv((VBv)))
call i0v(VBv,1,Vbv,7,0,-.003)
set Vbv=VBv
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
endfunction
function VCv takes nothing returns nothing
call BlzLoadTOCFile(("UI\\FDFList.toc"))
call aXv(.0218,.115)
call axv((GetHandleId((BlzGetOriginFrame(ORIGIN_FRAME_MINIMAP,0)))),.76)
call i0v((GetHandleId((BlzGetOriginFrame(ORIGIN_FRAME_MINIMAP,0)))),6,(GetHandleId((BlzGetOriginFrame(ORIGIN_FRAME_GAME_UI,0)))),6,.011,.01)
call TimerStart(CreateTimer(),.01,false,function VAv)
endfunction

function VFv takes integer xPv,integer Vgv,real n4v,real VGv,real Vhv,integer VHv returns nothing
call SaveInteger(w,$61F24BB6,Vgv,xPv)
call SaveInteger(w,xPv,$633009F5,Vgv)
call SaveReal(w,xPv,$FB6E8B46,n4v)
call SaveReal(w,xPv,$E6BB3831,VGv)
call SaveReal(w,xPv,$FEE6DD76,Vhv)
call SaveInteger(w,xPv,$2ACFE497,VHv)
endfunction
function Vjv takes player p,integer VDv,integer Vfv,real x,real y,real n5v,boolean VJv returns unit
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local integer Vkv
local unit u
if VDv>0 and(HaveSavedInteger(w,(VDv),$633009F5))then
if Vfv!=0 and HaveSavedInteger(w,$471FBE10,Vfv)then
set Vkv=LoadInteger(w,$471FBE10,Vfv)
else
set Vfv=0
set Vkv=LoadInteger(w,VDv,$633009F5)
endif
if Vkv!=0 then
set u=CreateUnit(p,Vkv,x,y,n5v)
call SetUnitX(u,x)
call SetUnitY(u,y)
if VJv then
set S[ilv]=VDv
set U[ilv]=Vfv
if Vfv>0 then
call SetUnitMoveSpeed(u,LoadReal(w,VDv,$FB6E8B46))
call amv(u,1,LoadReal(w,VDv,$E6BB3831))
call BlzSetUnitAttackCooldown((u),((LoadReal(w,VDv,$FEE6DD76))*1.),(1)-1)
call BlzSetUnitWeaponIntegerField((u),UNIT_WEAPON_IF_ATTACK_WEAPON_SOUND,(1)-1,(LoadInteger(w,VDv,$2ACFE497)))
endif
endif
set bj_lastCreatedUnit=u
set u=null
return bj_lastCreatedUnit
endif
endif
return null
endfunction

function Vlv takes nothing returns nothing
call TimerStart(CreateTimer(),1.,false,function VKv)
endfunction
function VLv takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=(GetTriggerPlayer())
local real x=GetStartLocationX(GetPlayerStartLocation(p))
local real y=GetStartLocationY(GetPlayerStartLocation(p))
call SetUnitPosition(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(p))],x,y)
if p==GetLocalPlayer()then
call PanCameraToTimed(x,y,.01)
endif
set p=null
endfunction
function Vmv takes nothing returns nothing
local integer VNv=(GetHandleId((BlzGetOriginFrame(ORIGIN_FRAME_GAME_UI,0))))
local integer nwv=0
local integer VMv
local integer Vpv
local integer VPv=(GetHandleId((BlzGetOriginFrame(ORIGIN_FRAME_MINIMAP,0))))
local string Vqv
local trigger iTv
call DestroyTimer(GetExpiredTimer())
loop
exitwhen nwv==3
if nwv==0 then
set Vqv="Hero"
elseif nwv==1 then
set Vqv="Skill"
elseif nwv==2 then
set Vqv="Return"
endif
set Vpv=iUv("ResponsiveButton",VNv,0,$514+nwv)
set VMv=(GetHandleId((BlzGetFrameByName(("ResponsiveButtonB"),($514+nwv)))))
call i9v(VMv,"UI\\"+Vqv+"A.tga",0)
set VMv=(GetHandleId((BlzGetFrameByName(("ResponsiveButtonPB"),($514+nwv)))))
call i9v(VMv,"UI\\"+Vqv+"B.tga",0)
set VMv=(GetHandleId((BlzGetFrameByName(("ResponsiveButtonDB"),($514+nwv)))))
call i9v(VMv,"UI\\"+Vqv+"C.tga",0)
if nwv==0 then
call i0v(Vpv,6,VPv,8,.004,.005)
else
call i0v(Vpv,6,VPv,8,.002,0)
endif
set VPv=Vpv
set W[nwv]=Vpv
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
call i7v(W[0],false)
call i7v(W[1],false)
set iTv=CreateTrigger()
call aRv(iTv,W[2],1)
call TriggerAddAction(iTv,function VLv)
set iTv=null
endfunction
function VQv takes nothing returns nothing
call TimerStart(CreateTimer(),.1,false,function Vmv)
endfunction
function GetCurrentHost takes nothing returns player
return Y
endfunction

endfunction
function VSv takes nothing returns nothing
endfunction
function Vtv takes integer xsv returns nothing
set Sm[vv]=jm[xsv]
if Ep[vv]==xsv then
set Ep[vv]=Km[xsv]
endif
call x9v(xsv)
call PauseTimer(Um[vv])
call xSv(vv)
endfunction
function VTv takes nothing returns boolean
local integer xsv=LoadInteger(mm,0,GetHandleId(GetTriggeringTrigger()))
local integer Vuv=vv
set vv=km[xsv]
set ev=vv
if TriggerEvaluate(Hm[xsv])then
call Vtv(xsv)
endif
set vv=Vuv
set ev=vv
return true
endfunction
function V6v takes integer V7v returns nothing
local integer xsv=V7v
loop
exitwhen xsv==0
call x9v(xsv)
set xsv=Km[xsv]
endloop
endfunction
function s__TimerPutsTriggerToSleep___TrigInfo_create takes nothing returns integer
local integer xsv=x8v()
call SaveInteger(mm,0,GetHandleId(hm[xsv]),xsv)
return xsv
endfunction
function V9v takes integer xsv returns nothing
if Um[xsv]==null then
return
endif
set Xp=xsv
call TriggerEvaluate(eHv[GetHandleId(um[xsv])])
call xUv(xsv)
call VRv(Um[xsv])
set Um[xsv]=null
call xtv(xsv)
call x6v(xsv)
endfunction
function Evv takes nothing returns nothing
local integer xsv=(LoadInteger(P,0,GetHandleId((GetExpiredTimer()))))
call V9v(xsv)
endfunction
function Eev takes nothing returns nothing
set vv=0
set ev=vv
endfunction
function Exv takes integer xsv returns nothing
local integer Eov=vv
set qm=true
set vv=xsv
set ev=vv
set Wm[xsv]=true
call TriggerExecute(Tm[xsv])
set qm=false
if Wm[xsv]then
call V9v(xsv)
endif
set vv=Eov
set ev=vv
call TimerStart(rp,0,false,function Eev)
endfunction
function Erv takes nothing returns nothing
local integer xsv=(LoadInteger(P,0,GetHandleId((GetExpiredTimer()))))
set Sm[xsv]=tm[xsv]
call Exv(xsv)
endfunction
function Eiv takes integer xsv,real Eav,integer Env returns nothing
if Um[xsv]==null then
return
endif
set tm[xsv]=Env
set Wm[xsv]=false
call TimerStart(Um[xsv],Eav,false,function Erv)
endfunction
function EVv takes integer xsv,real Eav returns nothing
call Eiv(xsv,Eav,Sm[xsv]+1)
endfunction
function EEv takes nothing returns integer
local integer xsv
local eventid EVENT
set qm=true
set xsv=x5v()
set vv=xsv
set ev=vv
set um[xsv]=GetTriggerEventId()
set Um[xsv]=VOv(xsv)
set Tm[xsv]=GetTriggeringTrigger()
call TimerStart(Um[xsv],0,false,function Evv)
set Xp=xsv
call TriggerEvaluate(eGv[GetHandleId(um[xsv])])
call xuv(xsv)
return xsv
endfunction
function EXv takes integer Env returns nothing
local integer xsv
local eventid EVENT
if vv!=0 and Sm[vv]==Qm then
set Sm[vv]=Env
return
elseif qm then
return
endif
set xsv=EEv()
set Sm[xsv]=Env
endfunction
function s__TrigVariables_Setting takes nothing returns nothing
call EXv(1)
endfunction
function EOv takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ERv
if vv==0 then
set ERv=vv
call EEv()
set sm[vv]=ERv
elseif Tm[vv]!=GetTriggeringTrigger()then
set ERv=vv
call EEv()
set sm[vv]=ERv
endif
endfunction
function EIv takes nothing returns nothing
local integer VMv
if sm[vv]!=Qm then
set VMv=sm[vv]
set sm[vv]=Qm
set vv=VMv
set ev=vv
else
set qm=false
endif
endfunction
function EAv takes trigger t returns nothing
if Vp==t then
return
endif
set Vp=t
call TriggerAddAction(t,function EOv)
set ap[np]=t
set np=np+1
endfunction
function ENv takes nothing returns nothing
local integer i=0
loop
exitwhen i>=np
call TriggerAddAction(ap[i],function EIv)
set ap[i]=null
set i=i+1
endloop
set np=0
set Vp=null
endfunction
function Ebv takes nothing returns nothing
call DestroyTimer(GetExpiredTimer())
call ENv()
endfunction

return
endif

function cIv takes code Xiv returns trigger
local trigger t=CreateTrigger()
call TriggerAddCondition(t,Condition(Xiv))
return t
endfunction

return t

function Fav takes code Xiv returns trigger
local trigger t=CreateTrigger()
call TriggerAddCondition(t,Condition(Xiv))
return t
endfunction

function hfv takes code Xiv returns trigger

call TriggerAddCondition(t,Condition(Xiv))
return t
endfunction

function jvv takes code Xiv returns trigger

endfunction

function KNv takes code Xiv returns trigger
local trigger t=CreateTrigger()
call TriggerAddCondition(t,Condition(Xiv))
return t
endfunction

set Gw[98+'d']=KNv(function KIv)
set Gw[99+'d']=KNv(function KAv)
endfunction
function KBv takes integer xsv,integer i,effect x returns nothing
set Ip=xsv
set Fw[xsv]=x
call TriggerEvaluate(Gw[i])
endfunction
function Kcv takes integer xsv,integer i returns effect
set Ip=xsv
call TriggerEvaluate(Gw[i+'d'])
return gw
endfunction

return t
endfunction

function PWv takes code Xiv returns trigger
local trigger t=CreateTrigger()
call TriggerAddCondition(t,Condition(Xiv))
return t
endfunction

function PYv takes integer xsv,integer i,unit x returns nothing
set Ip=xsv
set gz[xsv]=x
call TriggerEvaluate(hz[i])
endfunction
function Pzv takes integer xsv,integer i returns unit
set Ip=xsv
call TriggerEvaluate(hz[i+'d'])
return Gz
endfunction

function QGv takes code Xiv returns trigger
local trigger t=CreateTrigger()
call TriggerAddCondition(t,Condition(Xiv))
return t
endfunction

function QHv takes integer xsv,integer i,location x returns nothing
set Ip=xsv
set J0[xsv]=x
call TriggerEvaluate(Hz[i])
endfunction

function tsv takes code Xiv returns trigger
local trigger t=CreateTrigger()
call TriggerAddCondition(t,Condition(Xiv))
return t
endfunction

function ttv takes integer xsv,integer i,location x returns nothing
set Ip=xsv
set J0[xsv]=x
call TriggerEvaluate(K0[i])
endfunction
function tTv takes integer xsv,integer i returns location
set Ip=xsv
call TriggerEvaluate(K0[i+'d'])
return k0
endfunction

function ucv takes code Xiv returns trigger
local trigger t=CreateTrigger()
call TriggerAddCondition(t,Condition(Xiv))
return t
endfunction

function zYv takes code Xiv returns trigger
local trigger t=CreateTrigger()
call TriggerAddCondition(t,Condition(Xiv))
return t
endfunction
function zzv takes nothing returns nothing
call Xrv(function WPv)
set S4[0]=zYv(function Wqv)
set S4[1]=zYv(function WQv)
set S4[2]=zYv(function Wsv)
set S4[3]=zYv(function WSv)
set S4[4]=zYv(function Wtv)
set S4[5]=zYv(function WTv)
set S4[6]=zYv(function Wuv)
set S4[7]=zYv(function WUv)
set S4[8]=zYv(function Wwv)
set S4[9]=zYv(function WWv)
set S4[$A]=zYv(function Wyv)
set S4[$B]=zYv(function WYv)
set S4[$C]=zYv(function Wzv)
set S4[$D]=zYv(function WZv)
set S4[$E]=zYv(function W_v)

function zZv takes integer xsv,integer i,integer x returns nothing
set Ip=xsv
set Q4[xsv]=x
call TriggerEvaluate(S4[i])
endfunction

call TriggerAddCondition(t,Condition(Xiv))

endfunction

function ide takes integer xsv,integer i,boolean x returns nothing
set Ip=xsv
set s8[xsv]=x
call TriggerEvaluate(t8[i])
set s8[xsv]=true
endfunction
function ife takes integer xsv,integer iFe,integer i,real x returns nothing
if iFe==1 then
set Pk[vbv[xsv]+i]=x
elseif iFe==2 then
set Sk[vBv[xsv]+i]=x
elseif iFe==3 then
set Uk[vcv[xsv]+i]=x
elseif iFe==4 then
set Yk[vCv[xsv]+i]=x
elseif iFe==5 then
set eK[vdv[xsv]+i]=x
elseif iFe==6 then
set iK[vDv[xsv]+i]=x
endif
endfunction
function ige takes integer xsv,integer iFe,integer i returns real
if iFe==1 then
return Pk[vbv[xsv]+i]
elseif iFe==2 then
return Sk[vBv[xsv]+i]
elseif iFe==3 then
return Uk[vcv[xsv]+i]
elseif iFe==4 then
return Yk[vCv[xsv]+i]
elseif iFe==5 then
return eK[vdv[xsv]+i]
elseif iFe==6 then
return iK[vDv[xsv]+i]
else
return .0
endif
endfunction

function aOe takes nothing returns nothing
set exv=CreateItem('cnob',0,0)
set eov=AddSpecialEffect("Objects\\InventoryItems\\TreasureChest\\treasurechest.mdl",0,0)
set erv=CreateUnit(Player(0),'hfoo',0,0,0)
set eiv=Location(0,0)
set eav=AddLightning("CLPB",false,0,0,0,0)
call RemoveItem(exv)
call DestroyEffect(eov)
call RemoveUnit(erv)
call RemoveLocation(eiv)
call DestroyLightning(eav)
call TriggerAddCondition(env,Condition(function xwv))
call TriggerAddCondition(eVv,Condition(function xWv))
call TriggerAddCondition(eEv,Condition(function xyv))
call TriggerAddCondition(eXv,Condition(function xYv))
call TriggerAddCondition(eOv,Condition(function xzv))
call TriggerAddCondition(eRv,Condition(function xZv))
call TriggerAddCondition(eIv,Condition(function x_v))
call TriggerAddCondition(eAv,Condition(function x0v))
call TriggerAddCondition(eNv,Condition(function x1v))
call TriggerAddCondition(ebv,Condition(function x2v))
call TriggerAddCondition(eBv,Condition(function x3v))
call TriggerAddCondition(ecv,Condition(function x4v))
endfunction

function nEe takes unit u returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(u)))
local integer VDv=S[ilv]
if VDv==1 then
if ha[ilv]>0 then
call UnitRemoveAbility(u,'A01G')

call SetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A0G7',ha[ilv]+Jn[ilv])
call UnitMakeAbilityPermanent(u,true,'A0G7')
elseif ri[ilv]>0 then
call UnitAddAbility(u,'A01G')

call UnitMakeAbilityPermanent(u,true,'A01G')

if qn[ilv]>0 then

call SetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A052',ii[ilv])
call UnitMakeAbilityPermanent(u,true,'A052')
endif

call UnitMakeAbilityPermanent(u,true,'A05E')
endif

function nXe takes unit nOe,unit nRe returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(nRe)))

set nIe=(BlzGetUnitAbilityCooldownRemaining((nOe),('A0G7')))

if nIe>0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((nRe),('A0W3'),((nIe)*1.))
endif

call UnitMakeAbilityPermanent(nRe,true,'A0Y8')

if nIe>0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((nRe),('A0Y8'),((nIe)*1.))
endif

if Ui[ilv]>0 then

call UnitAddAbility(nRe,'A0Y9')
call SetUnitAbilityLevel(nRe,'A0Y9',Ui[ilv]+tV[ilv])
call UnitMakeAbilityPermanent(nRe,true,'A0Y9')

call UnitMakeAbilityPermanent(nRe,true,'A0YA')

if MX[ilv]>0 then
call UnitRemoveAbility(nRe,'A0T1')
call UnitAddAbility(nRe,'0')

call UnitMakeAbilityPermanent(nRe,true,'0')
set nIe=(BlzGetUnitAbilityCooldownRemaining((nOe),('0')))

if ha[ilv]>0 then

function nAe takes nothing returns nothing
endfunction
function nNe takes integer xPv,string iwv,string nbe,string nBe returns nothing
call SaveStr(ov,$7C181E3A,xPv,iwv)
call SaveStr(ov,$AE3F9358,xPv,nbe)
call SaveStr(ov,$E9DEFE1D,xPv,nBe)
endfunction
function nce takes nothing returns nothing
local integer VNv=(GetHandleId((BlzGetOriginFrame(ORIGIN_FRAME_GAME_UI,0))))
local integer nCe=(GetHandleId((BlzGetOriginFrame(ORIGIN_FRAME_MINIMAP,0))))
local integer VMv
local integer nwv=0
local real nde=.08671875
local real nDe=.018
loop
exitwhen nwv==3
set VMv=izv("BACKDROP","ResourceB"+I2S(nwv),VNv,"Template",$44C+nwv)
call i0v(VMv,0,nCe,2,.01,.0025-nDe*(3-nwv-1))
call arv(VMv,.01640625,.01640625)
if HaveSavedString(ov,$E9DEFE1D,nwv)then
call i9v(VMv,LoadStr(ov,$E9DEFE1D,nwv),0)
else
call i9v(VMv,"UI\\Feedback\\Resources\\ResourceGold.blp",0)
endif
call SaveInteger(ov,'e',nwv,VMv)
set VMv=izv("TEXT","ResourceT"+I2S(nwv),VNv,"EscMenuInfoTextTemplate",$456+nwv)
call i0v(VMv,2,nCe,2,nde,.0025-nDe*(3-nwv-1))
call arv(VMv,.07578125,.01640625)
call anv(VMv,1,5)
call i5v(VMv,"0")
call SaveInteger(ov,'d',nwv,VMv)
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
endfunction
function nfe takes integer ilv,integer xPv returns integer
local integer r=0
if 0<=xPv and xPv<3 then
set r=(BlzBitXor((LoadInteger(ov,ilv,xPv+$A)),(rv)))
endif
return r
endfunction
function nFe takes integer ilv,integer xPv,integer apv returns nothing
if 0<=xPv and xPv<3 then
call SaveInteger(ov,ilv,xPv,apv)
call SaveInteger(ov,ilv,xPv+$A,(BlzBitXor((apv),(rv))))
endif
endfunction
function nge takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=GetPlayerId(GetLocalPlayer())
local integer nwv=0
loop
exitwhen nwv==3
call i5v(LoadInteger(ov,'d',nwv),I2S((BlzBitXor((LoadInteger(ov,ilv,nwv+$A)),(rv)))))
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
endfunction
function nGe takes player p,integer xPv,integer apv returns nothing
if xPv<0 or 3<=xPv then
return
endif
if apv<0 then
set apv=0
endif
call nFe(GetPlayerId(p),xPv,apv)
if p==GetLocalPlayer()then
call nge()
endif
endfunction
function nhe takes player p,integer xPv,integer apv returns integer
local integer ilv=GetPlayerId(p)
local integer nHe
local integer VMv
local integer nje
local integer nwv=xPv+1
if xPv<0 or 3<=xPv then
return 0
endif
set nHe=nfe(ilv,xPv)+apv
if nwv<3 and nHe>=xv then
set VMv=nHe/ xv
set nHe=nHe-VMv*xv
loop
set VMv=nfe(ilv,nwv)+VMv
exitwhen nwv+1>=3
if VMv>=xv then
set nje=VMv/ xv
call nFe(ilv,nwv,VMv-nje*xv)
set VMv=nje
else
exitwhen true
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
call nFe(ilv,nwv,VMv)
endif
call nFe(ilv,xPv,nHe)
if p==GetLocalPlayer()then
call nge()
endif
return nHe
endfunction
function nJe takes player p,integer xPv,integer apv returns boolean
local integer ilv=GetPlayerId(p)
local integer nke
local integer nKe
local integer nwv=xPv+1
local integer Vcv=0
if xPv<0 or 3<=xPv then
return false
endif
set nke=nfe(ilv,xPv)
if nke>=apv then
call nFe(ilv,xPv,nke-apv)
return true
else
loop
exitwhen nwv>=3
set nKe=nfe(ilv,nwv)
if nKe>0 then
call nFe(ilv,nwv,nKe-1)
set Vcv=nwv-1
loop
exitwhen Vcv<=xPv
call nFe(ilv,Vcv,xv-1)
set Vcv=Vcv-1
endloop
call nFe(ilv,xPv,nke+xv-apv)
return true
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
return false
endif
endfunction
function nle takes player p,integer xPv,integer apv returns boolean
local boolean nHe=nJe(p,xPv,apv)
if nHe and p==GetLocalPlayer()then
call nge()
endif
return nHe
endfunction
function nLe takes player p,integer xPv,integer apv,integer nme returns boolean
local integer ilv=GetPlayerId(p)
local integer nke
local integer nKe
local integer nwv=xPv+1
local integer Vcv=0
local integer nMe
local real npe
if xPv<0 or 3<=xPv then
return false
endif
set nke=nfe(ilv,xPv)
if nke>=I2R(apv)*nme then
call nFe(ilv,xPv,nke-apv*nme)
return true
else
set npe=I2R(apv)*nme
set nMe=S2I(R2S(npe/ xv))
if nMe>0 then
set npe=npe-I2R(nMe)*xv
endif
set nKe=nfe(ilv,xPv+1)
if npe<=nke and nMe<=nKe then
call nFe(ilv,xPv,nke-S2I(R2S(npe)))
call nFe(ilv,xPv+1,nKe-nMe)
return true
else
if npe<=nke then
set nke=nke-S2I(R2S(npe))
elseif nKe>0 then
set nKe=nKe-1
set nke=nke+xv-S2I(R2S(npe))
else
set Vcv=nfe(ilv,xPv+2)
if Vcv>0 then
call nFe(ilv,xPv+2,Vcv-1)
set nKe=nKe+xv-1
set nke=nke+xv-S2I(R2S(npe))
else
return false
endif
endif
if nMe<=nKe then
set nKe=nKe-nMe
else
set Vcv=nfe(ilv,xPv+2)
if Vcv>0 then
call nFe(ilv,xPv+2,Vcv-1)
set nKe=nKe+xv-1
set nke=nke+xv-nMe
else
return false
endif
endif
call nFe(ilv,xPv,nke)
call nFe(ilv,xPv+1,nKe)
return true
endif
return false
endif
endfunction
function nPe takes player p,integer xPv,integer apv,integer nme returns boolean
local boolean nHe
if apv<=0 or nme<=0 then
return true
endif
set nHe=nLe(p,xPv,apv,nme)
if nHe and p==GetLocalPlayer()then
call nge()
endif
return nHe
endfunction
function nqe takes nothing returns boolean
local unit u=GetBuyingUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local item it=GetSoldItem()
local integer nQe=GetItemTypeId(it)
local integer nse=LoadInteger(ov,nQe,$83B83ED4)
if nse!=0 then
call RemoveItem(it)
if nle(p,LoadInteger(ov,nQe,$2776EDD2),LoadInteger(ov,nQe,$356707F3))then
set it=CreateItem(nse,GetUnitX(u),GetUnitY(u))
call SetItemPlayer(it,p,true)
call UnitAddItem(u,it)
endif
endif
set u=null
set p=null
set it=null
return false
endfunction
function nSe takes nothing returns nothing
call DestroyTimer(GetExpiredTimer())
call nce()
endfunction
function nte takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=CreateTimer()
local trigger iTv
local integer nwv=0
local integer Vcv
set rv=GetRandomInt(-$7FFFFFFF,$7FFFFFFF)
loop
exitwhen nwv==$C
set Vcv=0
loop
exitwhen Vcv==3
call SaveInteger(ov,nwv,Vcv,0)
call SaveInteger(ov,nwv,Vcv+$A,rv)
set Vcv=Vcv+1
endloop
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
set iTv=CreateTrigger()
call TriggerRegisterAnyUnitEventBJ(iTv,EVENT_PLAYER_UNIT_SELL_ITEM)
call TriggerAddCondition(iTv,Condition(function nqe))
call nNe(0,"동","|CffBC5E00","UI\\GameUI_Coin_Bronze.tga")
call nNe(1,"은","|CFFC0C0C0","UI\\GameUI_Coin_Silver.tga")
call nNe(2,"금","|CFFFFD700","UI\\GameUI_Coin_Gold.tga")
call TimerStart(t,.1,false,function nSe)
set t=null
set iTv=null
endfunction
function nTe takes integer i returns string
if i<$A then
return"0"+I2S(i)
else
return I2S(i)
endif
endfunction
function nue takes integer xsv returns integer
return(xsv-xsv/ 86400*86400)/ $E10
endfunction
function nUe takes integer xsv returns integer
return(xsv-xsv/ $E10*$E10)/ 60
endfunction
function nwe takes integer xsv returns integer
return xsv-xsv/ 60*60
endfunction
function nWe takes integer xsv returns string
local string nHe=nTe(nue(xsv))+":"+nTe(nUe(xsv))+":"+nTe(nwe(xsv))
if((xsv)/ 86400)>0 then
return I2S(((xsv)/ 86400))+"."+nHe
endif
return nHe
endfunction
function s__DateTime__get_Now takes nothing returns integer
return 0
endfunction
function nze takes integer xsv,integer nZe returns integer
local integer n=((xsv)+$7E90)/ 86400+$AF93A
local integer n_e=n/ $23AB1
local integer n0e
local integer y4
local integer y1
local integer n1e
local integer m
set n=n-n_e*$23AB1
set n0e=n/ $8EAC
if n0e==4 then
set n0e=3
endif
set n=n-n0e*$8EAC
set y4=n/ $5B5
set n=n-y4*$5B5
set y1=n/ 365
if y1==4 then
set y1=3
endif
if nZe==0 then
return n_e*400+n0e*'d'+y4*4+y1+1
endif
set n=n-y1*365
if nZe==1 then
return n+1
endif
if y1==3 and(y4!=24 or n0e==3)then
set n1e=1
else
set n1e=0
endif
set m=n/ 32+1
loop
if m>1 then
set y1=n1e
else
set y1=0
endif
exitwhen n<eFv[m]+y1
set m=m+1
endloop
if nZe==2 then
return m
endif
set m=m-1
if m<=1 then
set n1e=0
endif
return n-eFv[m]+n1e+1
endfunction
function n2e takes integer xsv returns integer
return(((xsv)+$7E90)-((xsv)+$7E90)/ 86400*86400)/ $E10
endfunction
function n3e takes integer xsv returns integer
return(((xsv)+$7E90)-((xsv)+$7E90)/ $E10*$E10)/ 60
endfunction
function n4e takes integer xsv returns integer
return((xsv)+$7E90)-((xsv)+$7E90)/ 60*60
endfunction
function n9e takes nothing returns nothing
set eFv[1]=31
set eFv[2]=59
set eFv[3]=90
set eFv[4]='x'
set eFv[5]=$97
set eFv[6]=$B5
set eFv[7]=$D4
set eFv[8]=$F3
set eFv[9]=273
set eFv[$A]=304
set eFv[$B]=334
set eFv[$C]=365
endfunction
function Vve takes integer xsv returns string
local integer Vee=n2e((xsv))
if Vee<$C then
if Vee==0 then
set Vee=$C
endif
return"오전 "+I2S(Vee)
else
set Vee=Vee-$C
if Vee==0 then
set Vee=$C
endif
return"오후 "+I2S(Vee)
endif
endfunction
function Vxe takes integer xsv returns string
return I2S((nze(((xsv)),0)))+"-"+(nTe((nze((((xsv))),2))))+"-"+(nTe((nze((((xsv))),3))))+" "+Vve(xsv)+":"+(nTe(n3e(((xsv)))))+":"+(nTe(n4e(((xsv)))))
endfunction
function Voe takes nothing returns nothing
endfunction

function Vie takes nothing returns nothing
local string array Vae
local integer array Vne
local boolean array VVe
local integer VEe=0
local string Vqv
local integer i=0
local integer j=0
local integer id
call DestroyTimer(GetExpiredTimer())
loop
exitwhen i>=$C
set Vqv=GetPlayerName(Player(i))
set id=Vre(Vqv)
set iv[i]=id
if id!=0 then
set j=0
loop
exitwhen j>=VEe or id==Vne[j]
set j=j+1
endloop
if j==VEe then
set Vae[VEe]=Vqv
set Vne[VEe]=id
set VEe=VEe+1
else
set Vae[j]=Vae[j]+" / "+Vqv
set VVe[j]=true
set nv=nv+1
endif
endif
set i=i+1
endloop
set i=0
loop
exitwhen Vne[i]==0
if VVe[i]then
set j=0
loop
exitwhen j>=$C
if Vne[i]==iv[j]then
set av[j]=true
endif
set j=j+1
endloop
endif
set i=i+1
endloop
endfunction
function VXe takes nothing returns nothing
call TimerStart(CreateTimer(),.1,false,function Vie)
endfunction

function VBe takes integer Vce returns string
local string inputStr=I2S(Vce)
local string VCe=null
local integer Vde
loop
exitwhen Vce<=0
set Vde=ModuloInteger(Vce,Ov)
set VCe=SubString(Vv,Vde,Vde+1)+VCe
set Vce=Vce/ Ov
endloop
return VCe
endfunction
function VDe takes string Vce returns integer
local integer Vfe=StringLength(Vce)
local string nke=null
local integer VCe=0
local integer nwv
local integer Vcv
set nwv=0
loop
exitwhen nwv>=Vfe
set VCe=VCe*Ov
set nke=SubString(Vce,nwv,nwv+1)
set Vcv=0
loop
exitwhen(Vcv>=Ov)or(nke==SubString(Vv,Vcv,Vcv+1))
set Vcv=Vcv+1
endloop
if(Vcv<=Ov)then
set VCe=VCe+Vcv
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
return VCe
endfunction
function VFe takes integer Vce returns string
local string Vge="01"
local integer VGe=StringLength(Vge)
local string inputStr=I2S(Vce)
local string VCe=null
local integer Vde
loop
exitwhen Vce<=0
set Vde=ModuloInteger(Vce,VGe)
set VCe=SubString(Vge,Vde,Vde+1)+VCe
set Vce=Vce/ VGe
endloop
return VCe
endfunction
function Vhe takes string Vce returns integer
local string Vge="01"
local integer VGe=StringLength(Vge)
local integer Vfe=StringLength(Vce)
local string nke=null
local integer VCe=0
local integer nwv
local integer Vcv
set nwv=0
loop
exitwhen nwv>=Vfe
set VCe=VCe*VGe
set nke=SubString(Vce,nwv,nwv+1)
set Vcv=0
loop
exitwhen(Vcv>=VGe)or(nke==SubString(Vge,Vcv,Vcv+1))
set Vcv=Vcv+1
endloop
if(Vcv<=VGe)then
set VCe=VCe+Vcv
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
return VCe
endfunction
function VHe takes string Vce,integer Vje returns string
local integer Vfe=StringLength(Vce)
local integer VJe=Vfe-Vje
if(VJe<0)then
loop
exitwhen VJe>=0
set Vce=Rv+Vce
set VJe=VJe+1
endloop
endif
return Vce
endfunction
function Vke takes string Vce,integer VKe returns string
local integer Vfe=StringLength(Vce)
local integer VJe=Vfe-VKe
if(VJe<0)then
loop
exitwhen VJe>=0
set Vce="0"+Vce
set VJe=VJe+1
endloop
endif
return Vce
endfunction
function Vle takes string iwv returns integer
local string VLe="ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz1234567890~`!#$^&*()-_=+|{}[]:;<>,.?@"
local string Vme
local integer VMe=StringLength(VLe)
local integer Vpe=StringLength(iwv)
local integer cutLength
local integer VCe=0
local integer nwv
local integer Vcv
if true then
set VLe=bj_ascii
set VMe=StringLength(VLe)
endif
set nwv=0
loop
exitwhen nwv>Vpe
set Vme=SubString(iwv,nwv,nwv+1)
set Vcv=0
loop
exitwhen Vcv>VMe
if(Vme==SubString(VLe,Vcv,Vcv+1))then
set VCe=VCe+(Vcv*nwv)
endif
set Vcv=Vcv+1
endloop
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
call TriggerSleepAction(.01)
return VCe
endfunction
function VPe takes string Vce,string ID returns string
local string Vqe=""
local string VQe=""
local string VMv=""
local integer Vse=GetRandomInt(0,$A2C2A)
local integer VSe=StringLength(Vce)
local integer nwv=0
loop
exitwhen nwv>=VSe
set VMv=VBe(ModuloInteger(VDe(SubString(Vce,nwv,nwv+1))+Vse+nwv,Ov))
if(StringLength(VMv)>0)then
set Vqe=Vqe+VMv
else
set Vqe=Vqe+SubString(Vv,0,1)
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
if(ModuloInteger(nwv,'d')==0)then
call TriggerSleepAction(.01)
endif
endloop
set VQe=VBe(Vse+Vle(ID)+Vle(Hv)+Jv)
loop
exitwhen StringLength(VQe)>=3
set VQe="A"+VQe
endloop
return VQe+Vqe
endfunction
function Vte takes string Vce,string ID returns string
local string Vqe=""
local string VMv=""
local integer Vse=VDe(SubString(Vce,0,3))-Vle(ID)-Vle(Hv)-Jv
local integer VSe=StringLength(Vce)-3
local integer nwv=0
loop
exitwhen nwv>=VSe
set VMv=VBe(ModuloInteger(VDe(SubString(Vce,nwv+3,nwv+4))-Vse-nwv,Ov))
if(StringLength(VMv)>0)then
set Vqe=Vqe+VMv
else
set Vqe=Vqe+SubString(Vv,0,1)
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
if(ModuloInteger(nwv,'d')==0)then
call TriggerSleepAction(.01)
endif
endloop
return Vqe
endfunction

endloop
return false
endfunction

function VWe takes string Vce returns string
local string VCe=""
local string Vye="|cff8080FF"
local string VYe="|cff75E975"
local string Vze="|cffFF8000"
local string VZe="|cffFEFE7F"
local string V_e
local boolean V0e=false
local boolean V1e=false
local boolean V2e=false
local boolean V3e=false
local integer nwv
set nwv=0
loop
exitwhen nwv>StringLength(Vce)
set V_e=SubString(Vce,nwv,nwv+1)
if(VTe(V_e))then
if(V3e)then
set VCe=VCe+V_e
else
set VCe=VCe+VZe+V_e
endif
set V3e=true
set V2e=false
set V0e=false
set V1e=false
endif
if(Vue(V_e))then
if(V2e)then
set VCe=VCe+V_e
else
set VCe=VCe+Vze+V_e
endif
set V3e=false
set V2e=true
set V0e=false
set V1e=false
endif
if(VUe(V_e))then
if(V0e)then
set VCe=VCe+V_e
else
set VCe=VCe+Vye+V_e
endif
set V3e=false
set V2e=false
set V0e=true
set V1e=false
endif
if(Vwe(V_e))then
if(V1e)then
set VCe=VCe+V_e
else
set VCe=VCe+VYe+V_e
endif
set V3e=false
set V2e=false
set V0e=false
set V1e=true
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
set VCe=VCe+"|r"
return VCe
endfunction
function V4e takes integer V5e,string V6e,integer V7e returns string
local integer i=1
local string V8e=""
loop
set V8e=LoadStr(Pe,V5e,i)
if V8e==null then
return V6e
elseif V8e==V6e then
call SaveStr(Pe,V5e,i,"")
return V6e
endif
exitwhen i==6
set i=i+1
endloop
set V8e=LoadStr(Pe,V5e,V7e)
return V8e+" →"+V6e
endfunction
function V9e takes integer V5e returns nothing

loop
set V8e=LoadStr(Pe,V5e,i)
call SaveStr(Pe,V5e,j,V8e)
exitwhen i==$C
set i=i+1
set j=j+1
endloop
endfunction

function XUe takes nothing returns nothing

"+VWe(Xwe))
endif
call FlushChildHashtable(vo,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
set t=null
set p=null
endfunction

function XYe takes integer nwv returns boolean
if(nwv==eo)or(nwv==me)or(nwv==Me)or(nwv==ue)or(nwv==Ue)or(nwv==bx)or(nwv==Xx)or(nwv==Nx)or(nwv==Rx)or(nwv==Ax)or(nwv==Ix)or(nwv==cx)or(nwv==Bx)or(nwv==fx)or(nwv==Cx)or(nwv==Dx)or(nwv==gx)or(nwv==Fx)or(nwv==Gx)or(nwv==hx)or(nwv==Ox)or(nwv==jx)or(nwv==Hx)or(nwv==Jx)or(nwv==kx)or(nwv==jv)then
return true
else
return false
endif
endfunction
function Xze takes nothing returns nothing
local integer nwv
set Kv=InitHashtable()
set nwv=1
loop
exitwhen nwv>8192

call SaveInteger(Kv,0,kv[nwv],nwv)
endif

call TriggerSleepAction(.01)
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
call SaveInteger(Kv,0,0,0)
endfunction

endfunction
function Ooe takes unit Vev,string i6v,integer Ore,real nYv,real n4v,real Oie,real Oae,real One,integer Oee,real nmv,integer OVe,integer OEe,integer OXe,boolean OOe returns nothing

endif

set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
if(Vhe(Obe[Cx])!=0)then
set Obe[Cx]=VBe(Vhe(Obe[Cx]))
else
set OBe[Cx]=0
endif
set Obe[Dx]=null
set nwv=421
set OJe=1
loop
exitwhen(nwv>Ev)or(OJe>30)

set OJe=OJe+1

else
set OBe[Dx]=0

endif
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
set Obe[eo]=VBe(Vhe(Obe[eo]))
call TriggerSleepAction(.01)
set nwv=1
loop
exitwhen nwv>Ev
if(OBe[nwv]==1)and(nwv!=jv)then
set OCe=OCe+(ModuloInteger(VDe(Obe[nwv]),R2I(Pow(Ov,2)))*(ModuloInteger(nwv,5)+1))
endif
if(ModuloInteger(nwv,'d')==0)then
call TriggerSleepAction(.01)
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
if(Jv>999)then
set OCe=OCe+ModuloInteger(Jv,$3E8)
else
set OCe=OCe+Jv
endif
set OCe=OCe+Vle(Hv)
set OCe=OCe+Vle(Rr[ilv])
set Obe[jv]=VBe(OCe)
call TriggerSleepAction(.01)
set nwv=1
loop
exitwhen nwv>Ev
if(OBe[nwv]==1)then
set Obe[nwv]=VHe(Obe[nwv],Xv[nwv])
set VCe=VCe+Obe[nwv]
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
call TriggerSleepAction(.01)
set VCe=VPe(VCe,Rr[ilv])
set Oje=StringLength(VCe)/ $7F
if(Oje+1==R2I(Oje)+1)then
set OJe=R2I(Oje)
else
set OJe=R2I(Oje)+1
endif
set nwv=1
loop
exitwhen OJe<0
if(StringLength(VCe)<$7F)then
set Xwe[nwv]=SubString(VCe,0,StringLength(VCe))

set Xwe[nwv]=SubString(VCe,0,$7F)
endif
set VCe=SubString(VCe,$7F,StringLength(VCe))
set nwv=nwv+1
set OJe=OJe-1
endloop
call TriggerSleepAction(.01)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(Ode,0),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(Ode,1),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(Ode,2),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(Ode,3),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(Ode,4),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(Ode,5),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(ODe,0),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(ODe,1),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(ODe,2),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(ODe,3),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(ODe,4),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(ODe,5),p,false)

call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(Ofe,2),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(Ofe,3),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(Ofe,4),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(Ofe,5),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(OFe,0),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(OFe,1),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(OFe,2),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(OFe,3),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(OFe,4),p,false)
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlot(OFe,5),p,false)
set nwv=1
loop
exitwhen nwv>30
call Xye(p,Xwe[nwv],nwv)
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
call TriggerSleepAction(.01)
set nwv=1
loop
exitwhen nwv>Ev
if(Oce[nwv]!=null)then
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(p),nwv,Oce[nwv])
else
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(p),nwv,"0")
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
set nwv=1
loop
exitwhen nwv>30
if(Xwe[nwv]!=null)then
call SaveStr(Zx,GetHandleId(p),nwv,Xwe[nwv])
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
call Eve(p,Eee,I2S(GetUnitLevel(Ode)))
set Ye[ilv]=false
set Ode=null
set ODe=null
set Ofe=null
set OFe=null
set Oge=null
set OGe=null
endfunction

endif
set Qe[ilv]=Vte(Qe[ilv],Rr[ilv])
set Ohe=0

loop
exitwhen nwv>Ev
if(OBe[nwv]==1)then
set Obe[nwv]=VDe(SubString(Qe[ilv],Ohe,Ohe+Xv[nwv]))
if(nwv==jv)then
set Ome=VDe(SubString(Qe[ilv],Ohe,Ohe+Xv[nwv]))
endif
set Ohe=Ohe+Xv[nwv]
endif
if(ModuloInteger(nwv,'d')==0)then
call TriggerSleepAction(.01)
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
call TriggerSleepAction(.01)
set Ohe=0
set OHe=0
set nwv=1
loop
exitwhen nwv>Ev
if(OBe[nwv]==1)and(nwv!=jv)then
set OCe=OCe+(ModuloInteger(Obe[nwv],R2I(Pow(Ov,2)))*(ModuloInteger(nwv,5)+1))
endif
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
if(Jv>999)then
set OCe=OCe+ModuloInteger(Jv,$3E8)
else
set OCe=OCe+Jv
endif
set OCe=OCe+Vle(Hv)
set OCe=OCe+Vle(Rr[ilv])
if(OCe!=Ome)then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,.0,.0,10.,"|cffFF0202Error) |c00DFFB4F아이디가 다르거나 코드가 틀립니다.|r")
set qe[ilv]=false
set ze[ilv]=false
return false
endif
if Obe['k']>0 and not(HaveSavedInteger(w,(Obe['k']),$633009F5))then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,.0,.0,10.,"|cffFF0202Error) |c00DFFB4F잘못된 유닛 타입입니다.|r")
set qe[ilv]=false
set ze[ilv]=false
return false
endif
if(Obe[Av]!=0 and kv[Obe[Av]]==0)or(Obe[bv]!=0 and kv[Obe[bv]]==0)or(Obe[Nv]!=0 and kv[Obe[Nv]]==0)or(Obe[Cv]!=0 and kv[Obe[Cv]]==0)or(Obe[Bv]!=0 and kv[Obe[Bv]]==0)or(Obe[cv]!=0 and kv[Obe[cv]]==0)then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,.0,.0,10.,"|cffFF0202Error) |c00DFFB4F잘못된 아이템 타입입니다.|r")
set qe[ilv]=false
set ze[ilv]=false
return false
endif
if(Obe[xe]!=0 and kv[Obe[xe]]==0)or(Obe[re]!=0 and kv[Obe[re]]==0)or(Obe[oe]!=0 and kv[Obe[oe]]==0)or(Obe[ae]!=0 and kv[Obe[ae]]==0)or(Obe[ie]!=0 and kv[Obe[ie]]==0)or(Obe[ne]!=0 and kv[Obe[ne]]==0)then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,.0,.0,10.,"|cffFF0202Error) |c00DFFB4F잘못된 아이템 타입입니다.|r")
set qe[ilv]=false
set ze[ilv]=false
return false
endif
if(Obe[ao]!=0 and kv[Obe[ao]]==0)or(Obe[no]!=0 and kv[Obe[no]]==0)or(Obe[Vo]!=0 and kv[Obe[Vo]]==0)or(Obe[Eo]!=0 and kv[Obe[Eo]]==0)or(Obe[Xo]!=0 and kv[Obe[Xo]]==0)or(Obe[Oo]!=0 and kv[Obe[Oo]]==0)then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,.0,.0,10.,"|cffFF0202Error) |c00DFFB4F잘못된 아이템 타입입니다.|r")
set qe[ilv]=false
set ze[ilv]=false
return false
endif
if(Obe[bo]!=0 and kv[Obe[bo]]==0)or(Obe[Bo]!=0 and kv[Obe[Bo]]==0)or(Obe[co]!=0 and kv[Obe[co]]==0)or(Obe[Co]!=0 and kv[Obe[Co]]==0)or(Obe[do]!=0 and kv[Obe[do]]==0)or(Obe[Do]!=0 and kv[Obe[Do]]==0)then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,.0,.0,10.,"|cffFF0202Error) |c00DFFB4F잘못된 아이템 타입입니다.|r")
set qe[ilv]=false
set ze[ilv]=false
return false
endif
if(Obe[Ia]!=0 and kv[Obe[Ia]]==0)or(Obe[Aa]!=0 and kv[Obe[Aa]]==0)or(Obe[Na]!=0 and kv[Obe[Na]]==0)or(Obe[ba]!=0 and kv[Obe[ba]]==0)or(Obe[Ba]!=0 and kv[Obe[Ba]]==0)or(Obe[ca]!=0 and kv[Obe[ca]]==0)then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,.0,.0,10.,"|cffFF0202Error) |c00DFFB4F잘못된 아이템 타입입니다.|r")
set qe[ilv]=false
set ze[ilv]=false
return false
endif
if(Obe[uE]!=0 and kv[Obe[uE]]==0)or(Obe[UE]!=0 and kv[Obe[UE]]==0)or(Obe[wE]!=0 and kv[Obe[wE]]==0)or(Obe[WE]!=0 and kv[Obe[WE]]==0)or(Obe[yE]!=0 and kv[Obe[yE]]==0)or(Obe[YE]!=0 and kv[Obe[YE]]==0)then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,.0,.0,10.,"|cffFF0202Error) |c00DFFB4F잘못된 아이템 타입입니다.|r")
set qe[ilv]=false
set ze[ilv]=false
return false
endif
set nwv=1
loop
exitwhen nwv>Ev
call SaveInteger(vx,ilv,nwv,Obe[nwv])
set nwv=nwv+1
endloop
call PanCameraToTimedForPlayer(p,GetLocationX(GetStartLocationLoc(GetPlayerStartLocation(p))),GetLocationY(GetStartLocationLoc(GetPlayerStartLocation(p))),.5)
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,.0,.0,10.,"|c00DFFB4F로드 완료!|r")
set ze[ilv]=false
set qe[ilv]=false
return true
endfunction
function OMe takes integer Ope,real iqv,integer Vkv returns nothing
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetKillingUnit())
local integer i=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local item OPe
if GetUnitTypeId(GetTriggerUnit())==Vkv and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[i]*GH[i-1]then
set OPe=CreateItem(Ope,GetUnitX(GetTriggerUnit()),GetUnitY(GetTriggerUnit()))
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')>=5 then
call SetItemPlayer(OPe,p,true)
endif
set OPe=null
endif
endfunction
function Oqe takes integer Ope,real iqv,integer Vkv returns nothing
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetKillingUnit())
local integer i=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
if GetUnitTypeId(GetTriggerUnit())==Vkv and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[i]*GH[i-1]then
call SetItemPlayer(CreateItem(Ope,GetUnitX(GetTriggerUnit()),GetUnitY(GetTriggerUnit())),p,true)
endif
set p=null
endfunction
function OQe takes unit u,integer a returns nothing
local integer i=0
local integer aev=1
loop
exitwhen aev==0
if(BlzBitAnd((a),(aev)))!=0 then
call UnitAddAbility(u,Oi[i])
call UnitMakeAbilityPermanent(u,true,Oi[i])
else
call UnitRemoveAbility(u,Oi[i])
endif
set aev=aev*2
set i=i+1
endloop
endfunction
function Ose takes unit u,integer a returns nothing
local integer i=0
local integer aev=1
loop
exitwhen aev==0
if(BlzBitAnd((a),(aev)))!=0 then
call UnitAddAbility(u,Xi[i])
call UnitMakeAbilityPermanent(u,true,Xi[i])
else
call UnitRemoveAbility(u,Xi[i])
endif
set aev=aev*2
set i=i+1
endloop
endfunction
function OSe takes unit u,integer a returns nothing
local integer i=0
local integer aev=1
loop
exitwhen aev==0 or i>23
if(BlzBitAnd((a),(aev)))!=0 then
call UnitAddAbility(u,ta[i])
call UnitMakeAbilityPermanent(u,true,ta[i])
else
call UnitRemoveAbility(u,ta[i])
endif
set aev=aev*2
set i=i+1
endloop
endfunction
function Ote takes nothing returns nothing
call TriggerExecute(bd)
call TriggerExecute(Bd)
call TriggerExecute(cd)
call TriggerExecute(Cd)
call TriggerExecute(dd)
call TriggerExecute(fd)
call TriggerExecute(Fd)
call TriggerExecute(gd)
call TriggerExecute(Gd)
call TriggerExecute(hd)
call TriggerExecute(jd)
call ExecuteFunc("OTe")
endfunction

endfunction

function RXe takes nothing returns nothing
local integer nwv=0
local player p
local real iqv
local integer ROe=0
loop
set p=Player(nwv)
set nwv=nwv+1
if GetPlayerController(p)==MAP_CONTROL_USER and GetPlayerSlotState(p)==PLAYER_SLOT_STATE_PLAYING then
set ROe=ROe+1
endif
exitwhen nwv==$A
endloop
set p=null
set iqv=ROe*.05
if iqv>.25 then
set iqv=.25
endif
set iqv=iqv+1
set nwv=0
loop
set nwv=nwv+1
set gi[nwv]=gi[nwv]+iqv
exitwhen nwv==$A
endloop
set ROe=ROe-nv
set Fi=ROe
set Xn=Xn-ROe*90.
set dj=1.2
if ROe>=4 then
set wn=true
set hH=false
set HH=false
set nwv=0
loop
set nwv=nwv+1
if HH then
set gi[nwv]=gi[nwv]+.2
else
set gi[nwv]=gi[nwv]+.1
endif
set jH=true
exitwhen nwv==8
endloop
endif
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFF9932CC랜덤 박스 획득은 12시간동안 지속됩니다.|R")
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFF9932CC랜덤 박스 획득은 12시간동안 지속됩니다.|R")
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"현재 플레이 인원수는 "+I2S(ROe)+"명 입니다.  드랍률 및 강화 확률이 |CFFFF0000"+I2S(ROe*2)+"|R % 증가합니다.")
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"현재 플레이 인원수는 "+I2S(ROe)+"명 입니다.  랜덤 상자 등장 시간이 |CFFFF0000"+I2S(ROe*90)+"|R초 감소합니다.")
if HH then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0," ")
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFF9932CC일정 인원수 이상으로 추가효과가 적용됩니다.|R")
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFF9932CC일정 인원수 이상으로 추가효과가 적용됩니다.|R")
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFFFF0000추가확률 10% 증가, 보스 이벤트 적용 적용됩니다.|R")
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFFFF0000추가확률 10% 증가, 보스 이벤트 적용 적용됩니다.|R")
endif
if ROe>=5 then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFFFF0000모든 플레이어에게 공격속도 150% 증가가 적용됩니다.|R")
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFFFF0000모든 플레이어에게 공격속도 150% 증가가 적용됩니다.|R")
call EnableTrigger(Zc)
endif
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFF70F170게임 저장시 반드시 리플레이를 저장해주세요!!

리플레이는 http://cafe.naver.com/scvrpg 올려주셔야

불이익을 당하지 않습니다!!

또한 리플레이를 올리지 않으신분은 제제를 먹으실수도있습니다..")
set Qa=ROe*.02
endfunction
function RRe takes nothing returns nothing
local integer RIe=(1+GetPlayerId((Y)))
local integer nwv=0
local player p
local integer ROe=0
loop
set p=Player(nwv)
set nwv=nwv+1
if GetPlayerController(p)==MAP_CONTROL_USER and GetPlayerSlotState(p)==PLAYER_SLOT_STATE_PLAYING then
set ROe=ROe+1
endif
exitwhen nwv==$A
endloop
if ROe>1 and jH then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,"|CFF0080FF호스트 플레이어|r인 |CFF0080FF"+Rr[RIe]+"|r님의 확률이 |CFFFF00006%|r 추가로 증가합니다.|R")
set gi[RIe]=gi[RIe]+.06
endif
endfunction

function Rce takes nothing returns nothing

call CreateTimerDialogBJ(bj_lastStartedTimer,"랜덤 상자 획득까지")
call StartTimerBJ(Rn,true,720.)
call CreateTimerDialogBJ(bj_lastStartedTimer,"1단계 에피소드 등장")
set tr=bj_lastCreatedTimerDialog
set In=1
if(RBe())then
call StartTimerBJ(Tn,true,1800.)
call CreateTimerDialogBJ(bj_lastStartedTimer,"겨울방학 선물 획득까지..")
set un=bj_lastCreatedTimerDialog
endif
set KX[1]=RH
set KX[2]=IH
set KX[3]=AH
set KX[4]=NH
set KX[5]=bH
set KX[6]=BH
set KX[7]=cH
set KX[8]=CH
set KX[9]=DH
set KX[$A]=dH
endfunction

function AGe takes nothing returns boolean
return(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="scvscvgo")
endfunction
function Ahe takes nothing returns nothing
call AddSpecialEffectTargetUnitBJ("overhead",hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))],"GlobalDonate_nisekr_1.mdl")
endfunction
function Aje takes nothing returns boolean
return(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="scvscvgo")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="nisekr")
endfunction
function AJe takes nothing returns boolean
return(Aje())
endfunction
function Ake takes nothing returns nothing
call StopMusic(false)
call ClearMapMusic()
call PlayMusicBJ(SB)
endfunction
function Ale takes nothing returns boolean
return(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="scvscvgo")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="nisekr")
endfunction
function ALe takes nothing returns boolean
return(Ale())
endfunction
function Ame takes nothing returns nothing
call StopMusic(false)
call ClearMapMusic()
endfunction
function Ape takes nothing returns nothing
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=8
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
call DisplayTextToForce(bj_FORCE_ALL_PLAYERS,Rr[bj_forLoopAIndex])
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
endfunction
function Aqe takes nothing returns nothing
local unit u=GetEnumUnit()
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(u)))
call SetUnitPosition(u,GetUnitX(hv[ilv]),GetUnitY(hv[ilv]))
call IssuePointOrderById(u,$D000F,GetUnitX(u),GetUnitY(u))
set u=null
endfunction
function AQe takes nothing returns nothing
call RemoveUnit(GetEnumUnit())
endfunction
function Ase takes integer RIe returns nothing
local real x=GetUnitX(hv[RIe])
local real y=GetUnitY(hv[RIe])
if Xa[RIe]!=null then
call SetUnitPosition(Xa[RIe],x,y)
call IssueTargetOrderById(Xa[RIe],$D0012,hv[RIe])
endif
if ia[RIe]!=null then
call SetUnitPosition(ia[RIe],x,y)
call IssuePointOrderById(ia[RIe],$D000F,x,y)
endif
if DV[RIe]!=null then
call SetUnitPosition(DV[RIe],x,y)
call IssuePointOrderById(DV[RIe],$D000F,x,y)
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(hv[RIe],'A0RE')>0 then
call ForGroup(xX[RIe],function Aqe)
endif
if dO[RIe]!=null then
call SetUnitPosition(dO[RIe],x,y)
call IssuePointOrderById(dO[RIe],$D000F,x,y)
endif
endfunction
function ASe takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local real x=GetStartLocationX(GetPlayerStartLocation(p))
local real y=GetStartLocationY(GetPlayerStartLocation(p))
call SetUnitPosition(hv[ilv],x,y)
call PanCameraToTimedForPlayer(p,x,y,0)
call Ase(ilv)
endfunction
function ATe takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
call SetUnitPositionLoc(hv[ilv],nr[ilv])
call PanCameraToTimedLocForPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),nr[ilv],0)
call Ase(ilv)
endfunction
function AUe takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
local integer Awe=GetHeroInt(hv[ilv],false)
local location l=null
if Awe>=$EC82E0 then
set l=sO[ilv]
elseif Awe>=$1E8480 then
set l=sE[ilv]
elseif Awe>=$186A0 then
set l=Wi[ilv]
endif
if l!=null then
call SetUnitPositionLoc(hv[ilv],l)
call PanCameraToTimedLocForPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),l,0)
call Ase(ilv)
set l=null
endif
endfunction
function Aye takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
local integer Awe=GetHeroInt(hv[ilv],false)
local location l=null
if Awe>=$4C4B40 then
set l=pX[ilv]
elseif Awe>=$7A120 then
set l=Pn[ilv]
endif
if l!=null then
call SetUnitPositionLoc(hv[ilv],l)
call PanCameraToTimedLocForPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),l,0)
call Ase(ilv)
set l=null
endif
endfunction
function Aze takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local real x=GetRectCenterX(DI)
local real y=GetRectCenterY(DI)
call SetUnitPosition(hv[ilv],x,y)
call PanCameraToTimedForPlayer(p,x,y,0)
call Ase(ilv)
endfunction
function A_e takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
if RectContainsUnit(RI,hv[ilv])then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),0,0,"|CFFFF0000마을에서는 저장할 수 없습니다.|R")
else
call RemoveLocation(aE[ilv])
set aE[ilv]=GetUnitLoc(hv[ilv])
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),0,0,"|CFFFF0000위치가 저장됐습니다.|R")
endif
endfunction
function A1e takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
local location l=aE[ilv]
if l!=null then
call SetUnitPositionLoc(hv[ilv],aE[ilv])
call PanCameraToTimedLocForPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),aE[ilv],0)
call Ase(ilv)
endif
set l=null
endfunction
function A3e takes unit u,string i6v,integer nKv returns nothing
local integer Vfe=StringLength(i6v)
local real aov
if Vfe>nKv then
set aov=S2R(SubString(i6v,nKv,Vfe))
if 0<=aov and aov<=$A then
call SetUnitScale(u,aov,aov,aov)
endif
endif
endfunction
function A4e takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
local integer Vfe
local string i6v
local real aov
if hv[ilv]!=null and U[ilv]>0 then
set i6v=GetEventPlayerChatString()
set Vfe=StringLength(i6v)
if Vfe>$F then
set aov=S2R(SubString(i6v,$F,Vfe))
if 0<=aov and aov<=$A then
call SetUnitScale(hv[ilv],aov,aov,aov)
set KH[ilv]=aov
endif
endif
endif
endfunction
function A5e takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
if TH[ilv]!=null then
call A3e(TH[ilv],GetEventPlayerChatString(),$C)
endif
endfunction
function A6e takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
if uv[ilv]!=null and GetUnitTypeId(uv[ilv])!=('����'+'zH+') then
call A3e(uv[ilv],GetEventPlayerChatString(),16)
endif
endfunction
function A7e takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
if Io[ilv]!=null and GetUnitTypeId(Io[ilv])!=('mX��'+'��|h') then
call A3e(Io[ilv],GetEventPlayerChatString(),16)
endif
endfunction
function A8e takes player p returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
if lH[ilv]>0 and LH[ilv]>0 and mH[ilv]>0 then
call SetUnitVertexColor(hv[ilv],lH[ilv],LH[ilv],mH[ilv],$FF)
endif
endfunction
function A9e takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
local integer Vfe
local string i6v
local integer Nve
if hv[ilv]!=null and U[ilv]>0 then
set i6v=GetEventPlayerChatString()
set Vfe=StringLength(i6v)
if Vfe>5 then
set Nve=S2I(SubString(i6v,5,Vfe))
if Nve<0 then
set Nve=0
elseif $FF<Nve then
set Nve=$FF
endif
call SetUnitVertexColor(hv[ilv],Nve,LH[ilv],mH[ilv],$FF)
set lH[ilv]=Nve
endif
endif
endfunction
function Nee takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
local integer Vfe
local string i6v
local integer Nve
if hv[ilv]!=null and U[ilv]>0 then
set i6v=GetEventPlayerChatString()
set Vfe=StringLength(i6v)
if Vfe>5 then
set Nve=S2I(SubString(i6v,5,Vfe))
if Nve<0 then
set Nve=0
elseif $FF<Nve then
set Nve=$FF

endif
endif
endfunction
function Nxe takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
local integer Vfe
local string i6v
local integer Nve
if hv[ilv]!=null and U[ilv]>0 then
set i6v=GetEventPlayerChatString()
set Vfe=StringLength(i6v)
if Vfe>5 then
set Nve=S2I(SubString(i6v,5,Vfe))
if Nve<0 then
set Nve=0
elseif $FF<Nve then
set Nve=$FF
endif
call SetUnitVertexColor(hv[ilv],lH[ilv],LH[ilv],Nve,$FF)
set mH[ilv]=Nve
endif
endif
endfunction
function Noe takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
local integer Vfe
local string i6v
local integer r
local integer g
local integer b
if hv[ilv]!=null and U[ilv]>0 then
set i6v=GetEventPlayerChatString()
set Vfe=StringLength(i6v)
if Vfe>7 then
set b=S2I(SubString(i6v,7,Vfe))
if b<0 then
set b=0
elseif $FFFFFF<b then
set b=$FFFFFF
endif
set g=b/ 256
set r=g/ 256
set g=g-r*256
set b=b-g*256
call SetUnitVertexColor(hv[ilv],r,g,b,$FF)
set lH[ilv]=r
set LH[ilv]=g
set mH[ilv]=b
endif
endif
endfunction
function Nre takes nothing returns boolean
return(ir[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]>=1)
endfunction
function Nie takes nothing returns nothing

function N_e takes nothing returns boolean
return(fr[bj_forLoopAIndex]>=60)
endfunction
function N0e takes nothing returns boolean
return(Nr[bj_forLoopAIndex]>=60)
endfunction
function N1e takes nothing returns boolean
return(GetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0VZ',hv[bj_forLoopAIndex])>0)
endfunction
function N2e takes nothing returns nothing
local location IQe
local location Ise
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=$A
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
set Hr[bj_forLoopAIndex]=(Hr[bj_forLoopAIndex]+1)
set fr[bj_forLoopAIndex]=(fr[bj_forLoopAIndex]+1)
if(N_e())then
set Nr[bj_forLoopAIndex]=(Nr[bj_forLoopAIndex]+1)
set Gr[bj_forLoopAIndex]=(Gr[bj_forLoopAIndex]+1)
set fr[bj_forLoopAIndex]=0
endif
if(N0e())then
set Fr[bj_forLoopAIndex]=(Fr[bj_forLoopAIndex]+1)
set Nr[bj_forLoopAIndex]=0
endif
if(N1e())then
set IQe=GetUnitLoc(hv[bj_forLoopAIndex])
set Ise=GetUnitLoc(dO[bj_forLoopAIndex])
if DistanceBetweenPoints(IQe,Ise)>700 then
call SetUnitPositionLoc(dO[bj_forLoopAIndex],(IQe))
endif
call RemoveLocation((IQe))
call RemoveLocation((Ise))
endif
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
set IQe=null
set Ise=null
endfunction
function N4e takes nothing returns nothing
call IssueImmediateOrderById(GetEnumUnit(),$D0228)
endfunction
function N5e takes nothing returns nothing
local group g=CreateGroup()
call GroupEnumUnitsInRect(g,dI,null)
call ForGroup(g,function N4e)
call GroupEnumUnitsInRect(g,sI,null)
call ForGroup(g,function N4e)
call GroupEnumUnitsInRect(g,eA,null)
call ForGroup(g,function N4e)
call DestroyGroup(g)
set g=null
endfunction

function bOe takes nothing returns nothing
call EXv(0)
if(boe())then
call zZv(vv,0,0)
call zZv(vv,1,0)
if(bxe())then
else
call zZv(vv,$F,GetRandomInt(1,5))
if(N7e())then
call DisplayTextToForce(bj_FORCE_ALL_PLAYERS,"1|CFFF06464-자동세이브 또는 -asave  입력시 5분주기로 자동으로 세이브 합니다.|R")
endif
if(N8e())then
call DisplayTextToForce(bj_FORCE_ALL_PLAYERS,"1|CFFF06464-강화시 세이브가 자동으로 됩니다. 아이템 분실을 조심해주세요|R")
endif
if(N9e())then
call DisplayTextToForce(bj_FORCE_ALL_PLAYERS,"1|CFFF06464-코드 롤백은 불가능합니다. 장비를 바닥에 버린후 세이브하신지 확인하세요|R")
endif
if(bve())then
call DisplayTextToForce(bj_FORCE_ALL_PLAYERS,"1|CFFF06464-공식까페 : https://cafe.naver.com/scvrpg (검색어 : 강화의노예)|R")
endif
if(bee())then
call DisplayTextToForce(bj_FORCE_ALL_PLAYERS,"1|CFFF06464-사용자 검색 및 공식 사이트 : https://m16tool.xyz/Game/UPR|R")
endif
endif
call EVv(vv,.03)
endif
if(bae())then
call zZv(vv,0,(s2[vv]+1))
call QHv(vv,0,GetUnitLoc(uv[s2[vv]]))
if(bie())then
set bn[s2[vv]]=RectFromCenterSizeBJ(Jz[vv],Yn[s2[vv]],Yn[s2[vv]])
call EnumItemsInRectBJ(bn[s2[vv]],function bre)
call RemoveRect(bn[s2[vv]])
endif
call EVv(vv,.03)
endif
if(bEe())then
call zZv(vv,1,(S2[vv]+1))
call QHv(vv,1,GetUnitLoc(Io[S2[vv]]))
if(bVe())then
set bn[S2[vv]]=RectFromCenterSizeBJ(kz[vv],Yn[S2[vv]],Yn[S2[vv]])
call EnumItemsInRectBJ(bn[S2[vv]],function bne)
call RemoveRect(bn[S2[vv]])
endif
call EVv(vv,.03)
endif
if(bXe())then
call V9v(vv)
endif
endfunction

function bbe takes player p returns real

local string iwv=Rr[ilv]
local integer bBe=0
local boolean bce=true
local real iqv=0
local integer i
if iwv=="kasha" or iwv=="dkdk100" or iwv=="sinlove12" or iwv=="z-2" or iwv=="clover6104" or iwv=="ATAL" or iwv=="kkb6571" or iwv=="kind0505" or iwv=="EbiyaGukiZzada" or iwv=="Hipo" or iwv=="signum" or iwv=="doffl0809" or iwv=="bbbb1229" or iwv=="et97" or iwv=="" or iwv=="ytk7251" or iwv=="sss124" or iwv=="" or iwv=="Wind.." or iwv=="sex12123" or iwv=="SHAKI" or iwv=="Gsik" or iwv=="RascaI#3740" or iwv=="LoneIy#31932" or iwv=="Xhide" or iwv=="spia" or iwv=="어린나무#3252" or iwv=="Rony#3697" or iwv=="" then
