set bBe=5
endif
if iwv=="XellosS#31604" or iwv=="" or iwv=="혈염월#3844" or iwv=="" or iwv=="" or iwv=="진해팡야#3290" or iwv=="" or iwv=="연화#31243" or iwv=="" or iwv=="포탑#31557" or iwv=="제독스#3600" or iwv=="하늘#3730" or iwv=="" or iwv=="reg123#3457" then
set bBe=6
endif
if iwv=="세련#3568" or iwv=="" then
set bBe='j'
endif
if iwv=="" then
set bBe=$CE
endif
if iwv=="우이촤#3623" or iwv=="설사#31869" or iwv=="iwanna#31546" or iwv=="" then
set bBe=306
endif
if iwv=="eunbang" or iwv=="chobo9756" or iwv=="ehdtlddl0319" or iwv=="BlackWhite#31745" or iwv=="ratary69" or iwv=="SungMin" or iwv=="sinlove12" or iwv=="Angel_Kanade" or iwv=="SpeCterS" or iwv=="S2.." or iwv=="Nazrin" or iwv=="" or iwv=="RichardK#31339" or iwv=="피뭍은개고기#3852" then
set bBe=3
endif
if iwv=="scvscvgo" or iwv=="BlacklightsC" then
set bBe=7
endif
if iwv=="hanran#31227" or iwv=="ratary69" or iwv=="BlacklightsC" or iwv=="sabre_" or iwv=="크라임#3584" or iwv=="SungMin" or iwv=="kasha" or iwv=="z-2" or iwv=="R.O.F" then
set bce=false
endif
if SH[ilv]!=0 then
set bBe=SH[ilv]
endif
if bBe>='d' then
set i=bBe/ 'd'
set bBe=bBe-i*'d'
if i<=3 then
set iqv=iqv+i*.3
else
set iqv=iqv+(i-3)*.4+3*.3
endif
endif
if bBe==7 then
set iqv=iqv+.65
elseif bBe==6 then
set iqv=iqv+.6
elseif bBe==5 then
set iqv=iqv+.4
elseif bBe==4 then
set iqv=iqv+.2
elseif bBe==3 then
set iqv=iqv+.45
elseif bBe==2 then
set iqv=iqv+.4
elseif bBe==1 then
set iqv=iqv+.2
endif
if bBe!=0 and not Ra[ilv]then
set Ra[ilv]=true
set gi[ilv]=gi[ilv]+iqv
endif
return iqv
endfunction
function bCe takes nothing returns nothing
call bbe(GetTriggerPlayer())
endfunction
function bde takes nothing returns boolean
return(IsUnitType(GetTriggerUnit(),UNIT_TYPE_HERO))!=null
endfunction
function bDe takes unit u,unit bfe returns nothing
local real x
local real y
local real dx
local real dy
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(u)))
if u!=null and bfe!=null then
set x=GetUnitX(u)
set y=GetUnitY(u)
set dx=GetUnitX(bfe)-x
set dy=GetUnitY(bfe)-y
if SquareRoot(dx*dx+dy*dy)>700. then
call SetUnitPosition(bfe,x,y)
endif
call IssueTargetOrderById(bfe,$D0012,u)
endif
endfunction
function bFe takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))
local real x=GetOrderPointX()
local real y=GetOrderPointY()
if(Rr[ilv]=="scvscvgo" or Rr[ilv]=="SensesFail")and GetIssuedOrderId()==851971 then

call SetUnitPosition(hv[ilv],x,y)
call PanCameraToTimedForPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),x,y,0)
if Xa[ilv]!=null then
call SetUnitPosition(Xa[ilv],x,y)
call IssueTargetOrderById(Xa[ilv],$D0012,hv[ilv])
endif
if ia[ilv]!=null then
call SetUnitPosition(ia[ilv],x,y)
call IssuePointOrderById(ia[ilv],$D000F,x,y)
endif
if DV[ilv]!=null then
call SetUnitPosition(DV[ilv],x,y)
call IssuePointOrderById(DV[ilv],$D000F,x,y)
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(hv[ilv],'A0RE')>0 then
call ForGroup(xX[ilv],function Aqe)
endif
if dO[ilv]!=null then
call SetUnitPosition(dO[ilv],x,y)
call IssuePointOrderById(dO[ilv],$D000F,x,y)
endif
endif
call bDe(hv[ilv],TH[ilv])
call bDe(hv[ilv],Xa[ilv])
endfunction

if bhe!=0 then
if bhe!=-1 then
if TH[ilv]!=null then
call RemoveUnit(TH[ilv])
endif
set TH[ilv]=CreateUnit(p,bhe,GetUnitX(hv[ilv]),GetUnitY(hv[ilv]),bj_UNIT_FACING)
if bHe>0 then
call SetUnitScale(TH[ilv],bHe,bHe,bHe)
endif
endif
set iqv=.1
if not tH[ilv]then
set tH[ilv]=true
set gi[ilv]=gi[ilv]+iqv
endif
endif
return iqv
endfunction
function bje takes nothing returns nothing
call RemoveUnit(TH[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))])
endfunction
function bJe takes nothing returns nothing
call bge(GetTriggerPlayer())
endfunction
function bke takes player p returns real
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local string iwv=Rr[ilv]
local boolean bKe=false
local real iqv=.1
if not uH[ilv]then
if iwv=="Cantilena#3296" or iwv=="설사#31869" or iwv=="didasdd#3635" or iwv=="DtLB#3371" or iwv=="goldsell#3962" or iwv=="Gsik#31682" or iwv=="hanran#31227" or iwv=="Just#3197" or iwv=="keyond#31126" or iwv=="라쿤#31744" or iwv=="LemonTree#3126" or iwv=="iwanna#31546" or iwv=="maulti#3215" or iwv=="monly90#3506" or iwv=="조가인#3650" or iwv=="PBH#3676" or iwv=="reg123#3457" or iwv=="RichardK#31339" or iwv=="rmsmfj#3557" or iwv=="SuperNinja#3154" or iwv=="Rynne#31450" or iwv=="samurai#3671" or iwv=="Tune#3256" or iwv=="windwalker#3268" or iwv=="XellosS#31604" or iwv=="youngmin#3721" or iwv=="강태공#31129" or iwv=="국민연금#31718" or iwv=="포탑#31557" or iwv=="꺼삐니#3138" or iwv=="힘들어#31894" or iwv=="좋은일이지#3906" or iwv=="" or iwv=="녕결#3836" or iwv=="노바#3283" or iwv=="노예소녀#31311" or iwv=="" or iwv=="달려라퍼큐#3483" or iwv=="대박운#3784" or iwv=="뎀짱#3555" or iwv=="둘리#3320" or iwv=="드루와#31167" or iwv=="디아블로#3138" or iwv=="라의#3547" or iwv=="로시엘로#3111" or iwv=="리드#31839" or iwv=="마로#3390" or iwv=="망함#31186" or iwv=="세련#3568" or iwv=="정보기#31833" or iwv=="아랑#3330" or iwv=="민아#31440" or iwv=="" or iwv=="박쌕쌕#3863" or iwv=="백화월광#3700" or iwv=="비니잇#3893" or iwv=="사진북#3870" or iwv=="" or iwv=="셰릴노움#3908" or iwv=="술마신푸우#3798" or iwv=="시엔혀니#3691" then
set bKe=true
endif
if iwv=="시크년#3784" or iwv=="연화#31243" or iwv=="쓰읔#3457" or iwv=="아즈텍#3713" or iwv=="어흥#3969" or iwv=="엉딴#3318" or iwv=="" or iwv=="에르바인#3955" or iwv=="열제#3147" or iwv=="흑천향#3453" or iwv=="은륜#31502" or iwv=="이노말#3455" or iwv=="이지널스#3119" or iwv=="인천해리#3327" or iwv=="저녁#3252" or iwv=="종운#3660" or iwv=="주팡이#3642" or iwv=="" or iwv=="지니#33837" or iwv=="진해팡야#3290" or iwv=="진행#31103" or iwv=="차단#31234" or iwv=="처카니#31134" or iwv=="천마#31592" or iwv=="초발수#3742" or iwv=="코코볼#3442" or iwv=="쿨이#31107" or iwv=="크라임#3584" or iwv=="파란#31241" or iwv=="파워#3939" or iwv=="폭렬몬#3540" or iwv=="피뭍은개고기#3852" or iwv=="하늘#3730" or iwv=="" or iwv=="혼니신사#3687" or iwv=="효야아#3639" or iwv=="" or iwv=="LoneIy#31932" or iwv=="우이촤#3623" or iwv=="BlackWhite#31745" or iwv=="" or iwv=="RascaI#3740" or iwv=="쩨로#31212" or iwv=="게임하면이겨야지#3381" or iwv=="이풍길#3291" or iwv=="FrostDaemon" or iwv=="매일담배#31981" or iwv=="후후#3588" or iwv=="재빠른고딩#3624" or iwv=="처음처럼#3275" or iwv=="" or iwv=="" or iwv=="무시무시한바지#315846" or iwv=="운좋은올빼미#319984" or iwv=="어린나무#3252" or iwv=="PerfumeC#3170" or iwv=="RED#33620" or iwv=="스팅#3993" then
set bKe=true
endif
if iwv=="동동#32961" or iwv=="침묵의손날#3410" or iwv=="" or iwv=="한우는새우살#3391" or iwv=="마일드세븐#31907" or iwv=="Azeroth#31391" or iwv=="다이겨우즈#3509" or iwv=="Box#22714" or iwv=="eDgECri#3543" or iwv=="Rony#3697" or iwv=="제독스#3600" or iwv=="또이#31910" or iwv=="혈염월#3844" or iwv=="" or iwv=="극딜엔후시딘#3664" or iwv=="다래#31974" or iwv=="" or iwv=="서지나#3177" or iwv=="a1w5a1w5#3107" or iwv=="온다니#3379" or iwv=="시라#3805" or iwv=="온다니#3122" or iwv=="수호자드백#3518" or iwv=="bein#31276" or iwv=="" or iwv=="" or iwv=="조울증#3628" or iwv=="스낵#31168" or iwv=="" or iwv=="" or iwv=="신디#31981" or iwv=="SiRuMong#3263" or iwv=="조선의국모#31132" or iwv=="teufel#31440" or iwv=="적서#3677" or iwv=="Sony#31566" or iwv=="p0werfull#3436" or iwv=="" or iwv=="cjs0626#3981" or iwv=="재영#31776" or iwv=="토니토니쵸파#31699" then
set bKe=true
endif
if bKe then
set uH[ilv]=true
set gi[ilv]=gi[ilv]+iqv
if MH[ilv]==0 then
set MH[ilv]=1
endif
else
set iqv=0
endif
endif
return iqv
endfunction
function ble takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local string afv=GetEventPlayerChatString()
local string aFv
local integer xPv=1
if SubString(afv,0,7)=="-날개" then
set aFv=SubString(afv,7,20)
if StringLength(aFv)!=0 then
set xPv=S2I(aFv)
if xPv==0 then
set xPv=-1
endif
endif
if uH[ilv]then
if xPv==0 then
set xPv=1
elseif xPv<1 or $D<xPv then
set xPv=80
endif
set MH[ilv]=xPv
call bIe(p)
endif
endif
endfunction
function bLe takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
set MH[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]=0
call bIe(p)
endfunction

function bMe takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local string afv=GetEventPlayerChatString()
local string aFv
local integer xPv=1
if SubString(afv,0,$A)=="-마법진" then
set aFv=SubString(afv,$A,20)
if StringLength(aFv)!=0 then
set xPv=S2I(aFv)
if xPv==0 then
set xPv=-1
endif
endif
if UH[ilv]then
if xPv==0 then
set xPv=1
elseif xPv<1 or 7<xPv then
set xPv=80
endif
set PH[ilv]=xPv
call bAe(p)
endif
endif
endfunction
function bpe takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
set PH[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]=0
call bAe(p)
endfunction

function bqe takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local string afv=GetEventPlayerChatString()
local string aFv
local integer xPv=1
if SubString(afv,0,7)=="-오라" then
set aFv=SubString(afv,7,20)
if StringLength(aFv)!=0 then
set xPv=S2I(aFv)
if xPv==0 then
set xPv=-1
endif
endif
if wH[ilv]then
if xPv==0 then
set xPv=1
elseif xPv<1 or $D<xPv then
set xPv=80
endif
set QH[ilv]=xPv
call bNe(p)
endif
endif
endfunction
function bQe takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
set QH[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]=0
call bNe(p)
endfunction
function bse takes player p returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local string iwv=Rr[ilv]
local real iqv=0
local boolean bGe=true
set iqv=iqv+bbe(p)
set iqv=iqv+bge(p)
set iqv=iqv+bke(p)
set iqv=iqv+bme(p)
set iqv=iqv+bPe(p)
if iwv=="Cantilena#3296" or iwv=="didasdd#3635" or iwv=="hanran#31227" or iwv=="Moon#3577" or iwv=="PBH#3676" or iwv=="reg123#3457" or iwv=="Rynne#31450" or iwv=="비니잇#3893" or iwv=="진해팡야#3290" or iwv=="초발수#3742" or iwv=="크라임#3584" then
set bGe=false
endif
if bGe and iqv>0 then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[ilv]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|R 님의 드랍률 및 강화확률은 |CFFFF0000"+I2S(S2I(R2SW((gi[ilv]-1.)*'d',0,1)))+"|R % 가 증가합니다.")
endif
endfunction

function bTe takes nothing returns nothing
call bSe(GetTriggerPlayer(),1)
endfunction
function bue takes nothing returns nothing
call bSe(GetTriggerPlayer(),2)
endfunction
function bUe takes player p,integer bte returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local string iwv=Rr[ilv]
local string Vxv=null
if bte==1 then
if iwv=="RoyalGuardSOsi" or iwv=="SensesFail" then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season Title 1st.mdx"
elseif iwv=="Melonaid" then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season Title 2nd.mdx"
elseif iwv=="king." then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season Title 3rd.mdx"
endif
set rj[ilv]='e'
elseif bte==2 then
if iwv=="Melonaid" or iwv=="SensesFail" then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season2 Title 1st.mdx"
elseif iwv=="stil1love" then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season2 Title 2nd.mdx"
elseif iwv=="starfire" then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season2 Title 3rd.mdx"
endif
set rj[ilv]='g'
endif
set ij[ilv]=Vxv
if Vxv!=null then
call DestroyEffect(aj[ilv])
set aj[ilv]=AddSpecialEffectTarget(Vxv,hv[ilv],"overhead")
endif
endfunction
function bwe takes nothing returns nothing
call bUe(GetTriggerPlayer(),1)
endfunction
function bWe takes nothing returns nothing
call bUe(GetTriggerPlayer(),2)
endfunction
function bye takes player p returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
if Rr[ilv]=="RoyalGuardSOsi" then
set rj[ilv]='d'
set ij[ilv]="Eden\\Season Title Tester.mdx"
call DestroyEffect(aj[ilv])
set aj[ilv]=AddSpecialEffectTarget("Eden\\Season Title Tester.mdx",hv[ilv],"overhead")
endif
endfunction
function bYe takes nothing returns nothing
call bye(GetTriggerPlayer())
endfunction
function bze takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
set MH[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]=21
call bIe(p)
endfunction
function bZe takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
set MH[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]=22
call bIe(p)
endfunction
function b_e takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
set MH[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]=23
call bIe(p)
endfunction
function b0e takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
set MH[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]=24
call bIe(p)
endfunction
function b1e takes nothing returns nothing
local string iwv
local integer i=0
loop
exitwhen i>=8
set i=i+1
set iwv=Rr[i]
if iwv=="TuTu-BoBo" or iwv=="Days" or iwv=="kasha" or iwv=="dusqja12" or iwv=="RoyalGuardSOsi" or iwv=="GTA" or iwv=="gjfjfjfjf" or iwv=="ChuenA" or iwv=="IMWHAT" or iwv=="Asic" or iwv=="Mist_RPG" or iwv=="데토" or iwv=="nero88" or iwv=="king." or iwv=="Melonaid" or iwv=="gagage" or iwv=="SensesFail" then
set WH[i]=1
elseif iwv=="pjk504" or iwv=="fpsdleksh" or iwv=="Laeva" or iwv=="furanki" or iwv=="RKatkd" or iwv=="RAHON" or iwv=="qhd1012" or iwv=="mandu3426" or iwv=="miko134" or iwv=="S2.." or iwv=="hunter-" or iwv=="SiRin" or iwv=="Omi_2sae" or iwv=="Tollos" or iwv=="Crescent" or iwv=="[Donald]" then
set WH[i]=2
elseif iwv=="yoonsok" or iwv=="wlfkfakducls" or iwv=="mindol" or iwv=="vice.hello[lv]" or iwv=="doffl0809" or iwv=="[Kira]" or iwv=="justitia" or iwv=="dhqpffltm" or iwv=="soongu" or iwv=="raians" or iwv=="DuMo" or iwv=="Gura" or iwv=="Mark-2" or iwv=="qwe564qwr" or iwv=="Game" or iwv=="JaMong" then
set WH[i]=3
endif
if iwv=="RoyalGuardSOsi" or iwv=="SensesFail" then
set yH[i]=1
elseif iwv=="Melonaid" then
set yH[i]=2
elseif iwv=="king." then
set yH[i]=3
endif
if iwv=="WOONO__" or iwv=="sunwoo05091" or iwv=="sellget" or iwv=="min4489" or iwv=="stil1love" or iwv=="dkwkcjstk" or iwv=="starfire" or iwv=="River" or iwv=="333" or iwv=="zxcv020" or iwv=="Arica" or iwv=="d-.-b" or iwv=="dudj" or iwv=="mbticute" or iwv=="Melonaid" or iwv=="Asic" or iwv=="gainox2" or iwv=="SensesFail" then
set WH[i+$A]=1
elseif iwv=="전쟁" or iwv=="_Kazuki" or iwv=="kasha" or iwv=="skdmnoe" or iwv=="dark.." or iwv=="979194" or iwv=="a14" or iwv=="jossamthresh" or iwv=="Crescent" or iwv=="[24]" or iwv=="sadistcat" or iwv=="rnflrnfl1855" or iwv=="mute" or iwv=="ShiRaOri" or iwv=="gjfjfjfjf" or iwv=="momo." or iwv=="yoonsok" then
set WH[i+$A]=2
elseif iwv=="1234875s" or iwv=="wnk20864" or iwv=="ranse" or iwv=="apfhd2xx" or iwv=="bot124" or iwv=="Ang" or iwv=="qwer040404" or iwv=="Dekaron_Hell" or iwv=="hak.sar." or iwv=="mikoo_" or iwv=="ggoggalcon" or iwv=="Hapi1" or iwv=="kntjjs" or iwv=="poi232" or iwv=="[Kira]" or iwv=="qudejr14" or iwv=="Vee" then
set WH[i+$A]=3
endif
if iwv=="Melonaid" or iwv=="SensesFail" then
set yH[i+$A]=1
elseif iwv=="stil1love" then
set yH[i+$A]=2
elseif iwv=="starfire" then
set yH[i+$A]=3
endif
endloop
endfunction

function b7e takes player p returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local integer xPv=ZH[ilv]
local string Vxv=null
if xPv==21 and vj[ilv]!=0 then
if vj[ilv]==1 then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season Weapon Job 1st.mdx"
elseif vj[ilv]==2 then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season Weapon Job 2nd.mdx"
elseif vj[ilv]==3 then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season Weapon Job 3rd.mdx"
else
set ZH[ilv]=0
endif
elseif xPv==22 and ej[ilv]!=0 then
if ej[ilv]==1 then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season Weapon Whole 1st.mdx"
elseif ej[ilv]==2 then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season Weapon Whole 2nd.mdx"
elseif ej[ilv]==3 then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season Weapon Whole 3rd.mdx"
else
set ZH[ilv]=0
endif
elseif xPv==23 and vj[ilv+$A]!=0 then
if vj[ilv+$A]==1 then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season2 Weapon Job 1st.mdx"
elseif vj[ilv+$A]==2 then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season2 Weapon Job 2nd.mdx"
elseif vj[ilv+$A]==3 then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season2 Weapon Job 3rd.mdx"
else
set ZH[ilv]=0
endif
elseif xPv==24 and ej[ilv+$A]!=0 then
if ej[ilv+$A]==1 then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season2 Weapon Whole 1st.mdx"
elseif ej[ilv+$A]==2 then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season2 Weapon Whole 2nd.mdx"
elseif ej[ilv+$A]==3 then
set Vxv="Eden\\Season2 Weapon Whole 3rd.mdx"
else
set ZH[ilv]=0
endif
else
set ZH[ilv]=0
endif
if xj[ilv]!=null then
call DestroyEffect(xj[ilv])
call DestroyEffect(oj[ilv])
endif
if Vxv==null then
set xj[ilv]=null
set oj[ilv]=null
else
set xj[ilv]=AddSpecialEffectTarget(Vxv,hv[ilv],"hand left")
set oj[ilv]=AddSpecialEffectTarget(Vxv,hv[ilv],"hand right")
endif
endfunction

function Bre takes player p returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
if aj[ilv]!=null then
call DestroyEffect(aj[ilv])

endif
endfunction
function Bie takes player p returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local integer Awe=rj[ilv]
local string iwv=Rr[ilv]
local string Vxv=null
if Awe>='d' then
if Awe=='d' then
call bye(p)
elseif Awe=='e' then
call bUe(p,1)
elseif Awe=='f' then
call bSe(p,1)
elseif Awe=='g' then
call bUe(p,2)
elseif Awe=='h' then
call bSe(p,2)
endif
elseif Awe>=2 then
call aCv(p,Awe-1)
elseif Awe==1 then
else
if iwv=="Nikita" then
set Vxv="The Name Nikita.mdx"
elseif iwv=="bond" then
set Vxv="The_Name_Overmind...mdx"
elseif iwv=="Bongyari" or iwv=="KP31" then
set Vxv="The_Name_KP31.mdx"
elseif iwv=="SpeCterS" or iwv=="ehdtlddl0319" or iwv=="sinlove12" then
set Vxv="The_Name_Pribil.mdx"
elseif iwv=="SungMin" then
set Vxv="The_Name_THE_THIS.mdx"
elseif iwv=="데토" then
set Vxv="The_Name_Asic.mdx"
elseif iwv=="scvscvgo" then
set Vxv="Eden\\GlobalDonate_nisekr_1.mdl"
elseif iwv=="피뭍은개고기#3852" then
set Vxv="The_Name_VVIP01.mdx"
elseif iwv=="BlackWhite#31745" then
set Vxv="The_Name_VVIP03.mdx"
elseif iwv=="ratary69" then
set Vxv="The Neme rayary69.mdx"
elseif iwv=="[Kira]" then
set Vxv="The Name Kira.mdx"
elseif iwv=="Card" then
set Vxv="The Name Card.mdx"
elseif iwv=="Tollos" then
set Vxv="The_Name_Tollos.mdx"
elseif iwv=="S2.." then
set Vxv="The_Name_nttgoser.mdx"
elseif iwv=="The_Tornado" or iwv=="Chic_" then
set Vxv="The Name Guide of Upgrade.mdx"
endif
if Vxv==null then
if aj[ilv]==null then
if ir[ilv]>=50 then
set Vxv="The Name 06.mdx"
else
set Awe=GetHeroInt(hv[ilv],false)
if Awe>=$927C0 then
set Vxv="The Name 05.mdx"
elseif Awe>=$7A120 then
set Vxv="The Name 04.mdx"
elseif Awe>=$186A0 then
set Vxv="The Name 03.mdx"
elseif Awe>=5000 then
set Vxv="The Name 02.mdx"
elseif GetHeroLevel(hv[ilv])>=$3E8 then
set Vxv="The Name 01.mdx"
endif
endif
endif
endif
if Vxv!=null then
set ij[ilv]=Vxv
call DestroyEffect(aj[ilv])
set aj[ilv]=AddSpecialEffectTarget(Vxv,hv[ilv],"overhead")
endif
endif
endfunction
function Bae takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))

set rj[ilv]=1
set ij[ilv]=null
endfunction
function Bne takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
set rj[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]=0
call Bie(p)
endfunction

function BOe takes nothing returns nothing
call BXe(GetTriggerPlayer())
endfunction
function BRe takes nothing returns nothing
local integer IT=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
local string iwv=Rr[IT]
if iwv=="sabre_" then
set Dr[IT]="|CFF00ff00타|CFF00ff7f츠|CFF7fff00마|CFF000000키|R"
elseif iwv=="BlacklightsC" then
set Dr[IT]="|CFFA6F343평타|R|CFF54BFF5천국|R"
endif
call SetPlayerName(GetTriggerPlayer(),dr[IT]+ce[IT]+Dr[IT])
endfunction
function BAe takes nothing returns nothing
local integer IT=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
local string iwv=Rr[IT]
if iwv=="sabre_" then
set Dr[IT]="|CFF0100FF시온|R"
endif
call SetPlayerName(GetTriggerPlayer(),dr[IT]+ce[IT]+Dr[IT])
endfunction
function Bbe takes player p,integer Vfv,boolean VJv returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local unit nOe=hv[ilv]
local unit nRe
local real nIe
if Vfv<0 then
set Vfv=U[ilv]
endif
set nRe=Vjv(p,S[ilv],Vfv,GetUnitX(nOe),GetUnitY(nOe),GetUnitFacing(nOe),VJv)
set hv[ilv]=null
call nXe(nOe,nRe)
set Ej[0]=UnitItemInSlot(nOe,0)
set Ej[1]=UnitItemInSlot(nOe,1)
set Ej[2]=UnitItemInSlot(nOe,2)
set Ej[3]=UnitItemInSlot(nOe,3)
set Ej[4]=UnitItemInSlot(nOe,4)
set Ej[5]=UnitItemInSlot(nOe,5)
call UnitRemoveItem(nOe,Ej[0])
call UnitRemoveItem(nOe,Ej[1])
call UnitRemoveItem(nOe,Ej[2])
call UnitRemoveItem(nOe,Ej[3])
call UnitRemoveItem(nOe,Ej[4])
call UnitRemoveItem(nOe,Ej[5])
call SetHeroXP(nRe,GetHeroXP(nOe),false)
call SetHeroStr(nRe,GetHeroStr(nOe,false),true)
call SetHeroAgi(nRe,GetHeroAgi(nOe,false),true)
call SetHeroInt(nRe,GetHeroInt(nOe,false),true)
call UnitAddItem(nRe,Ej[0])
call UnitAddItem(nRe,Ej[1])
call UnitAddItem(nRe,Ej[2])
call UnitAddItem(nRe,Ej[3])
call UnitAddItem(nRe,Ej[4])
call UnitAddItem(nRe,Ej[5])
set Ej[0]=null
set Ej[1]=null
set Ej[2]=null
set Ej[3]=null
set Ej[4]=null
set Ej[5]=null
call OQe(nRe,R2I(Ri[ilv]))
call Ose(nRe,R2I(Ei[ilv]*Li[ilv]))
call SelectUnitForPlayerSingle(nRe,p)
set hv[ilv]=nRe
if GetUnitTypeId(nRe)==('��i'+'�H�') then
call SetUnitColor(nRe,PLAYER_COLOR_RED)
elseif GetUnitTypeId(nRe)==('� *�'+'�8r') then
call SetUnitColor(nRe,PLAYER_COLOR_LIGHT_GRAY)
endif
call Bre(p)
call bIe(p)
call bAe(p)
call bNe(p)
call b7e(p)
call RemoveUnit(nOe)
set nOe=null
set nRe=null
endfunction
function BBe takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local integer VDv=S[ilv]
local string iwv=Rr[ilv]
local boolean Bce=false
if VDv==1 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==2 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==3 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==4 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==5 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==6 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==7 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==8 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==9 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==$A then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==$B then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==$C then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==$D then
set Bce=iwv=="Warcraft"
elseif VDv==$E then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==$F then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==16 then
set Bce=iwv=="Warcraft"
endif
if Bce or iwv=="Maste" then
call Bbe(p,39,true)
endif
set p=null
endfunction
function Bde takes nothing returns nothing
if U[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]!=0 then
call Bbe(GetTriggerPlayer(),0,true)
endif
endfunction
function Bfe takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()

local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local integer VDv=S[ilv]
local string iwv=Rr[ilv]
local boolean Bce=false
local boolean BFe=iwv=="scvscvgo" or iwv=="SensesFail"
if VDv==1 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==2 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==3 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==4 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==5 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==6 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==7 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==8 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==9 then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==$A then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==$B then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==$C then
set Bce=iwv=="MGM" or iwv=="akaikuro" or iwv=="abdc0505"
elseif VDv==$D then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==$E then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==$F then
set Bce=false
elseif VDv==16 then
set Bce=iwv=="XellosS#31604"
elseif VDv==17 then
set Bce=false
endif
if Bce or BFe then
call Bbe(p,$F5,true)
endif
endfunction

function fUe takes nothing returns boolean
return(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="scvscvgo")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="Nikita")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="Card")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="Krul-Tepes")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="Play")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="Tatara.Kogasa.")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="Legend")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="Izayoi-Sakuya")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="GangHwa_NoYae")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="chobo9756")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="[Kira]")
endfunction
function fwe takes nothing returns boolean
return(fUe())
endfunction
function fWe takes nothing returns nothing
call CreateNUnitsAtLoc(1,('�dqG'+'�Ͽ'),GetTriggerPlayer(),GetUnitLoc(uv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]),bj_UNIT_FACING)
call UnitAddItem(bj_lastCreatedUnit,UnitItemInSlotBJ(uv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))],1))
call UnitAddItem(bj_lastCreatedUnit,UnitItemInSlotBJ(uv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))],2))
call UnitAddItem(bj_lastCreatedUnit,UnitItemInSlotBJ(uv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))],3))
call UnitAddItem(bj_lastCreatedUnit,UnitItemInSlotBJ(uv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))],4))
call UnitAddItem(bj_lastCreatedUnit,UnitItemInSlotBJ(uv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))],5))
call UnitAddItem(bj_lastCreatedUnit,UnitItemInSlotBJ(uv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))],6))
call RemoveUnit(uv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))])
set uv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=bj_lastCreatedUnit
endfunction

function Fpe takes nothing returns nothing
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=$C
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
if(FMe())then
set YV[bj_forLoopAIndex]=true
call CustomDefeatBJ(Player(-1+(bj_forLoopAIndex)),"TRIGSTR_975")
endif
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
endfunction

set Lv="~!@#$%^&*()_-+={[}]:;'<,>.?/"
set mv="abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz"
set Mv="ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ"
endfunction

function Fwe takes nothing returns nothing
call InitHashtableBJ()
set Pe=GetLastCreatedHashtableBJ()
call InitHashtableBJ()
set vx=GetLastCreatedHashtableBJ()
call InitHashtableBJ()
set Zx=GetLastCreatedHashtableBJ()
call InitHashtableBJ()
set vo=GetLastCreatedHashtableBJ()
call InitHashtableBJ()
set Tv=GetLastCreatedHashtableBJ()
call InitHashtableBJ()
set De=GetLastCreatedHashtableBJ()
call InitHashtableBJ()
set Wv=GetLastCreatedHashtableBJ()
call InitHashtableBJ()
set Ne=GetLastCreatedHashtableBJ()
set ce[1]="|cffff0202"
set ce[2]="|cff0042ff"
set ce[3]="|cff1ce6b9"
set ce[4]="|cff540081"
set ce[5]="|cfffffc01"
set ce[6]="|cfffe8a0e"
set ce[7]="|cff20c000"
set ce[8]="|cffe55bb0"
set ce[9]="|cff959697"
set ce[$A]="|cff7ebff1"
set ce[$B]="|cff106246"
set ce[$C]="|cff4e2a04"
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=$C
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
call CreateFogModifierRectBJ(true,Player(-1+(bj_forLoopAIndex)),FOG_OF_WAR_VISIBLE,kR)
set qv=GetRectCenter(kR)
call PanCameraToTimedLocForPlayer(Player(-1+(bj_forLoopAIndex)),qv,0)
call RemoveLocation(qv)
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
endfunction
function Fye takes nothing returns nothing
local group g=CreateGroup()
local unit u
set sv=InitHashtable()
call GroupEnumUnitsInRect(g,bj_mapInitialPlayableArea,null)
loop
set u=FirstOfGroup(g)
exitwhen u==null
if GetOwningPlayer(u)==Player($C)and GetUnitPointValue(u)!='d' then
call SaveReal(sv,GetHandleId(u),0,GetUnitX(u))
call SaveReal(sv,GetHandleId(u),1,GetUnitY(u))
endif
call GroupRemoveUnit(g,u)
endloop
call DestroyGroup(g)
set g=null
endfunction
function Fze takes nothing returns boolean
return(GetPlayerSlotState(Player(-1+(bj_forLoopAIndex)))==PLAYER_SLOT_STATE_PLAYING)and(GetPlayerController(Player(-1+(bj_forLoopAIndex)))==MAP_CONTROL_USER)
endfunction
function FZe takes nothing returns nothing
set Uv=('����'+'�0+')
set Ro=('�Y|`'+'i���')

function OTe takes nothing returns nothing
local quest F3e
local string Vqv
set F3e=CreateQuest()
call QuestSetTitle(F3e,"|c00DFFB4FGrabiti's RPG Creator 1.07|r")
set Vqv="|cff47455A∴ |cffB4C3FFRPG 이름 : |cffFFCD28"+Hv
set Vqv=Vqv+"
|cff47455A∴ |c00DFFB4F이 맵은 Grabiti's RPG Creator 1.07을 기반으로 제작된 맵입니다."
set Vqv=Vqv+"
|cff47455A∴ |cfffffc01세이브시에도 캐릭터가 삭제되지 않으며 아이템이 귀속됩니다. 또한 세이브 코드가 |cffFFCD28워크래프트 폴더\\Grabiti's RPG Creator\\RPG 이름 |cfffffc01경로에 텍스트 파일로 기록됩니다."
set Vqv=Vqv+"
|cff47455A∴ |cffB4C3FF아이템의 중첩수도 세이브가 되며, 배낭의 인벤토리 또한 세이브가 됩니다."
set Vqv=Vqv+"
|cff47455A∴ |cff78EFAD그 외 자세한 내용은 |cff63CC63http://cafe.naver.com/rpgcreator |cff78EFAD에서 확인 가능합니다.|r"
call QuestSetDescription(F3e,Vqv)
call QuestSetIconPath(F3e,"ReplaceableTextures\\CommandButtons\\BTNAmbush.blp")
call QuestSetRequired(F3e,true)
set F3e=CreateQuest()
call QuestSetTitle(F3e,"|cff557DE1기본적인 명령어|r")
set Vqv="|cffffcc00-시야 <50~150> : |r카메라 시야를 조절합니다."
set Vqv=Vqv+"
|cffffcc00-Cam <50~150> : |r카메라 시야를 조절합니다."
set Vqv=Vqv+"
|cffffcc00-자살 : |r자신의 캐릭터를 살해합니다."
set Vqv=Vqv+"
|cffffcc00-Suicide : |r자신의 캐릭터를 살해합니다."
set Vqv=Vqv+"
|cffffcc00-주사위 : |r1~100 사이의 랜덤 숫자를 출력합니다."
set Vqv=Vqv+"
|cffffcc00-Dice : |r1~100 사이의 랜덤 숫자를 출력합니다."
set Vqv=Vqv+"
|cffffcc00-Save : |r캐릭터를 세이브합니다."
set Vqv=Vqv+"
|cffffcc00-Load : |r캐릭터를 로드합니다. (-Load 타이핑 후에 코드를 이어서 입력해야 합니다.)"
call QuestSetDescription(F3e,Vqv)
call QuestSetIconPath(F3e,"ReplaceableTextures\\CommandButtons\\BTNAmbush.blp")
call QuestSetRequired(F3e,true)
set F3e=null
endfunction
function F5e takes nothing returns boolean
return(be)
endfunction
function F6e takes nothing returns nothing
if(F5e())then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),.0,.0,60.,"|cffFF0202Warning) |c00DFFB4F현재 테스트 모드이므로 세이브가 불가능합니다.|r")
else
call Preloader("RPGCreator_Single.mdx")
endif
endfunction
function F8e takes nothing returns boolean
return(bj_forLoopAIndex!=bj_forLoopBIndex)and(StringCase(GetPlayerName(Player(-1+(bj_forLoopAIndex))),false)==StringCase(GetPlayerName(Player(-1+(bj_forLoopBIndex))),false))
endfunction
function F9e takes nothing returns boolean
return(GetPlayerSlotState(Player(-1+(bj_forLoopAIndex)))==PLAYER_SLOT_STATE_PLAYING)and(GetPlayerController(Player(-1+(bj_forLoopAIndex)))==MAP_CONTROL_USER)
endfunction
function gve takes nothing returns nothing
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=$C
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
if(F9e())then
set bj_forLoopBIndex=1
set bj_forLoopBIndexEnd=$C
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopBIndex>bj_forLoopBIndexEnd
if(F8e())then
call CustomDefeatBJ(Player(-1+(bj_forLoopBIndex)),"|cffFF3232같은 아이디로의 접속은 불가능합니다.|r")
endif
set bj_forLoopBIndex=bj_forLoopBIndex+1
endloop
endif
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
endfunction
function gxe takes nothing returns boolean
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
local boolean nHe=hv[ilv]==null and IsUnitType(GetTriggerUnit(),UNIT_TYPE_HERO)and GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())==Player($F)and RectContainsUnit(kR,GetTriggerUnit())and oi[ilv]
return nHe
endfunction
function goe takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local integer Vkv=GetUnitTypeId(u)
if Pv[ilv]==0 then
set Pv[ilv]=Vkv
call TimerStart(pv[ilv],1,false,null)
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,.1,"|CFFFFBE0A'"+GetUnitName(u)+"|CFFFFBE0A' |C00DFFB4F를 선택하시려면 한번 더 클릭하십시오.|r")

elseif u==Zh then

elseif u==VH then

elseif u==EH then

범위사냥 : 1")
elseif u==OH then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(p,0,0,"|CFFFF0000스톰 트루퍼

극단적인 범위 데미지에 치중되어있음

단일사냥 : 1
범위사냥 : 9")
elseif u==XH then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(p,0,0,"|CFFFF0000인다라천

|CFFC1FF6B모든 스킬이 패시브인 캐릭터

별도의 매크로없이 잠수타기 최적화 되어있다

사냥과 보스클리어를 적절히 섞어논 캐릭터

단일사냥 : 4
범위사냥 : 4")
elseif u==nH then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(p,0,0,"|CFFFF0000스트라이커

|CFFC1FF6B보스와 사냥이 조화를 이룬 근접 캐릭터

사냥 및 보스사냥이 적절하게 섞인 캐릭터며 무난하게 사용하기 좋다")
elseif u==aH then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(p,0,0,"|CFFFF0000악귀나찰

|CFFC1FF6B강화의노예에서 사냥 보스잡 모든것이 압도적으로 강한 캐릭터

그럼에도 일반캐릭터의 최소 2~3배 이상강력한 성능을 가지고있다.")
endif
else
if Pv[ilv]==Vkv then
call PanCameraToTimedForPlayer(p,GetStartLocationX(GetPlayerStartLocation(p)),GetStartLocationY(GetPlayerStartLocation(p)),.5)
set ri[ilv]=1
set hv[ilv]=Vjv(p,(LoadInteger(w,$61F24BB6,(Pv[ilv]))),0,GetStartLocationX(GetPlayerStartLocation(p)),GetStartLocationY(GetPlayerStartLocation(p)),bj_UNIT_FACING,true)
call SelectUnitForPlayerSingle(hv[ilv],p)
set uv[ilv]=CreateUnitAtLoc(p,Uv,Sv[ilv],275)
set Io[ilv]=CreateUnitAtLoc(p,Ro,Sv[ilv],275)
set No[ilv]=CreateUnit(p,Ao,GetLocationX(nr[ilv])-512,GetLocationY(nr[ilv])+512,275)
set Yi[ilv]=CreateUnitAtLoc(p,('��'+'RF��'),zi[ilv],275)
set Ai[ilv]=CreateUnitAtLoc(p,('̩.'+'�dJ�'),zr[ilv],275)
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,$A,"|C00DFFB4F"+GetUnitName(hv[ilv])+" |C00DFFB4F선택!|r")
call nEe(hv[ilv])
call fte(p)
call fue(p)
call Bie(p)
call BXe(p)
call BVe(p)
call bse(p)
call bIe(p)
call bAe(p)
call bNe(p)
call OUe(p)
if Rr[ilv]=="scvscvgo" or Rr[ilv]=="SensesFail" then
set tE[ilv]=CreateUnitAtLoc(p,('��M'+'�Dt�'),TE[ilv],275)
call UnitAddItemByIdSwapped(kv[LoadInteger(vx,ilv,uE)],tE[ilv])
call UnitDropItemSlot(tE[ilv],bj_lastCreatedItem,0)
call SetItemPlayer(bj_lastCreatedItem,p,false)
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(tE[ilv]),1,GetItemName(bj_lastCreatedItem))
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(tE[ilv]),7,GetItemName(bj_lastCreatedItem))
call UnitAddItemByIdSwapped(kv[LoadInteger(vx,ilv,UE)],tE[ilv])
call UnitDropItemSlot(tE[ilv],bj_lastCreatedItem,1)
call SetItemPlayer(bj_lastCreatedItem,p,false)
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(tE[ilv]),2,GetItemName(bj_lastCreatedItem))
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(tE[ilv]),8,GetItemName(bj_lastCreatedItem))
call UnitAddItemByIdSwapped(kv[LoadInteger(vx,ilv,wE)],tE[ilv])
call UnitDropItemSlot(tE[ilv],bj_lastCreatedItem,2)
call SetItemPlayer(bj_lastCreatedItem,p,false)
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(tE[ilv]),3,GetItemName(bj_lastCreatedItem))
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(tE[ilv]),9,GetItemName(bj_lastCreatedItem))
call UnitAddItemByIdSwapped(kv[LoadInteger(vx,ilv,WE)],tE[ilv])
call UnitDropItemSlot(tE[ilv],bj_lastCreatedItem,3)
call SetItemPlayer(bj_lastCreatedItem,p,false)
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(tE[ilv]),4,GetItemName(bj_lastCreatedItem))
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(tE[ilv]),$A,GetItemName(bj_lastCreatedItem))
call UnitAddItemByIdSwapped(kv[LoadInteger(vx,ilv,yE)],tE[ilv])
call UnitDropItemSlot(tE[ilv],bj_lastCreatedItem,4)
call SetItemPlayer(bj_lastCreatedItem,p,false)
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(tE[ilv]),5,GetItemName(bj_lastCreatedItem))
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(tE[ilv]),$B,GetItemName(bj_lastCreatedItem))
call UnitAddItemByIdSwapped(kv[LoadInteger(vx,ilv,YE)],tE[ilv])
call UnitDropItemSlot(tE[ilv],bj_lastCreatedItem,5)
call SetItemPlayer(bj_lastCreatedItem,p,false)
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(tE[ilv]),6,GetItemName(bj_lastCreatedItem))
call SaveStr(Pe,GetHandleId(tE[ilv]),$C,GetItemName(bj_lastCreatedItem))
endif
else
set Pv[ilv]=Vkv
call TimerStart(pv[ilv],1,false,null)
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,.1,"|CFFFFBE0A'"+GetUnitName(u)+"|CFFFFBE0A' |C00DFFB4F를 선택하시려면 한번 더 클릭하십시오.|r")
endif
endif
set u=null
set p=null
endfunction

endfunction

function gQe takes player p returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
if ri[ilv]>7 then
set ri[ilv]=7
endif
if ii[ilv]>7 then
set ii[ilv]=7
endif
if ai[ilv]>7 then
set ai[ilv]=7
endif
if di[ilv]>7 then
set di[ilv]=7
endif
if mi[ilv]>7 then
set mi[ilv]=7
endif
if Ui[ilv]>7 then
set Ui[ilv]=7
endif
if Ua[ilv]>7 then
set Ua[ilv]=7
endif
if ha[ilv]>7 then
set ha[ilv]=7
endif
if qn[ilv]>7 then
set qn[ilv]=7
endif
if MX[ilv]>7 then
set MX[ilv]=7
endif
call nEe(hv[ilv])
call fte(p)
call fue(p)
call Bie(p)
call BXe(p)
call BVe(p)
call bse(p)
call bIe(p)
call bAe(p)
call bNe(p)
call b7e(p)
call OUe(p)
endfunction
function gse takes nothing returns boolean
return not Ye[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]and StringCase(SubString(GetEventPlayerChatString(),0,5),false)=="-save"
endfunction
function gSe takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
local unit Ode=hv[ilv]
local unit ODe=uv[ilv]
local unit Ofe=Io[ilv]
local unit OFe=No[ilv]

local unit OGe=tE[ilv]

call nOv(GetTriggerPlayer(),30,"Upgrade_RPG.blp",'d','d','d',0,0,0,0,'d')
set Ze[jr]=Gr[ilv]

set Ze[xn]=IMaxBJ(0,i-$B1FA7)

set Ze[Lo]=GetItemCharges(UnitItemInSlot(No[ilv],5))

set Ze[Ba]=LoadInteger(Kv,0,GetItemTypeId(UnitItemInSlot(Oge,4)))
set Ze[ca]=LoadInteger(Kv,0,GetItemTypeId(UnitItemInSlot(Oge,5)))
set Ze[Ca]=GetItemCharges(UnitItemInSlot(Yi[ilv],0))
set Ze[Da]=GetItemCharges(UnitItemInSlot(Yi[ilv],1))
set Ze[fa]=GetItemCharges(UnitItemInSlot(Yi[ilv],2))
set Ze[Fa]=GetItemCharges(UnitItemInSlot(Yi[ilv],3))
set Ze[da]=GetItemCharges(UnitItemInSlot(Yi[ilv],4))
set Ze[ga]=GetItemCharges(UnitItemInSlot(Yi[ilv],5))
set Ze[uE]=LoadInteger(Kv,0,GetItemTypeId(UnitItemInSlot(OGe,0)))
set Ze[UE]=LoadInteger(Kv,0,GetItemTypeId(UnitItemInSlot(OGe,1)))
set Ze[wE]=LoadInteger(Kv,0,GetItemTypeId(UnitItemInSlot(OGe,2)))
set Ze[WE]=LoadInteger(Kv,0,GetItemTypeId(UnitItemInSlot(OGe,3)))
set Ze[yE]=LoadInteger(Kv,0,GetItemTypeId(UnitItemInSlot(OGe,4)))
set Ze[YE]=LoadInteger(Kv,0,GetItemTypeId(UnitItemInSlot(OGe,5)))
if hv[ilv]!=null and Ex[ilv]+1<=$3B9ACA00 then
set Ex[ilv]=Ex[ilv]+1
endif
set Ze[Vx]=Ex[ilv]
call XZe(GetTriggerPlayer())
if not be or StringCase(GetPlayerName(GetTriggerPlayer()),false)==StringCase(Be,false)then
set Ye[ilv]=true
call ONe(GetTriggerPlayer(),GetEventPlayerChatString())
else
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),.0,.0,.1,"|cffFF0202Error) |c00DFFB4F현재 테스트 모드이므로 세이브가 불가능합니다.|r")
endif
set Ode=null
set ODe=null
set Ofe=null
set OFe=null
set Oge=null
set OGe=null
endfunction
function gTe takes nothing returns boolean
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
return not qe[ilv]and not YV[ilv]
endfunction
function gue takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
if hv[ilv]==null then
call TriggerSleepAction(.01)
set qe[ilv]=true
set Qe[ilv]=""
set te[ilv]=0
set Te[ilv]=0
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),.0,.0,3.,"|c00DFFB4F세이브 코드를 입력하세요.|r")
else
set qe[ilv]=false
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),.0,.0,10.,"|cffFF0202Error) |c00DFFB4F이미 영웅을 소지하고 있습니다.|r")
endif
endfunction
function gwe takes nothing returns boolean
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
return hv[ilv]==null and not ze[ilv]and qe[ilv]
endfunction

function gYe takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local real x=LoadReal(Qv,GetHandleId(t),0)
local real y=LoadReal(Qv,GetHandleId(t),1)
local integer Vkv=LoadInteger(Qv,GetHandleId(t),2)
local unit u=CreateUnit(Player($C),Vkv,x,y,GetRandomReal(0,360))
call SaveReal(sv,GetHandleId(u),0,x)
call SaveReal(sv,GetHandleId(u),1,y)
call FlushChildHashtable(Qv,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
set t=null
set u=null
endfunction
function gze takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t
local integer h=GetHandleId(GetTriggerUnit())
local integer Vkv=GetUnitTypeId(GetTriggerUnit())
if HaveSavedReal(sv,h,0)then
set t=CreateTimer()
call SaveReal(Qv,GetHandleId(t),0,LoadReal(sv,h,0))
call SaveReal(Qv,GetHandleId(t),1,LoadReal(sv,h,1))
call SaveInteger(Qv,GetHandleId(t),2,Vkv)
call FlushChildHashtable(sv,h)
call TimerStart(t,GetUnitPointValueByType(Vkv),false,function gYe)
set t=null
endif
endfunction
function g_e takes nothing returns nothing
local string Nve=ce[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),.0,.0,10.,"|cffFFCD28'"+GetPlayerName(GetTriggerPlayer())+"|cffFFCD28'"+Nve+" 님이 퇴장하셨습니다.")
call RemoveUnit(ia[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))])
call RemoveUnit(dO[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))])
call SetPlayerName(GetTriggerPlayer(),("|CFF888888"+Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]))
endfunction
function g1e takes nothing returns boolean
return(fe)and(S2I(SubStringBJ(GetEventPlayerChatString(),9,$B))>=50)and(S2I(SubStringBJ(GetEventPlayerChatString(),9,$B))<=$E6)
endfunction
function g2e takes nothing returns nothing
set Ae[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=(S2I(SubStringBJ(GetEventPlayerChatString(),9,$B))*17)
call SetCameraFieldForPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),CAMERA_FIELD_TARGET_DISTANCE,I2R(Ae[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]),.5)
endfunction
function g4e takes nothing returns boolean
return(fe)and(S2I(SubStringBJ(GetEventPlayerChatString(),6,8))>=50)and(S2I(SubStringBJ(GetEventPlayerChatString(),6,8))<=$E6)
endfunction
function g5e takes nothing returns nothing
set Ae[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=(S2I(SubStringBJ(GetEventPlayerChatString(),6,8))*17)
call SetCameraFieldForPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),CAMERA_FIELD_TARGET_DISTANCE,I2R(Ae[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]),.5)
endfunction
function g7e takes nothing returns boolean
return(Fe)
endfunction
function g8e takes nothing returns nothing
local string Nve=ce[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]
local string g9e="|cffFFCD28'"
local string iwv=GetPlayerName(GetTriggerPlayer())
local string Gve=I2S(GetRandomInt(0,'d'))
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),.0,.0,10.,g9e+iwv+g9e+Nve+" 님의 주사위는 "+g9e+Gve+g9e+Nve+" 입니다.")
endfunction
function Gxe takes nothing returns boolean
return(Ge)
endfunction
function Goe takes nothing returns nothing
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=$C
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
set bj_forLoopBIndex=1
set bj_forLoopBIndexEnd=$C
loop

function GPe takes nothing returns nothing

local real y

endif
loop

set x=GetLocationX(Sv[i])
set y=GetLocationY(Sv[i])

call Gpe(uv[i],x,y-$C8)
call Gpe(Io[i],x,y-$C8)
call Gpe(No[i],x,y-$C8)
call Gpe(Yi[i],x,y-$C8)
endif
exitwhen i>=8
endloop
endfunction

function hHe takes nothing returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
local integer i=GetPlayerId(p)+1
local integer Awe=GetHeroInt(hv[i],false)
if GetItemTypeId(QM[vv])==('��4�'+'��9e') then
call nhe(p,1,$6978)
endif
if GetItemTypeId(QM[vv])==('M�i'+'��') then
if Awe<500 then
call nhe(p,0,Awe*50)
elseif Awe<$FA0 then
call nhe(p,0,Awe*500)
elseif Awe<$2710 then
call nhe(p,0,Awe*$186A0)
elseif Awe<75000 then
call nhe(p,1,2)
elseif Awe<$61A80 then
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*.0008))
elseif Awe<$AAE60 then
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*.0032))
elseif Awe<$F4240 then
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*.013))
elseif Awe<$1E8480 then
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*.052))
elseif Awe<$4C4B40 then
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*.2))
elseif Awe<$E4E1C0 then
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*.8))
else
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*3.2))
endif
endif
if GetItemTypeId(QM[vv])==('���'+'X��') then
if Awe<500 then
call nhe(p,0,Awe*25)
elseif Awe<$FA0 then
call nhe(p,0,Awe*$FA)
elseif Awe<$2710 then
call nhe(p,0,Awe*$C350)
elseif Awe<75000 then
call nhe(p,1,1)
elseif Awe<$61A80 then
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*.0004))
elseif Awe<$AAE60 then
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*.0016))
elseif Awe<$F4240 then
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*.0065))
elseif Awe<$1E8480 then
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*.026))
elseif Awe<$4C4B40 then
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*.1))
elseif Awe<$E4E1C0 then
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*.4))
else
call nhe(p,1,R2I(Awe*1.6))
endif
endif
set u=null
set p=null
endfunction

function hte takes nothing returns nothing
call EXv(0)
if(hSe())then
call PYv(vv,0,oM[vv])
call zZv(vv,$F,(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv]))))
call Ifv(vv,0,GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv]))
if(hKe())then
call xre(vv,1,GetRandomReal(0,100.))
call xre(vv,2,GetRandomReal(0,100.))
call xre(vv,3,GetRandomReal(0,100.))
if(hJe())then
call UnitAddItemByIdSwapped(('Ǡ�'+'?x��'),jy[vv])
call SetItemPlayer(bj_lastCreatedItem,GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv]),true)
endif
if(hke())then
call UnitAddItemByIdSwapped(('bL��'+'���X'),jy[vv])
call SetItemPlayer(bj_lastCreatedItem,GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv]),true)
endif
endif
if(hMe())then
if(hle())then
call CreateNUnitsAtLoc(1,('Qa�'+'���}'),Player($C),Wi[r3[vv]],bj_UNIT_FACING)
endif
if(hLe())then
call CreateNUnitsAtLoc(1,('�ZT'+'�6��'),Player($C),Pn[r3[vv]],bj_UNIT_FACING)
endif
if(hme())then
call CreateNUnitsAtLoc(1,('�n��'+'8ԵJ'),Player($C),sE[r3[vv]],bj_UNIT_FACING)
endif
endif
if(hse())then
if(hpe())then
call CreateNUnitsAtLoc(1,('�x�'+'Bه�'),Player($C),Wi[r3[vv]],bj_UNIT_FACING)
endif
if(hPe())then
call CreateNUnitsAtLoc(1,('|�D�'+'��M'),Player($C),Pn[r3[vv]],bj_UNIT_FACING)
endif
if(hqe())then
call CreateNUnitsAtLoc(1,('�J~�'+'{��M'),Player($C),sE[r3[vv]],bj_UNIT_FACING)
endif
if(hQe())then
call CreateNUnitsAtLoc(1,('�P�'+'���'),Player($C),pX[r3[vv]],bj_UNIT_FACING)
endif
endif
call V9v(vv)
endif
endfunction

endif

function Hxe takes nothing returns boolean
return(GetSpellAbilityId()=='A0HA')
endfunction
function Hoe takes nothing returns boolean
return(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="scvscvgo")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="scvscvgo#3226")or(Rr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=="SensesFail")
endfunction
function Hre takes nothing returns boolean
return(Hoe())
endfunction
function Hie takes nothing returns boolean
return(Sm[vv]==1)
endfunction
function Hae takes nothing returns nothing
call EXv(1)
if(Hie())then
call PYv(vv,0,oM[vv])
call RemoveUnit(Mr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(oM[vv])))])
if(Hre())then
call V9v(vv)
else
call UnitRemoveAbility(jy[vv],'A0HA')
call EVv(vv,1800.)
endif
else
call UnitAddAbility(jy[vv],'A0HA')
call V9v(vv)
endif
endfunction
function HVe takes nothing returns boolean
return(IsUnitType(GetTriggerUnit(),UNIT_TYPE_HERO))!=null
endfunction
function HEe takes nothing returns boolean
return(DistanceBetweenPoints(GetUnitLoc(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]),GetUnitLoc(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]))>700.)
endfunction
function HXe takes nothing returns boolean
return(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]!=null)
endfunction
function HOe takes nothing returns nothing
call SetUnitPositionLoc(GetTriggerUnit(),GetRectCenter(DI))
call PanCameraToTimedLocForPlayer(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit()),GetRectCenter(DI),0)
if(HXe())then
if(HEe())then
call SetUnitPositionLoc(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],GetUnitLoc(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]))
call IssueTargetOrderById(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],$D0012,hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))])
else
call IssueTargetOrderById(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],$D0012,hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))])
endif
endif
call Ase((1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer())))
endfunction
function HIe takes nothing returns boolean
return(IsUnitType(GetTriggerUnit(),UNIT_TYPE_HERO))!=null
endfunction
function HAe takes nothing returns boolean
return(DistanceBetweenPoints(GetUnitLoc(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]),GetUnitLoc(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]))>700.)
endfunction
function HNe takes nothing returns boolean
return(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]!=null)
endfunction
function Hbe takes nothing returns nothing
call SetUnitPositionLoc(GetTriggerUnit(),nr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))])
call PanCameraToTimedLocForPlayer(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit()),nr[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],0)
if(HNe())then
if(HAe())then
call SetUnitPositionLoc(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],GetUnitLoc(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]))
call IssueTargetOrderById(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],$D0012,hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))])
else
call IssueTargetOrderById(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],$D0012,hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))])
endif
endif
call Ase((1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer())))
endfunction

function jge takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local integer i=0
loop
exitwhen i>=8 or t==Nj[i]
set i=i+1
endloop
set t=null
if i<8 then
set bj[i]=false
endif
endfunction
function jGe takes unit u,item OPe,boolean jhe,integer abv,integer Ope,integer jHe,integer nme,integer originId returns nothing
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer ilv=GetPlayerId(p)
local location l=GetUnitLoc(u)
if jhe then
call PlaySoundAtPointBJ(iN,'d',l,0)
call RemoveItem(OPe)
set OPe=CreateItem(Ope,GetUnitX(u),GetUnitY(u))
call SetItemPlayer(OPe,p,true)
call UnitAddItem(u,OPe)
set OPe=null
else
if abv<=$A then
call PlaySoundAtPointBJ(ON,'d',l,0)
else
call PlaySoundAtPointBJ(RN,'d',l,0)
endif
endif
call RemoveLocation(l)
set l=null
set bj[ilv]=true
call TimerStart(Nj[ilv],.4,false,function jge)
endfunction
function jje takes nothing returns integer
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local integer i=0
local integer j
local item OPe
local integer Ope
loop
set OPe=UnitItemInSlot(u,i)
if OPe!=null then
set Ope=GetItemTypeId(OPe)
set j=0
loop
if Ope==Mo[j]then
set OPe=null
set u=null
return j
endif
set j=j+1
exitwhen j==20
endloop
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set OPe=null
set u=null
return-1
endfunction
function jJe takes nothing returns boolean
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())
return not bj[GetPlayerId(p)]and jje()>=0 and nle(p,0,21)
endfunction
function jke takes nothing returns boolean
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())
return not bj[GetPlayerId(p)]and jje()>=0 and nPe(p,0,21,$A)
endfunction
function jKe takes nothing returns boolean
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())
return not bj[GetPlayerId(p)]and jje()>=0 and nPe(p,0,21,30)
endfunction
function jle takes integer nme returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer jHe=jje()
local integer abv=jHe
local integer Ope=Mo[jHe]
local integer i=0
local boolean jhe=false
local real iqv
call SetUnitPosition(u,GetRectCenterX(JR),GetRectCenterY(JR))
if nme>0 then
loop
if abv<=3 then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=Mo[abv]
set jhe=true
else
if abv<=6 then
set iqv=30
elseif abv<=$A then
set iqv=$C
elseif abv<=$F then
set iqv=1.8
else
set iqv=1.8
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=Mo[abv]
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else

function jpe takes nothing returns integer
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local integer i=0
local integer j
local item OPe
local integer Ope
loop
set OPe=UnitItemInSlot(u,i)
if OPe!=null then
set Ope=GetItemTypeId(OPe)
set j=0
loop
if Ope==Po[j]then
set OPe=null
set u=null
return j
endif
set j=j+1
exitwhen j==20
endloop
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set OPe=null
set u=null
return-1
endfunction

endif

exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop

call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('�.��'+'�ۋH')))

call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=Uo[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('ڹ|�'+'6O�)')))
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
endif
endif
call jGe(u,GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,Uo[jHe]),jhe,abv,Ope,jHe,nme,Uo[0])
set u=null
endfunction

function JJe takes nothing returns integer
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()

local integer j

loop

set Ope=GetItemTypeId(OPe)
set j=0
loop

set OPe=null
set u=null
return j
endif
set j=j+1
exitwhen j==20
endloop

set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set OPe=null
set u=null
return-1
endfunction

endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=wo[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('꺦�'+'&O�M')))

set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=xr[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('g��'+'���Q')))

elseif abv<=$A then
set iqv=$C
elseif abv<=$F then
set iqv=1.8
else
set iqv=.45
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=ki[abv]
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=ki[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('2=@'+'
�1�')))
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
endif
endif
call jGe(u,GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,ki[jHe]),jhe,abv,Ope,jHe,nme,ki[0])
set u=null

function lVe takes nothing returns integer

endloop

elseif abv<=$A then
set iqv=$C
elseif abv<=$F then
set iqv=1.8
else
set iqv=.45
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=ui[abv]
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=ui[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('Ptп'+'���U')))
if abv<=$A then

function Lee takes nothing returns integer

loop

endloop

exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set OPe=null
set u=null
return-1
endfunction

set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else

set Ope=ka[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('����'+'Sg�')))

set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else

set Ope=an[abv]
set jhe=true

else

set iqv=.3
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=Fn[abv]
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=Fn[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('�rR�'+'*�:')))
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else

endif

endif

function ppe takes nothing returns integer
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local integer i=0
local integer j
local item OPe
local integer Ope
loop
set OPe=UnitItemInSlot(u,i)
if OPe!=null then
set Ope=GetItemTypeId(OPe)
set j=0
loop
if Ope==gn[j]then
set OPe=null
set u=null
return j
endif
set j=j+1
exitwhen j==20
endloop
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set OPe=null
set u=null
return-1
endfunction

set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=iV[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('Ȯ@_'+'HZ.�')))

set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1

endloop
else

set jhe=true
if abv>3 then

endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=UV[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('���'+'k%�=')))

call SetUnitPosition(u,GetRectCenterX(JR),GetRectCenterY(JR))
if nme>0 then
loop
if abv<=3 then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=pE[abv]
set jhe=true
else
if abv<=6 then
set iqv=24
elseif abv<=$A then
set iqv=9
elseif abv<=$F then
set iqv=1.2
else
set iqv=.3
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=pE[abv]
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=pE[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('ʅ)8'+'G�E�')))
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif

endif
call jGe(u,GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,pE[jHe]),jhe,abv,Ope,jHe,nme,pE[0])

function sVe takes nothing returns integer
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local integer i=0
local integer j
local item OPe
local integer Ope
loop
set OPe=UnitItemInSlot(u,i)
if OPe!=null then
set Ope=GetItemTypeId(OPe)
set j=0
loop
if Ope==PE[j]then
set OPe=null
set u=null
return j
endif
set j=j+1
exitwhen j==20
endloop
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set OPe=null
set u=null
return-1
endfunction

local integer Ope=EX[jHe]
local integer i=0
local boolean jhe=false
local real iqv
call SetUnitPosition(u,GetRectCenterX(JR),GetRectCenterY(JR))
if nme>0 then
loop
if abv<=3 then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=EX[abv]
set jhe=true
else
if abv<=6 then
set iqv=24
elseif abv<=$A then
set iqv=9
elseif abv<=$F then
set iqv=1.2
else
set iqv=.3
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=EX[abv]
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=EX[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('��='+'���')))
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
endif
endif
call jGe(u,GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,EX[jHe]),jhe,abv,Ope,jHe,nme,EX[0])
set u=null
endfunction

function See takes nothing returns integer
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local integer i=0
local integer j
local item OPe
local integer Ope
loop
set OPe=UnitItemInSlot(u,i)
if OPe!=null then
set Ope=GetItemTypeId(OPe)
set j=0
loop
if Ope==RX[j]then
set OPe=null
set u=null
return j
endif
set j=j+1
exitwhen j==20
endloop
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set OPe=null
set u=null
return-1
endfunction
function Sxe takes nothing returns boolean
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())
return not bj[GetPlayerId(p)]and See()>=0 and nle(p,1,$1E3660)
endfunction

local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())
return not bj[GetPlayerId(p)]and See()>=0 and nPe(p,1,$1E3660,$A)
endfunction
function Sre takes nothing returns boolean
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())
return not bj[GetPlayerId(p)]and See()>=0 and nPe(p,1,$1E3660,30)
endfunction

local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer jHe=SYe()
local integer abv=jHe
local integer Ope=FX[jHe]
local integer i=0
local boolean jhe=false
local real iqv
call SetUnitPosition(u,GetRectCenterX(JR),GetRectCenterY(JR))
if nme>0 then
loop
if abv<=3 then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=FX[abv]
set jhe=true
else
if abv<=6 then
set iqv=24
elseif abv<=$A then
set iqv=9
elseif abv<=$F then
set iqv=1.2
else
set iqv=.3
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=FX[abv]
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=FX[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('����'+'|{z�')))
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
endif
endif
call jGe(u,GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,FX[jHe]),jhe,abv,Ope,jHe,nme,FX[0])
set u=null
endfunction
function S1e takes nothing returns nothing
if UnitHasItemOfTypeBJ(GetTriggerUnit(),('��'+'���p'))then
call S0e(0)
else
call S0e(1)
endif
endfunction
function S2e takes nothing returns nothing
call S0e($A)
endfunction
function S3e takes nothing returns nothing
call S0e(30)
endfunction
function S4e takes nothing returns integer
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local integer i=0
local integer j
local item OPe
local integer Ope
loop
set OPe=UnitItemInSlot(u,i)
if OPe!=null then
set Ope=GetItemTypeId(OPe)
set j=0
loop
if Ope==gX[j]then
set OPe=null
set u=null
return j
endif
set j=j+1
exitwhen j==20
endloop
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set OPe=null
set u=null
return-1
endfunction
function S5e takes nothing returns boolean
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())
return not bj[GetPlayerId(p)]and S4e()>=0 and nle(p,1,$2255100)
endfunction
function S6e takes nothing returns boolean
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())
return not bj[GetPlayerId(p)]and S4e()>=0 and nPe(p,1,$2255100,$A)
endfunction

local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())
return not bj[GetPlayerId(p)]and S4e()>=0 and nPe(p,1,$2255100,30)

local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())
return not bj[GetPlayerId(p)]and tte()>=0 and nPe(p,1,$A3140C0,30)
endfunction
function twe takes integer nme returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer jHe=tte()
local integer abv=jHe
local integer Ope=UX[jHe]
local integer i=0
local boolean jhe=false
local real iqv
call SetUnitPosition(u,GetRectCenterX(JR),GetRectCenterY(JR))
if nme>0 then
loop
if abv<=3 then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=UX[abv]
set jhe=true
else
if abv<=6 then
set iqv=24
elseif abv<=$A then
set iqv=9
elseif abv<=$F then
set iqv=1.2
else
set iqv=.3
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=UX[abv]
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=UX[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('-I}�'+'��R')))
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
endif
endif
call jGe(u,GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,UX[jHe]),jhe,abv,Ope,jHe,nme,UX[0])
set u=null
endfunction
function tWe takes nothing returns nothing
if UnitHasItemOfTypeBJ(GetTriggerUnit(),('���'+'�<�b'))then
call twe(0)
else
call twe(1)
endif
endfunction

call twe($A)
endfunction
function tYe takes nothing returns nothing
call twe(30)
endfunction
function tze takes nothing returns integer
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local integer i=0
local integer j
local item OPe
local integer Ope
loop
set OPe=UnitItemInSlot(u,i)
if OPe!=null then
set Ope=GetItemTypeId(OPe)
set j=0
loop
if Ope==wX[j]then
set OPe=null
set u=null
return j
endif
set j=j+1
exitwhen j==20
endloop
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set OPe=null
set u=null
return-1
endfunction

function Tre takes nothing returns boolean
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local item i=GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('*���'+'�f'))
local integer Tie=GetItemCharges(i)
local boolean nHe=not bj[GetPlayerId(p)]and Toe()>=0 and Tie>=2 and nle(p,1,$B7E94)
if nHe then
if Tie==2 then
call RemoveItem(i)
else
call SetItemCharges(i,Tie-2)
endif
endif
set i=null
set u=null
return nHe
endfunction

endfunction

local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())
return not bj[GetPlayerId(p)]and TJe()>=0 and nPe(p,1,$28C50300,$A)
endfunction
function Tle takes nothing returns boolean
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())
return not bj[GetPlayerId(p)]and TJe()>=0 and nPe(p,1,$28C50300,30)
endfunction
function TLe takes integer nme returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer jHe=TJe()
local integer abv=jHe
local integer Ope=xO[jHe]
local integer i=0
local boolean jhe=false
local real iqv
call SetUnitPosition(u,GetRectCenterX(JR),GetRectCenterY(JR))
if nme>0 then
loop
if abv<=3 then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=xO[abv]
set jhe=true
else
if abv<=6 then
set iqv=24
elseif abv<=$A then
set iqv=9
elseif abv<=$F then
set iqv=1.2
else
set iqv=.3
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=xO[abv]
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=xO[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('�9�'+'�5A')))
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
endif
endif
call jGe(u,GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,xO[jHe]),jhe,abv,Ope,jHe,nme,xO[0])
set u=null
endfunction
function Tme takes nothing returns nothing
if UnitHasItemOfTypeBJ(GetTriggerUnit(),('s��'+'��s'))then
call TLe(0)
else
call TLe(1)
endif
endfunction
function TMe takes nothing returns nothing
call TLe($A)
endfunction
function Tpe takes nothing returns nothing
call TLe(30)
endfunction
function TPe takes nothing returns integer
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local integer i=0
local integer j
local item OPe
local integer Ope
loop
set OPe=UnitItemInSlot(u,i)
if OPe!=null then
set Ope=GetItemTypeId(OPe)
set j=0
loop
if Ope==oO[j]then
set OPe=null
set u=null
return j
endif
set j=j+1
exitwhen j==20
endloop
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set OPe=null
set u=null
return-1
endfunction

endloop
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set OPe=null
set u=null
return-1
endfunction

function uhe takes integer nme returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer jHe=ufe()
local integer abv=jHe
local integer Ope=OO[jHe]
local integer i=0
local boolean jhe=false
local real iqv
call SetUnitPosition(u,GetRectCenterX(JR),GetRectCenterY(JR))
if nme>0 then
loop
if abv<=3 then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=OO[abv]
set jhe=true
else
if abv<=6 then
set iqv=24
elseif abv<=$A then
set iqv=9
elseif abv<=$F then
set iqv=1.2
else
set iqv=.3
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=OO[abv]
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=OO[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('ה�!'+'9u��')))
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
endif
endif
call jGe(u,GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,OO[jHe]),jhe,abv,Ope,jHe,nme,OO[0])
set u=null
endfunction

function uke takes nothing returns integer

exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set OPe=null
set u=null
return-1
endfunction

function UCe takes integer nme returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer jHe=UNe()
local integer abv=jHe
local integer Ope=GO[jHe]
local integer i=0
local boolean jhe=false
local real iqv
call SetUnitPosition(u,GetRectCenterX(JR),GetRectCenterY(JR))
if nme>0 then
loop
if abv<=3 then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=GO[abv]
set jhe=true
else
if abv<=6 then
set iqv=24
elseif abv<=$A then
set iqv=9
elseif abv<=$F then
set iqv=1.2
else
set iqv=.3
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=GO[abv]
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=GO[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('(mJ�'+'�%�')))
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
endif
endif
call jGe(u,GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,GO[jHe]),jhe,abv,Ope,jHe,nme,GO[0])
set u=null
endfunction

function UFe takes nothing returns integer

function wRe takes integer nme returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer jHe=wVe()
local integer abv=jHe
local integer Ope=lO[jHe]
local integer i=0
local boolean jhe=false
local real iqv
call SetUnitPosition(u,GetRectCenterX(JR),GetRectCenterY(JR))
if nme>0 then
loop
if abv<=3 then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=lO[abv]
set jhe=true
else
if abv<=6 then
set iqv=24
elseif abv<=$A then
set iqv=9
elseif abv<=$F then
set iqv=1.2
else
set iqv=.3
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=lO[abv]
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=lO[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('	R��'+'��')))
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
endif
endif
call jGe(u,GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,lO[jHe]),jhe,abv,Ope,jHe,nme,lO[0])
set u=null
endfunction

function wbe takes nothing returns integer

endloop
set OPe=null

endfunction

function Wie takes integer nme returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer jHe=Wee()
local integer abv=jHe
local integer Ope=pO[jHe]
local integer i=0
local boolean jhe=false
local real iqv
call SetUnitPosition(u,GetRectCenterX(JR),GetRectCenterY(JR))
if nme>0 then
loop
if abv<=3 then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=pO[abv]
set jhe=true
else
if abv<=6 then
set iqv=24
elseif abv<=$A then
set iqv=9
elseif abv<=$F then
set iqv=1.2
else
set iqv=.3
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=iqv*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]then
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=pO[abv]
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
set jhe=true
endif
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=nme or abv>=20
endloop
else
set abv=abv+1
set Ope=pO[abv]
set jhe=true
if abv>3 then
call RemoveItem(GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,('N���'+'�Q�P')))
if abv<=$A then
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,1.2,GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화 성공!!")
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[(1+GetPlayerId(p))]+GetPlayerName(p)+"|r 님이 "+GetObjectName(Ope)+"|R 강화에 성공하였습니다!!")
endif
endif
endif
call jGe(u,GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(u,pO[jHe]),jhe,abv,Ope,jHe,nme,pO[0])
set u=null
endfunction

function WEe takes nothing returns integer

loop

set Ope=GetItemTypeId(OPe)
set j=0

set OPe=null
set u=null
return j
endif
set j=j+1
exitwhen j==20
endloop
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set OPe=null
set u=null
return-1
endfunction

function Whe takes nothing returns boolean

return Ope==('Mv�'+'��{P') or Ope==('��T�'+'x�ƥ') or Ope==('�Ƞ'+'l�m') or Ope==('
`�'+'�v') or Ope==('�Hޓ'+'�{') or Ope==('�:�'+'B!�h') or Ope==('3�z'+'�W�K') or Ope==('(�7�'+'�9') or Ope==('���'+'i:�') or Ope==('Z�'+'�U�')
endfunction
function WHe takes nothing returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local integer Ope=GetItemTypeId(GetManipulatedItem())
local integer Wje=0
if Ope==('O�5�'+'б�') then
if ri[ilv]==0 then
set ri[ilv]=1
set Wje=1
elseif ri[ilv]<7 then
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=5*gi[ilv]then
set ri[ilv]=ri[ilv]+1
set Wje=1
else
set Wje=-1
endif
endif
endif
if Ope==('2�$�'+'ڠ��') then
if ii[ilv]==0 then
set ii[ilv]=1
set Wje=1
elseif ii[ilv]<7 then
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=5*gi[ilv]then
set ii[ilv]=ii[ilv]+1
set Wje=1
else
set Wje=-1
endif
endif
endif
if Ope==('���X'+'DOx�') then
if ai[ilv]==0 then
set ai[ilv]=1
set Wje=1
elseif ai[ilv]<7 then
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=5*gi[ilv]then
set ai[ilv]=ai[ilv]+1
set Wje=1
else
set Wje=-1
endif
endif
endif
if Ope==('�íM'+'E�y�') then
if di[ilv]==0 then
set di[ilv]=1
set Wje=1
elseif di[ilv]<7 then
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=5*gi[ilv]then
set di[ilv]=di[ilv]+1
set Wje=1
else
set Wje=-1
endif
endif
endif
if Ope==('��'+'�l�') then
if mi[ilv]==0 then
set mi[ilv]=1
set Wje=1
elseif mi[ilv]<7 then
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=5*gi[ilv]then
set mi[ilv]=mi[ilv]+1
set Wje=1
else
set Wje=-1
endif
endif
endif
if Ope==('�+h�'+'R�=') then
if Ui[ilv]==0 then
set Ui[ilv]=1
set Wje=1
elseif Ui[ilv]<7 then
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=5*gi[ilv]then
set Ui[ilv]=Ui[ilv]+1
set Wje=1
else
set Wje=-1
endif
endif
endif
if Ope==('����'+'ql~y') then
if Ua[ilv]==0 then
set Ua[ilv]=1
set Wje=1
elseif Ua[ilv]<7 then
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=5*gi[ilv]then
set Ua[ilv]=Ua[ilv]+1
set Wje=1
else
set Wje=-1
endif
endif
endif
if Ope==('��}'+'�r�') and ha[ilv]<7 then
set ha[ilv]=ha[ilv]+1
set Wje=1
endif
if Ope==('+��'+'�}bn') and qn[ilv]<7 then
set qn[ilv]=qn[ilv]+1
set Wje=1
endif
if Ope==('�L�?'+'H�') and MX[ilv]<7 then
set MX[ilv]=MX[ilv]+1
set Wje=1
endif
if Wje==1 then
call nEe(hv[ilv])
elseif Wje==-1 then
call PlaySoundBJ(rN)
call CreateTextTagUnitBJ("스킬 강화에 실패했습니다.",u,25,20,'d',0,0,0)
call SetTextTagPermanent(bj_lastCreatedTextTag,false)
call SetTextTagLifespan(bj_lastCreatedTextTag,3)
call SetTextTagVelocityBJ(bj_lastCreatedTextTag,40,90)
endif
set p=null
set u=null
endfunction

function Wke takes integer Ope returns real
if Ope==li[0]then
return .1*1.
elseif Ope==li[1]then
return .101*1.
elseif Ope==li[2]then
return .103*1.
elseif Ope==li[3]then
return .106*1.
elseif Ope==li[4]then
return .11*1.

function WKe takes unit u,item i returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(u)))
local integer Ope=GetItemTypeId(i)
local real Awe=WJe(Ope)
local real Wle=Wke(Ope)
local boolean aev=false
if Awe>0 then
set Ei[ilv]=Ei[ilv]+Awe
set Ri[ilv]=Ri[ilv]+Awe*10.
call OQe(u,R2I(Ri[ilv]))
set aev=true
endif
if Wle>0 then
set Li[ilv]=Li[ilv]+Wle
set aev=true
endif
if aev then
call Ose(u,R2I(Ei[ilv]*Li[ilv]))
endif
endfunction
function WLe takes unit u,item i returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(u)))
local integer Ope=GetItemTypeId(i)
local real Awe=WJe(Ope)
local real Wle=Wke(Ope)
local boolean aev=false
if Awe>0 then
set Ei[ilv]=Ei[ilv]-Awe
set Ri[ilv]=Ri[ilv]-Awe*10.
call OQe(u,R2I(Ri[ilv]))
set aev=true
endif
if Wle>0 then
set Li[ilv]=Li[ilv]-Wle
set aev=true
endif
if aev then
call Ose(u,R2I(Ei[ilv]*Li[ilv]))
endif
endfunction

function WMe takes unit u,item i returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(u)))
set hi[ilv]=hi[ilv]+Wme(GetItemTypeId(i))
endfunction
function Wpe takes unit u,item i returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(u)))
set hi[ilv]=hi[ilv]-Wme(GetItemTypeId(i))
endfunction

function Wqe takes unit u,item it returns nothing
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local integer Ope=GetItemTypeId(it)
local real WQe=WPe(Ope)
local integer i=0
if WQe>0 then
set FV[ilv]=FV[ilv]+WQe
call DisplayTextToPlayer(p,0,0,"공격력 증가량 = "+R2S(FV[ilv]*'d')+"%")
else
loop
exitwhen i>20
if Ope==To[i]then
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A00N')==0 then
call UnitAddAbility(u,'A00N')
endif
call SetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A00N',i+1)
exitwhen true
endif
if Ope==Br[i]then
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A05F')==0 then
call UnitAddAbility(u,'A05F')
endif
call SetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A05F',i+1)
exitwhen true
endif
set i=i+1
endloop
endif
set p=null
endfunction
function Wse takes unit u,item it returns nothing
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local integer Ope=GetItemTypeId(it)
local real WQe=WPe(Ope)
local integer i=0
if WQe>0 then
set FV[ilv]=FV[ilv]-WQe
call DisplayTextToPlayer(p,0,0,"공격력 증가량 = "+R2S(FV[ilv]*'d')+"%")
else
loop
exitwhen i>20
if Ope==To[i]then
call UnitRemoveAbility(u,'A00N')
exitwhen true
endif
if Ope==Br[i]then
call UnitRemoveAbility(u,'A05F')
exitwhen true
endif
set i=i+1
endloop
endif
set p=null
endfunction

endfunction
function WTe takes unit u,item i returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(u)))
local integer Ope=GetItemTypeId(i)
local real Wue=WSe(Ope)
local real WUe=Wte(Ope)
if Wue>0 then
set Lr[ilv]=Lr[ilv]+Wue
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetOwningPlayer(u),0,0,"추가데미지 = "+R2S(Lr[ilv]*'d')+"%")
endif
if WUe>0 then
set Ar[ilv]=Ar[ilv]+WUe
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetOwningPlayer(u),0,0,"스킬데미지 증가 = "+R2S((Ar[ilv]-1)*'d')+"%")
endif
endfunction
function Wwe takes unit u,item i returns nothing
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(u)))
local integer Ope=GetItemTypeId(i)
local real Wue=WSe(Ope)
local real WUe=Wte(Ope)
if Wue>0 then
set Lr[ilv]=Lr[ilv]-Wue
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetOwningPlayer(u),0,0,"추가데미지 = "+R2S(Lr[ilv]*'d')+"%")
endif
if WUe>0 then
set Ar[ilv]=Ar[ilv]-WUe
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetOwningPlayer(u),0,0,"스킬데미지 증가 = "+R2S((Ar[ilv]-1)*'d')+"%")
endif
endfunction

elseif Ope==qO[$C]then
set Wye=$2FB0FC
elseif Ope==qO[$D]then
set Wye=$402BBC
elseif Ope==qO[$E]then
set Wye=$54A9D4
elseif Ope==qO[$F]then

set Wye=$F740E0
elseif Ope==qO[20]then
set Wye=$123CD2C
endif
endif
if Wye>0 then
if WYe!=0 then
if S[ilv]==1 then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(Player(-1+(ilv)),0,0,"|cffffcc00[System]|r 오버마인드 쿨타임 감소 : "+R2S((1.-sV[ilv])*'d')+"%")
elseif S[ilv]==$A then

elseif S[ilv]==19 then

elseif S[ilv]==$C then
call DisplayTextToPlayer(Player(-1+(ilv)),0,0,"|cffffcc00[System]|r 스트라이커 모든 스킬의 지능비례 수치 증가 : "+R2S((CV[ilv]-1)*'d')+"%")
elseif S[ilv]==7 then

elseif S[ilv]==$E then

endif
endif
set Ei[ilv]=Ei[ilv]+Wye
set Ri[ilv]=Ri[ilv]+Wye*$A
call Ose(hv[ilv],R2I(Ei[ilv]*Li[ilv]))
call OQe(hv[ilv],R2I(Ri[ilv]))
endif
set u=null
endfunction

function W1e takes nothing returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()

function W3e takes nothing returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(u)))
local integer Ope=GetItemTypeId(GetManipulatedItem())
local integer i=0
local boolean B=false
if GetUnitTypeId(u)==('X�͙'+'�rF�') then
loop
if Ope==na[i]then
set Va[ilv]=0
exitwhen true
elseif Ope==ra[i]or Ope==ua[i]or Ope==Ln[i]or Ope==XO[i]then
if S[ilv]==2 then
call RemoveUnit(ia[ilv])
elseif S[ilv]==3 then
set Ta[ilv]=1
endif
exitwhen true
endif
exitwhen i>20
set i=i+1
endloop
endif
set u=null
endfunction
function W5e takes nothing returns boolean
return(GetItemTypeId(GetManipulatedItem())==Ln[bj_forLoopAIndex])or(GetItemTypeId(GetManipulatedItem())==mn[bj_forLoopAIndex])or(GetItemTypeId(GetManipulatedItem())==Mn[bj_forLoopAIndex])or(GetItemTypeId(GetManipulatedItem())==('l�
'+'��@'))
endfunction

function yne takes nothing returns nothing
set bj_forLoopAIndex=0
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=20
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
if(W7e())then
if(W6e())then
else
call Ooe(GetTriggerUnit(),"|c00DFFB4F영웅의 지능이 부족합니다.|r",0,15.,90,1.25,90,90,7,.02,$FF,$FF,$FF,true)
call UnitRemoveItemSwapped(GetManipulatedItem(),GetTriggerUnit())
endif
endif
if(yve())then
if(W8e())then
else
call Ooe(GetTriggerUnit(),"|c00DFFB4F영웅의 지능이 부족합니다.|r",0,15.,90,1.25,90,90,7,.02,$FF,$FF,$FF,true)
call UnitRemoveItemSwapped(GetManipulatedItem(),GetTriggerUnit())
endif
endif
if(yoe())then
if(yee())then
else
call Ooe(GetTriggerUnit(),"|c00DFFB4F영웅의 지능이 부족합니다.|r",0,15.,90,1.25,90,90,7,.02,$FF,$FF,$FF,true)
call UnitRemoveItemSwapped(GetManipulatedItem(),GetTriggerUnit())
endif
endif
if(yae())then
if(yre())then
else
call Ooe(GetTriggerUnit(),"|c00DFFB4F영웅의 지능이 부족합니다.|r",0,15.,90,1.25,90,90,7,.02,$FF,$FF,$FF,true)
call UnitRemoveItemSwapped(GetManipulatedItem(),GetTriggerUnit())
endif
endif
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
endfunction

function yRe takes nothing returns boolean
return(GetItemType(GetManipulatedItem())==ITEM_TYPE_UNKNOWN)or(GetItemType(GetManipulatedItem())==ITEM_TYPE_PURCHASABLE)or(GetItemType(GetManipulatedItem())==ITEM_TYPE_CAMPAIGN)or(GetItemType(GetManipulatedItem())==ITEM_TYPE_POWERUP)

endfunction
