function yKe takes nothing returns nothing
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=6
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=6
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
if(yAe())then
if(yOe())then
call SetItemPlayer(UnitItemInSlotBJ(GetTriggerUnit(),bj_forLoopAIndex),GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit()),false)
endif
call SetItemCharges(UnitItemInSlotBJ(GetTriggerUnit(),bj_forLoopAIndex),(GetItemCharges(UnitItemInSlotBJ(GetTriggerUnit(),bj_forLoopAIndex))+GetItemCharges(GetManipulatedItem())))
call RemoveItem(GetManipulatedItem())
endif
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=6
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
if(yNe())then
call UnitRemoveItemSwapped(GetManipulatedItem(),GetTriggerUnit())
call Ooe(GetTriggerUnit(),"|c00DFFB4F같은 종류의 아이템을 이미 장착중입니다.|r",0,15.,90,1.25,90,90,7,.02,$FF,$FF,$FF,true)
endif
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
set bj_forLoopAIndex=0
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=20
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
if(ybe())then
call RemoveUnit(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))])
call CreateNUnitsAtLoc(1,('���'+'
p�m'),GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit()),GetUnitLoc(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]),bj_UNIT_FACING)
set Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]=bj_lastCreatedUnit
call UnitAddAbility(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],'A0G6')
call SetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0G6',Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],(bj_forLoopAIndex+1))
endif
if(yBe())then
call RemoveUnit(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))])
call CreateNUnitsAtLoc(1,('�I'+':66'),GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit()),GetUnitLoc(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]),bj_UNIT_FACING)
set Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]=bj_lastCreatedUnit
call UnitAddAbility(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],'A0G6')
call SetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0G6',Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],(bj_forLoopAIndex+22))
endif
if(yfe())then
if(yde())then
if(yce())then
call RemoveUnit(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))])
call CreateNUnitsAtLoc(1,('F���'+'ʹ�f'),GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit()),GetUnitLoc(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]),bj_UNIT_FACING)
set Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]=bj_lastCreatedUnit
call UnitAddAbility(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],'A0G6')
call SetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0G6',Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],(bj_forLoopAIndex+43))
endif
if(yCe())then
call RemoveUnit(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))])
call CreateNUnitsAtLoc(1,('U(8'+'�.
'),GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit()),GetUnitLoc(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]),bj_UNIT_FACING)
set Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]=bj_lastCreatedUnit
call UnitAddAbility(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],'A0G6')
call SetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0G6',Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],64)
endif
else
call Ooe(GetTriggerUnit(),"|c00DFFB4F영웅의 지능이 부족합니다.|r",0,15.,90,1.25,90,90,7,.02,$FF,$FF,$FF,true)
call UnitRemoveItemSwapped(GetManipulatedItem(),GetTriggerUnit())
endif
endif
if(yhe())then
if(yge())then
if(yFe())then
call UnitRemoveAbility(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],'A0R9')
call UnitAddAbility(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],'A0R9')
call SetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0R9',Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],(bj_forLoopAIndex+1))
endif
else
call Ooe(GetTriggerUnit(),"|c00DFFB4F영웅의 지능이 부족합니다.|r",0,15.,90,1.25,90,90,7,.02,$FF,$FF,$FF,true)
call UnitRemoveItemSwapped(GetManipulatedItem(),GetTriggerUnit())
endif
endif
if(yke())then
if(yje())then
if(yHe())then
call UnitRemoveAbility(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],'A0R9')
call UnitAddAbility(Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],'A0R9')
call SetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0R9',Xa[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],(bj_forLoopAIndex+22))
endif
else
call Ooe(GetTriggerUnit(),"|c00DFFB4F영웅의 지능이 부족합니다.|r",0,15.,90,1.25,90,90,7,.02,$FF,$FF,$FF,true)
call UnitRemoveItemSwapped(GetManipulatedItem(),GetTriggerUnit())
endif
endif
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
endfunction
function yLe takes unit u,item i returns boolean
local player up=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local player ip=GetItemPlayer(i)
if ip!=up then
if ip==null or ip==Player($F)then
call SetItemPlayer(i,up,true)
else
call UnitRemoveItem(u,i)
call Ooe(u,"|cffFFBE0A'"+GetPlayerName(ip)+"|cffFFBE0A' |c00DFFB4F님의 아이템입니다.|r",0,15.,90,1.25,90,90,7,.02,$FF,$FF,$FF,true)
return false
endif
endif
return true
endfunction
function yme takes unit u,item it returns nothing
local integer i=0
local item yMe
local itemtype t=GetItemType(it)
if(t==ITEM_TYPE_CHARGED or t==ITEM_TYPE_PURCHASABLE or t==ITEM_TYPE_CAMPAIGN or t==ITEM_TYPE_POWERUP)and GetItemCharges(it)==0 then
loop
set yMe=UnitItemInSlot(u,i)
if yMe!=null and yMe!=it and t==GetItemType(yMe)then
call UnitRemoveItem(u,it)
call Ooe(u,"|c00DFFB4F같은 종류의 아이템을 이미 장착중입니다.|r",0,15.,90,1.25,90,90,7,.02,$FF,$FF,$FF,true)
endif
set i=i+1
exitwhen i>=6
endloop
set yMe=null
endif
set t=null
endfunction
function ype takes nothing returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local item i=GetManipulatedItem()
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(u)))
local boolean yPe=yLe(u,i)
if GetItemTypeId(i)==('%�N`'+'�S �') then
set Oj[ilv]=Oj[ilv]+1
if Oj[ilv]>3 then
call UnitRemoveItem(u,i)
call Ooe(u,"|c00DFFB4F이 아이템은 4개 이상 소지할 수 없습니다.|r",0,15.,90,1.25,90,90,7,.02,$FF,$FF,$FF,true)
endif
endif
if u==hv[ilv]then
call WKe(u,i)
call WMe(u,i)
call Wqe(u,i)
call WTe(u,i)
if yPe then
call yme(u,i)
endif
endif
set i=null
set u=null
endfunction
function yqe takes nothing returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local item it=GetManipulatedItem()
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(u)))
local integer Ope=GetItemTypeId(it)
local integer i=0
if Ope==('l�h�'+'�O&') then
set Oj[ilv]=Oj[ilv]-1
endif
if u==hv[ilv]then
call WLe(u,it)
call Wpe(u,it)
call Wse(u,it)
call Wwe(u,it)
elseif GetUnitTypeId(u)==('���'+'$c(�') then
loop
exitwhen i>20
if Ope==Ea[i]then
call RemoveUnit(Xa[ilv])
endif
if Ope==Mn[i]then
call RemoveUnit(Xa[ilv])
endif
set i=i+1
endloop
endif
set it=null
set u=null
endfunction
function yQe takes nothing returns boolean
return GetItemTypeId(GetManipulatedItem())==('�?�v'+'@�&�')
endfunction
function yse takes nothing returns nothing
local unit u=GetTriggerUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
if S[ilv]!=$D then
set Cj[ilv]=u
call DialogSetMessage(Bj[0],"변경할 직업을 선택하세요")
call DialogDisplay(p,Bj[0],true)
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(p,0,0,"|CFFFF3333악귀나찰은 사용할 수 없습니다.")
endif
set p=null
set u=null
endfunction
function ySe takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetTriggerPlayer()
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local button yte=GetClickedButton()
local integer nOe=S[ilv]
local integer nRe=0
local item OPe
if yte==cj[0]then
set nRe=1
elseif yte==cj[1]then
set nRe=2
elseif yte==cj[2]then
set nRe=3
elseif yte==cj[3]then
set nRe=4
elseif yte==cj[4]then
set nRe=5
elseif yte==cj[5]then
set nRe=6
elseif yte==cj[6]then
set nRe=7
elseif yte==cj[7]then
set nRe=8
elseif yte==cj[8]then
set nRe=-1
call DialogSetMessage(Bj[1],"변경할 직업을 선택하세요")
call DialogDisplay(p,Bj[1],true)
elseif yte==cj[9]then
set nRe=9
elseif yte==cj[$A]then
set nRe=$A
elseif yte==cj[$B]then
set nRe=$B
elseif yte==cj[$C]then
set nRe=$C
elseif yte==cj[$D]then
set nRe=$E
elseif yte==cj[$E]then
set nRe=$F
elseif yte==cj[$F]then
set nRe=16
elseif yte==cj[16]then
set nRe=17
elseif yte==cj[17]then
set nRe=18
elseif yte==cj[18]then
set nRe=-1
call DialogSetMessage(Bj[0],"변경할 직업을 선택하세요")
call DialogDisplay(p,Bj[0],true)
endif
if nRe>0 then
if nOe!=nRe then
if nOe==3 then
set hi[ilv]=hi[ilv]-Pa[ilv]
set vV[ilv]=vV[ilv]-eV[ilv]
set Ma[ilv]=0
set Pa[ilv]=0
set Sa[ilv]=0
set zn[ilv]=0
set eV[ilv]=0
endif
if ia[ilv]!=null then
call RemoveUnit(ia[ilv])
endif
if DV[ilv]!=null then
call RemoveUnit(DV[ilv])
endif
if nOe==$E then
call ForGroup(xX[ilv],function AQe)
endif
if dO[ilv]!=null then
call RemoveUnit(dO[ilv])
endif
set S[ilv]=nRe
call Bbe(p,0,true)
endif
set Cj[ilv]=null
elseif nRe==0 then
set OPe=GetItemOfTypeFromUnitBJ(Cj[ilv],('�9�'+'i�.'))
if OPe==null then
set OPe=CreateItem(('���Z'+'%J�'),GetUnitX(Cj[ilv]),GetUnitY(Cj[ilv]))
call SetItemPlayer(OPe,p,true)
call UnitAddItem(Cj[ilv],OPe)
else
call SetItemCharges(OPe,GetItemCharges(OPe)+1)
endif
set OPe=null
set Cj[ilv]=null
endif
set yte=null
set p=null
endfunction
function yTe takes nothing returns nothing
local dialog d=DialogCreate()
call DestroyTimer(GetExpiredTimer())
call TriggerRegisterDialogEvent(UD,d)
set Bj[0]=d
call DialogAddButton(d,"실수로 인한 잘못 사용 방지",0)
set cj[0]=DialogAddButton(d,"오버마인드",0)
set cj[1]=DialogAddButton(d,"아슈타르테",0)
set cj[2]=DialogAddButton(d,"헤카테",0)
set cj[3]=DialogAddButton(d,"지니위즈",0)
set cj[4]=DialogAddButton(d,"데스페라도",0)
set cj[5]=DialogAddButton(d,"무녀",0)
set cj[6]=DialogAddButton(d,"헬벤터",0)
set cj[7]=DialogAddButton(d,"검신",0)
set cj[8]=DialogAddButton(d,">>",0)
call DialogAddButton(d,"취소 (ESC)",512)
set d=DialogCreate()
call TriggerRegisterDialogEvent(UD,d)
set Bj[1]=d
set cj[9]=DialogAddButton(d,"마제스티",0)
set cj[$A]=DialogAddButton(d,"스톰 트루퍼",0)
set cj[$B]=DialogAddButton(d,"인다라천",0)
set cj[$C]=DialogAddButton(d,"스트라이커",0)
set cj[$D]=DialogAddButton(d,"백화요란",0)
set cj[$E]=DialogAddButton(d,"진 : 베가본드",0)
set cj[$F]=DialogAddButton(d,"다크나이트",0)
set cj[16]=DialogAddButton(d,"블레이드",0)
set cj[17]=DialogAddButton(d,"사령술사",0)
set cj[18]=DialogAddButton(d,"<<",0)
call DialogAddButton(d,"취소 (ESC)",512)
set d=null
endfunction

function Yee takes nothing returns nothing

if(yue())then

endif
endif

if(ywe())then
call SetHeroInt(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],(GetHeroStatBJ(2,hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],false)+2),true)
endif
endif

if(yye())then
call SetHeroInt(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],(GetHeroStatBJ(2,hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],false)+$A),true)
endif

endif
endif

if(y_e())then
call SetHeroInt(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],(GetHeroStatBJ(2,hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],false)+5),true)
endif
endif

if(y1e())then
call SetHeroInt(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],(GetHeroStatBJ(2,hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],false)+$F),true)
endif
endif

if(y3e())then
call SetHeroInt(hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],(GetHeroStatBJ(2,hv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))],false)+4),true)
endif
endif

if(y5e())then

function Yoe takes nothing returns boolean

return(GetItemTypeId(GetManipulatedItem())==('��2'+'����'))

return(GetItemTypeId(GetManipulatedItem())==('qB+'+'��S'))

function YEe takes nothing returns nothing
if(Yoe())then
call UnitAddItemByIdSwapped(So[GetRandomInt(0,5)],GetTriggerUnit())
call SetItemPlayer(bj_lastCreatedItem,GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit()),true)
endif
if(Yre())then
call UnitAddItemByIdSwapped(Mo[GetRandomInt(8,$E)],GetTriggerUnit())
endif
if(Yie())then
call UnitAddItemByIdSwapped(Po[GetRandomInt(8,$E)],GetTriggerUnit())
endif
if(Yae())then
call UnitAddItemByIdSwapped(yo[GetRandomInt(0,4)],GetTriggerUnit())
call SetItemPlayer(bj_lastCreatedItem,GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit()),true)
endif
if(Yne())then
call UnitAddItemByIdSwapped(zo[GetRandomInt(0,4)],GetTriggerUnit())
endif
if(YVe())then
call CreateItemLoc(('d(z'+'�	�'),GetUnitLoc(GetTriggerUnit()))
call SetItemPlayer(bj_lastCreatedItem,GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit()),true)
call SetItemCharges(bj_lastCreatedItem,50)
endif
endfunction
function YOe takes location l returns nothing
call StartSound(YA)
call PingMinimap(GetLocationX(l),GetLocationY(l),7)
call UnitApplyTimedLife(CreateUnitAtLoc(Player($C),('
�A�'+'���'),l,bj_UNIT_FACING),'BHwe',3)
endfunction
function YRe takes player p,location l,integer RewTypCla,integer RewAmoCla,integer YIe,integer YAe,real YNe,integer Ybe,integer YBe,real Yce,integer YCe returns nothing
local integer RIe=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
call nhe(p,YIe,R2I(YAe*dj))
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=YNe*gi[RIe]*GH[RIe-1]then
if not JX[RIe]then
call CreateItemLoc(Ybe,l)
call StartSound(YA)
call PingMinimap(GetLocationX(l),GetLocationY(l),7)
call UnitApplyTimedLife(CreateUnitAtLoc(Player($C),('.+�'+'��5�'),l,bj_UNIT_FACING),'BHwe',3)
endif
if YBe!=0 then
call CreateItemLoc(YBe,l)
endif
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=Yce*gi[RIe]*GH[RIe-1]and YCe!=0 then
call CreateItemLoc(YCe,l)
call StartSound(YA)
call PingMinimap(GetLocationX(l),GetLocationY(l),7)
call UnitApplyTimedLife(CreateUnitAtLoc(Player($C),('R���'+'Їf�'),l,bj_UNIT_FACING),'BHwe',3)
endif
if H[RIe]then
call IssueImmediateOrder(No[RIe],G[RIe])
endif
call RemoveLocation(l)
endfunction

if Vkv==('��x)'+'p9��') then
call CreateItemLoc(('0�
�'+'�(?x'),Iqe)
call CreateItemLoc(('݈�!'+')��'),Iqe)
call CreateItemLoc(('��:�'+'�'),Iqe)
call CreateItemLoc(('�!�7'+'�b�'),Iqe)
call CreateItemLoc(('���'+'^@F�'),Iqe)
call CreateItemLoc(('���'+'sv('),Iqe)
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.1*gi[ilv]then
call CreateItemLoc(QO[GetRandomInt(0,2)],Iqe)
call YOe(Iqe)
endif
endif
call RemoveLocation(Iqe)
set Iqe=null
set tu=null
endfunction

function Y7e takes nothing returns nothing

if Vkv==('D'+'q��') then

call nhe(p,0,R2I(20*dj))
endif

function zoe takes nothing returns boolean
return(GetRandomReal(0,100.)<=(5.*gi[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())))]))
endfunction

function zZe takes nothing returns nothing

if OPe==('��1
'+'X�/#') then

elseif OPe==('3�i�'+'Ը�') then
call nhe(p,0,R2I($10B07600*dj))

function z0e takes nothing returns nothing
local unit u=GetBuyingUnit()
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer Ope=GetItemTypeId(GetSoldItem())
local item it
if Ope==('7$c'+'K�*	') then
if nle(p,0,1)then
set it=CreateItem(('�`��'+'`�v�'),GetUnitX(u),GetUnitY(u))
call SetItemPlayer(it,p,true)
call UnitAddItem(u,it)
endif
elseif Ope==('jN�P'+'���') then
if nle(p,0,500)then
set it=CreateItem(('��F�'+'�W�q'),GetUnitX(u),GetUnitY(u))
call SetItemPlayer(it,p,true)
call UnitAddItem(u,it)
endif
elseif Ope==('~.�'+'�@A9') then
if nle(p,0,5000)then
set it=CreateItem(('%x'+'e�'),GetUnitX(u),GetUnitY(u))
call SetItemPlayer(it,p,true)
call UnitAddItem(u,it)
endif
elseif Ope==('�d�'+'�@Ӣ') then
if nle(p,0,$2710)then
set it=CreateItem(('
���'+'���'),GetUnitX(u),GetUnitY(u))
call SetItemPlayer(it,p,true)
call UnitAddItem(u,it)
endif
elseif Ope==('p��5'+'�Fd8') then
if nle(p,0,$2710)then
set it=CreateItem(('�~A�'+'���K'),GetUnitX(u),GetUnitY(u))
call SetItemPlayer(it,p,true)
call UnitAddItem(u,it)
endif
endif
call RemoveItem(GetSoldItem())
set u=null
set it=null

endif

function eRx takes nothing returns nothing
local unit u
call EXv(0)
if Sm[vv]==0 then
call ttv(vv,0,GetUnitLoc(oM[vv]))
call zZv(vv,0,(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(oM[vv]))))
if not La then
set u=CreateUnitAtLoc(GetOwningPlayer(oM[vv]),('��t�'+'���e'),Jz[vv],bj_UNIT_FACING)
call SetUnitTimeScale(u,1.7)
call UnitApplyTimedLife(u,'BHwe',4)
endif
call PlaySoundAtPointBJ(pN,'d',Jz[vv],0)
set u=oM[vv]
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A01G')>0 then
call BlzEndUnitAbilityCooldown((u),('A01G'))
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A052')>0 then
call BlzEndUnitAbilityCooldown((u),('A052'))
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A05E')>0 then
call BlzEndUnitAbilityCooldown((u),('A05E'))
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A0E6')>0 then
call BlzEndUnitAbilityCooldown((u),('A0E6'))
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A0FU')>0 then
call BlzEndUnitAbilityCooldown((u),('A0FU'))
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A0FX')>0 then
call BlzEndUnitAbilityCooldown((u),('A0FX'))
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A0G7')>0 then
call BlzEndUnitAbilityCooldown((u),('A0G7'))
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(u,'A0L7')>0 then
call BlzEndUnitAbilityCooldown((u),('A0L7'))
endif
set u=null
call EVv(vv,.04)
elseif Sm[vv]==1 then
if sV[s2[vv]]!=1 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((oM[vv]),('A0I4'),(((BlzGetUnitAbilityCooldownRemaining((oM[vv]),('A0I4')))*sV[s2[vv]])*1.))
endif
call EVv(vv,2.76)
elseif Sm[vv]==2 then
if not La then
set u=CreateUnitAtLoc(GetOwningPlayer(oM[vv]),('o���'+'��s�'),Jz[vv],bj_UNIT_FACING)
call SetUnitAnimation(u,"Birth")
call SetUnitTimeScale(u,.6)
call UnitApplyTimedLife(u,'BHwe',2)
endif
set u=null
call iMv(uv[s2[vv]],I2R(GetUnitAbilityLevel(oM[vv],'A0I4'))*I2R(GetHeroInt(oM[vv],true))*40000.*Ar[s2[vv]],1500.,GetLocationX(Jz[vv]),GetLocationY(Jz[vv]))
call V9v(vv)
endif
endfunction

function eHx takes nothing returns nothing
call EXv(1)
if(ehx())then
call PYv(vv,0,oM[vv])
call PYv(vv,2,uv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv])))])
call ttv(vv,0,GetUnitLoc(jy[vv]))
call xre(vv,0,GetUnitFacing(jy[vv]))
call iMv(ky[vv],((1.+(I2R(GetHeroStatBJ(2,jy[vv],true))*(I2R(GetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0T2',jy[vv]))*2400000.)))*Ar[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv])))]),1500.,GetLocationX(Jz[vv]),GetLocationY(Jz[vv]))
call StopSoundBJ(WB,false)
call PlaySoundOnUnitBJ(WB,'d',jy[vv])
if(eGx())then
call V9v(vv)
else
call EVv(vv,.04)
endif
else
if(egx())then
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("Nen_Master_Skill_SE11.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((5)*1.))
call n8v(hu[vv],6.25)
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("EskillSE6.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call KBv(vv,1,AddSpecialEffectTarget("EskillSE3.mdx",jy[vv],"chest"))
call n8v(AddSpecialEffectLoc("EskillSE4.mdx",Jz[vv]),3.35)
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=7
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
call QHv(vv,1,xNv(Jz[vv],SquareRoot(GetRandomReal(0,(1000.*1000.))),GetRandomReal(0,360)))
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("EskillSE1.mdx",kz[vv]))
call QHv(vv,1,xNv(Jz[vv],SquareRoot(GetRandomReal(0,(1000.*1000.))),GetRandomReal(0,360)))
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("EskillSE2.mdx",kz[vv]))
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
call EVv(vv,.5)
else
if(eFx())then
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("EskillSE6.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call KBv(vv,2,AddSpecialEffectTarget("EskillSE3.mdx",jy[vv],"chest"))
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("EskillSE4.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((2)*1.))
call n8v(hu[vv],2.7)
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=7
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
call QHv(vv,1,xNv(Jz[vv],SquareRoot(GetRandomReal(0,(1000.*1000.))),GetRandomReal(0,360)))
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("EskillSE1.mdx",kz[vv]))
call QHv(vv,1,xNv(Jz[vv],SquareRoot(GetRandomReal(0,(1000.*1000.))),GetRandomReal(0,360)))
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("EskillSE2.mdx",kz[vv]))
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
call EVv(vv,.6)
else
if(efx())then
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("EskillSE6.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call KBv(vv,3,AddSpecialEffectTarget("EskillSE3.mdx",jy[vv],"chest"))
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("EskillSE4.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((3)*1.))
call n8v(hu[vv],2.05)
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=7
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
call QHv(vv,1,xNv(Jz[vv],SquareRoot(GetRandomReal(0,(1000.*1000.))),GetRandomReal(0,360)))
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("EskillSE1.mdx",kz[vv]))
call QHv(vv,1,xNv(Jz[vv],SquareRoot(GetRandomReal(0,(1000.*1000.))),GetRandomReal(0,360)))
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("EskillSE2.mdx",kz[vv]))
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
call EVv(vv,.0)
else
if(eDx())then
call KBv(vv,4,AddSpecialEffectLoc("EskillSE5.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call EVv(vv,1.)

endif
endif

set Pa[r3[vv]]=(((I2R(GetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0GZ',jy[vv]))*225.)+((I2R(GetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0GZ',jy[vv]))*I2R(GetHeroStatBJ(2,jy[vv],true)))*(.00012)))*Ta[r3[vv]])
endif
else
set Pa[r3[vv]]=(((I2R(GetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0GZ',jy[vv]))*225.)+((I2R(GetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0GZ',jy[vv]))*I2R(GetHeroStatBJ(2,Jy[vv],true)))*(.00012)))*Ta[r3[vv]])
if(oPx())then
set Pa[r3[vv]]=(I2R(GetHeroLevel(Jy[vv]))*.5)
endif
endif
if(oQx())then
call SetUnitLifePercentBJ(qa[r3[vv]],'d')
else
call CreateNUnitsAtLoc(1,('^�l�'+'�|��'),GetOwningPlayer(Jy[vv]),Jz[vv],bj_UNIT_FACING)
set qa[r3[vv]]=bj_lastCreatedUnit
endif
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv]),0,0,"올바른 대상이 아닙니다.")
endif
endif
set hi[r3[vv]]=(hi[r3[vv]]+Pa[r3[vv]])
call DisplayTextToForce(bj_FORCE_ALL_PLAYERS,(ce[r3[vv]]+(GetPlayerName(GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv]))+("|R 님이 "+(ce[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(Jy[vv])))]+(GetPlayerName(GetOwningPlayer(Jy[vv]))+("|R 님에게 |CFFFF0000"+(R2S((Pa[r3[vv]]*1.))+"|R 의 20%확률 지능비례 데미지 능력을 부여합니다."))))))))
call V9v(vv)
endif

function o2x takes nothing returns nothing
local real WQe
call EXv(0)
if Sm[vv]==0 then
call PYv(vv,0,oM[vv])
call PYv(vv,1,JM[vv])
call ttv(vv,0,GetUnitLoc(jy[vv]))
call Ifv(vv,0,GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv]))
call Ifv(vv,1,GetOwningPlayer(Jy[vv]))
call zZv(vv,0,(1+GetPlayerId(Np[vv])))
call zZv(vv,1,(1+GetPlayerId(bp[vv])))
call PlaySoundAtPointBJ(HN,'d',Jz[vv],0)
set Sa[S2[vv]]=0
call OSe(Jy[vv],0)
call EVv(vv,.04)
elseif Sm[vv]==1 then
set WQe=GetUnitAbilityLevel(jy[vv],'A0H5')*Ta[s2[vv]]*.1
if Jy[vv]==jy[vv]then
set WQe=WQe*GetHeroInt(jy[vv],false)
elseif iv[GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv]))]==0 or iv[GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv]))]!=iv[GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(Jy[vv]))]then
if GetHeroInt(jy[vv],false)>=GetHeroInt(Jy[vv],false)then
set WQe=WQe*GetHeroInt(Jy[vv],false)*.15
else
set WQe=WQe*GetHeroInt(jy[vv],false)*.15
endif
if GetWidgetLife(sa[S2[vv]])>0 then
call SetWidgetLife(sa[S2[vv]],GetUnitState(sa[S2[vv]],UNIT_STATE_MAX_LIFE))
else
set sa[S2[vv]]=CreateUnitAtLoc(GetOwningPlayer(Jy[vv]),('1_j�'+'��'),Jz[vv],bj_UNIT_FACING)
endif
else
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv]),0,0,"올바른 대상이 아닙니다.")
endif
set Sa[S2[vv]]=R2I(WQe)
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,ce[s2[vv]]+GetPlayerName(Np[vv])+"|R 님이 "+ce[S2[vv]]+GetPlayerName(bp[vv])+"|R 님에게 |CFFFF0000"+I2S(Sa[S2[vv]])+"|R 만큼 지능 증가 버프를 걸었습니다.")
call EVv(vv,.04)
elseif Sm[vv]==2 then
call OSe(Jy[vv],Sa[S2[vv]])
call V9v(vv)
endif
endfunction

endif
set Lr[S2[vv]]=(Lr[S2[vv]]-zn[S2[vv]])

set Lr[S2[vv]]=(Lr[S2[vv]]+zn[S2[vv]])

function rlx takes nothing returns nothing

call DisplayTextToPlayer(Player(ilv-1),0,0,"-초월-편애 버프종료")
call RemoveUnit(u)
set u=null
endfunction

function ryx takes nothing returns nothing
call EXv(1)
if(rWx())then
call PYv(vv,0,oM[vv])
call PYv(vv,2,uv[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv])))])
call ttv(vv,0,GetUnitLoc(jy[vv]))
call xre(vv,0,GetUnitFacing(jy[vv]))
call iMv(ky[vv],((1.+(I2R(GetHeroStatBJ(2,jy[vv],true))*(I2R(GetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0T4',jy[vv]))*2000000.)))*Ar[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv])))]),1500.,GetLocationX(Jz[vv]),GetLocationY(Jz[vv]))
call StopSoundBJ(YB,false)
call PlaySoundOnUnitBJ(YB,'d',jy[vv])
if(rwx())then
call V9v(vv)
else
call EVv(vv,.04)
endif
else
if(rUx())then
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("Nen_Master_Skill_SE11.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((5)*1.))
call n8v(hu[vv],8.2)
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("HskillSE1.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((2.25)*1.))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectYaw((hu[vv]),((270)*1.))

else

call zZv(vv,0,GetRandomInt(1,4))
if(ahx())then

else
if(aGx())then

else
if(agx())then

else
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("GskillSE10.mdx",kz[vv]))
endif
endif
endif
call EVv(vv,.15)
else
if(aFx())then
call EVv(vv,.2)
else
call n8v(AddSpecialEffectTarget("GskillSE11.mdx",jy[vv],"origin"),1.8)
call V9v(vv)
endif
endif
endif
endif
endif
endif
endif

function Atx takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local unit u=LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$286B853A)
local real ATx=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$318A7F74)
local real Aux=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$F9C6D145)
local real AUx=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$28126BD7)
local real Awx=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$C9DBDDA)
local real AWx=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$4CE555A)
local real Ayx=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$4C8D1FC6)
local real AYx=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$54DD8B83)
local real aav=LoadReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$7A24E61E)
if AYx<=1 then
if AYx<=.5 then
call SetUnitFlyHeight(u,aav*AYx,0)
call SetUnitVertexColorBJ(u,'d','d','d',100.)
call SetUnitVertexColor(u,$FF,$FF,$FF,0)
else
call SetUnitFlyHeight(u,aav*AYx-aav*(AYx-.5)-50,0)
call SetUnitVertexColor(u,$FF,$FF,$FF,$FF)
endif
call SetUnitX(u,ATx*(1-AYx)*(1-AYx)+AWx*AYx*AYx+AUx*2.*AYx*(1.-AYx))
call SetUnitY(u,Aux*(1-AYx)*(1-AYx)+Ayx*AYx*AYx+Awx*2.*AYx*(1.-AYx))
call SetUnitFacingTimed(u,bj_RADTODEG*Atan2(Ayx-GetUnitY(u),AWx-GetUnitX(u)),0)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$54DD8B83,AYx+GetRandomReal(.03,.07))
call TimerStart(t,.025,false,function Atx)
else
call SetUnitFlyHeight(u,0,0)
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffect("Abilities\\Weapons\\SteamTank\\SteamTankImpact.mdl",AWx,Ayx))
call KillUnit(u)
call DestroyTimer(t)
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
endif
set t=null
set u=null
endfunction
function Azx takes unit u,location nKv,location AZx,location A_x returns nothing
local timer t=CreateTimer()
call SaveUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$286B853A,u)
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$318A7F74,GetUnitX(u))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$F9C6D145,GetUnitY(u))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$28126BD7,GetLocationX(AZx))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$C9DBDDA,GetLocationY(AZx))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$4CE555A,GetLocationX(A_x)+GetRandomReal(0,750)*Cos(GetRandomInt(1,360)*bj_DEGTORAD))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$4C8D1FC6,GetLocationY(A_x)+GetRandomReal(0,750)*Sin(GetRandomInt(1,360)*bj_DEGTORAD))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$7A24E61E,GetRandomReal(350,600))
call SaveReal(F,GetHandleId(t),$54DD8B83,0)
call TimerStart(t,.025,false,function Atx)
set t=null
endfunction

function bGx takes nothing returns nothing
call EXv(1)
if(bgx())then
call PYv(vv,0,GetEventDamageSource())
call PYv(vv,1,oM[vv])

call ttv(vv,0,GetUnitLoc(jy[vv]))
call ttv(vv,1,GetUnitLoc(Jy[vv]))

call zZv(vv,$F,(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv]))))
call iMv(ky[vv],((1.+(I2R(GetHeroStatBJ(2,jy[vv],true))*(I2R(GetUnitAbilityLevelSwapped('A0TC',jy[vv]))*2000000.)))*Ar[(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(jy[vv])))]),1500.,GetLocationX(Jz[vv]),GetLocationY(Jz[vv]))
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((jy[vv]),('A0TC'),((300)*1.))
call StopSoundBJ(uB,false)
call PlaySoundOnUnitBJ(uB,'d',jy[vv])
set QX[r3[vv]]=true
if(bFx())then
call Eiv(vv,300.,50)
else
call EVv(vv,.04)
endif
else
if(bDx())then
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("Nen_Master_Skill_SE11.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((5)*1.))
call n8v(hu[vv],6.7)
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE1.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((2)*1.))
call n8v(hu[vv],1.25)
call EVv(vv,.35)
else
if(bdx())then
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE2.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((.75)*1.))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectYaw((hu[vv]),((270)*1.))
call n8v(hu[vv],1.)
call EVv(vv,1.)
else
if(bCx())then
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE3.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((.65)*1.))
call DestroyEffect(hu[vv])
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE5.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((3.5)*1.))
call n8v(hu[vv],3.4)
call EVv(vv,.7)
else
if(bcx())then
call QHv(vv,1,xNv(Jz[vv],SquareRoot(GetRandomReal((200.*200.),(1250.*1250.))),GetRandomReal(0,360)))
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE4.mdx",kz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((GetRandomReal(.5,1))*1.))
call DestroyEffect(hu[vv])
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE6.mdx",kz[vv]))

else
if(bBx())then
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=2
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
call QHv(vv,1,xNv(Jz[vv],SquareRoot(GetRandomReal((200.*200.),(1250.*1250.))),GetRandomReal(0,360)))

call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((GetRandomReal(.5,1))*1.))

call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE8.mdx",kz[vv]))
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
if(bbx())then
call EVv(vv,.07)
else
call EVv(vv,.65)
endif
else
if(bNx())then
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE10.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE11.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((3)*1.))
call DestroyEffect(hu[vv])
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=(3+(Sm[vv]-40))
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
call QHv(vv,1,xNv(Jz[vv],SquareRoot(GetRandomReal((200.*200.),(1250.*1250.))),GetRandomReal(0,360)))
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE9.mdx",kz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectHeight((hu[vv]),((GetRandomInt($96,500))*1.))
call DestroyEffect(hu[vv])
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
set bj_forLoopAIndex=1
set bj_forLoopAIndexEnd=5
loop
exitwhen bj_forLoopAIndex>bj_forLoopAIndexEnd
call QHv(vv,1,xNv(Jz[vv],SquareRoot(GetRandomReal((200.*200.),(1250.*1250.))),GetRandomReal(0,360)))
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE4.mdx",kz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((GetRandomReal(.5,1))*1.))
call DestroyEffect(hu[vv])
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE6.mdx",kz[vv]))
set bj_forLoopAIndex=bj_forLoopAIndex+1
endloop
if(bAx())then
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("Nen_Master_Skill_SE10.mdl",Jz[vv]))
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("MskillSE15.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE3.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call BlzSetSpecialEffectScale((hu[vv]),((.65)*1.))
call DestroyEffect(hu[vv])
call EVv(vv,.3)
else
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("Soul_Blaed_SkillSE9.mdl",Jz[vv]))
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("Asura_SkillSE12.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call EVv(vv,.65)
endif
else
if(bIx())then
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("Nen_Master_Skill_SE10.mdl",Jz[vv]))
call Eiv(vv,294.33,50)
endif
endif
endif
endif
endif
endif
endif
if(bfx())then
set QX[r3[vv]]=false
call V9v(vv)
endif
endif
endfunction
function bHx takes nothing returns boolean
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))
return fj[ilv]and I2S(Dj[ilv])==SubString(GetEventPlayerChatString(),1,7)
endfunction
function bjx takes nothing returns nothing
set fj[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=false
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),0,0,$A,"|cffFFCD28입력되었습니다.|r")
endfunction
function bJx takes nothing returns boolean
local integer bkx=GetSpellAbilityId()
return bkx=='A0QG' or bkx=='A0QH' or bkx=='A0QI' or bkx=='A0QJ' or bkx=='A0QK' or bkx=='A0QL' or bkx=='A0QM' or bkx=='A0QN' or bkx=='A0RB'
endfunction
function bKx takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local integer ilv=LoadInteger(F,GetHandleId(t),$B79E5965)
local player p=Player(-1+(ilv))
local integer blx=GetPlayerStartLocation(p)
set Dj[ilv]=0
if fj[ilv]then
set fj[ilv]=false
call SetUnitPosition(hv[ilv],GetStartLocationX(blx),GetStartLocationY(blx))
if ha[ilv]>0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((hv[ilv]),('A0QN'),((300.)*1.))
else
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((hv[ilv]),('A0QG'),((300.)*1.))
endif
if qn[ilv]>0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((hv[ilv]),('A0RB'),((300.)*1.))
elseif ii[ilv]>0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((hv[ilv]),('A0QH'),((300.)*1.))
endif
if ai[ilv]>0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((hv[ilv]),('A0QI'),((300.)*1.))
endif
if di[ilv]>0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((hv[ilv]),('A0QJ'),((300.)*1.))
endif
if mi[ilv]>0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((hv[ilv]),('A0QK'),((300.)*1.))
endif
if Ui[ilv]>0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((hv[ilv]),('A0QL'),((300.)*1.))
endif
if Ua[ilv]>0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((hv[ilv]),('A0QM'),((300.)*1.))
endif
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,GetPlayerName(p)+"|R님에게 부정한 기운이 누적되어 강제로 귀환 당합니다.
또한, 모든 스킬을 5분간 사용할 수 없게 됩니다. (매크로 의심)")
endif
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
set t=null
set p=null
endfunction
function bLx takes nothing returns nothing
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(GetTriggerUnit())
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local timer t
set nX[ilv]=nX[ilv]+1
if nX[ilv]>=3 then
set nX[ilv]=0
set Dj[ilv]=GetRandomInt($186A0,$F423F)
set fj[ilv]=true
call DisplayTimedTextToPlayer(p,0,0,20,"|CFFDFFB4F20초 내로 |CFFFFCD28'-"+I2S(Dj[ilv])+"|CFFFFCD28' |CFFDFFB4F를 입력하세요.")
set t=CreateTimer()
call SaveInteger(F,GetHandleId(t),$B79E5965,ilv)
call TimerStart(t,20.,false,function bKx)
set t=null
endif
set p=null
endfunction

else
set KE[(1+GetPlayerId(GetTriggerPlayer()))]=true
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetTriggerPlayer(),0,0,"스킬의 타이핑이 자동으로 입력됩니다.")
endif
endfunction

set VE[s2[vv]]=GetUnitLoc(Jy[vv])

set ZE[s2[vv]]=Jy[vv]
call EVv(vv,.04)
endif

call SetTextTagFadepointBJ(bj_lastCreatedTextTag,2.7)
call SetTextTagVelocityBJ(bj_lastCreatedTextTag,60.,90)
set nE[s2[vv]]=bj_lastCreatedTextTag
call V9v(vv)
endif
endfunction

else

call QHv(vv,1,xNv(Jz[vv],500.,T4[vv]))
call KBv(vv,0,AddSpecialEffectLoc("Vegabond_SkillSE9.mdx",kz[vv]))

else
if(fyx())then
call RemoveUnit(Jy[vv])
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("Vegabond_SkillSE10.mdx",kz[vv]))
call EVv(vv,.3)
else
if(fWx())then

function FAx takes nothing returns nothing
local timer t=GetExpiredTimer()
local unit u=LoadUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(t),$FC63F4B2)
local integer FNx=LoadInteger(F,GetHandleId(u),$79885D8A)-1
call SaveInteger(F,GetHandleId(u),$79885D8A,FNx)
if FNx<=0 then
call BlzSetUnitAttackCooldown((u),((.5)*1.),(1)-1)
call FlushChildHashtable(F,GetHandleId(t))
call DestroyTimer(t)
if LoadBoolean(F,GetHandleId(u),$212FEA52)then
call SaveBoolean(F,GetHandleId(u),$212FEA52,false)
endif
endif
set t=null
set u=null
endfunction
function Fbx takes unit u,real ncv,real FBx,boolean Fcx returns nothing
local player p=GetOwningPlayer(u)
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(p))
local integer FNx=LoadInteger(F,GetHandleId(u),$79885D8A)
if Fcx then
call BlzSetUnitAttackCooldown((u),((.5*('d'/('d'+FBx+zX[ilv])))*1.),(1)-1)
call SaveInteger(F,GetHandleId(u),$79885D8A,R2I(ncv/ .5))
call SaveBoolean(F,GetHandleId(u),$212FEA52,true)
elseif not LoadBoolean(F,GetHandleId(u),$212FEA52)then
call SaveInteger(F,GetHandleId(u),$79885D8A,FNx+R2I(ncv/ .5))
endif
if FNx==0 then
set Fj[ilv]=CreateTimer()
call BlzSetUnitAttackCooldown((u),((.5*('d'/('d'+FBx+zX[ilv])))*1.),(1)-1)
call SaveUnitHandle(F,GetHandleId(Fj[ilv]),$FC63F4B2,u)
call TimerStart(Fj[ilv],.5,true,function FAx)
elseif LoadBoolean(F,GetHandleId(u),$212FEA52)then
call TimerStart(Fj[ilv],.5,true,function FAx)
endif
set p=null
endfunction

return(Sm[vv]==2)

call DestroyEffect(hu[vv])
call EVv(vv,.35)
else
if(hsx())then
call EVv(vv,2.39)
else
if(hQx())then
call DestroyEffect(Hu[vv])
call DestroyEffect(ju[vv])
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("NecroSkillSEJ.mdx",Jz[vv]))

call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("NecroSkillSEL.mdx",Jz[vv]))
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffectLoc("NecroSkillSEM.mdx",Jz[vv]))

call V9v(vv)
endif

function LogEventDamage takes nothing returns nothing
local real iLv=GetEventDamage()
local unit xbv=GetEventDamageSource()
local integer ilv=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(xbv)))
local integer at=GetHandleId((BlzGetEventAttackType()))
local integer dt=GetHandleId((BlzGetEventDamageType()))
local string i6v="["+I2S(ilv)+"] "+R2SW(GetEventDamage(),0,0)
if xbv==hv[ilv]then
set i6v="hero"+i6v
elseif xbv==uv[ilv]then
set i6v="bag"+i6v
elseif xbv==Io[ilv]then
set i6v="bag2"+i6v
elseif xbv==No[ilv]then
set i6v="bag3"+i6v
elseif xbv==Ai[ilv]then
set i6v="Damage_Unit"+i6v
else
set i6v="unknown"+i6v
endif
if at==0 then
set i6v=i6v+" / NORMAL"
elseif at==1 then
set i6v=i6v+" / MELEE"
elseif at==2 then
set i6v=i6v+" / PIERCE"
elseif at==3 then
set i6v=i6v+" / SIEGE"
elseif at==4 then
set i6v=i6v+" / MAGIC"
elseif at==5 then
set i6v=i6v+" / CHAOS"
elseif at==6 then
set i6v=i6v+" / HERO"
else
set i6v=i6v+" / NULL("+I2S(at)+")"
endif
if dt==0 then
set i6v=i6v+" / UNKNOWN"
elseif dt==4 then
set i6v=i6v+" / NORMAL"
elseif dt==5 then
set i6v=i6v+" / ENHANCED"
elseif dt==8 then
set i6v=i6v+" / FIRE"
elseif dt==9 then
set i6v=i6v+" / COLD"
elseif dt==$A then
set i6v=i6v+" / LIGHTNING"
elseif dt==$B then
set i6v=i6v+" / POISON"
elseif dt==$C then
set i6v=i6v+" / DISEASE"
elseif dt==$D then
set i6v=i6v+" / DIVINE"
elseif dt==$E then
set i6v=i6v+" / MAGIC"
elseif dt==$F then
set i6v=i6v+" / SONIC"
elseif dt==16 then
set i6v=i6v+" / ACID"
elseif dt==17 then
set i6v=i6v+" / FORCE"
elseif dt==18 then
set i6v=i6v+" / DEATH"
elseif dt==19 then
set i6v=i6v+" / MIND"
elseif dt==20 then
set i6v=i6v+" / PLANT"
elseif dt==21 then
set i6v=i6v+" / DEFENSIVE"
elseif dt==22 then
set i6v=i6v+" / DEMOLITION"
elseif dt==23 then
set i6v=i6v+" / SLOW_POISON"
elseif dt==24 then
set i6v=i6v+" / SPIRIT_LINK"
elseif dt==25 then
set i6v=i6v+" / SHADOW_STRIKE"
elseif dt==26 then
set i6v=i6v+" / UNIVERSAL"
else
set i6v=i6v+" / NULL("+I2S(dt)+")"
endif
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetLocalPlayer(),0,0,i6v)
endfunction
function jGx takes nothing returns nothing
local unit T=GetTriggerUnit()
local unit D=GetEventDamageSource()
local integer ID=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(D)))
local location LT=GetUnitLoc(T)
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A04T')>0 or GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0SY')>0 then
call TriggerExecute(Ph)
endif
if IsUnitType(D,UNIT_TYPE_HERO)then
if S[ID]==16 then
call TriggerExecute(th)
endif
if S[ID]==7 then
call TriggerExecute(Sh)
endif
if S[ID]==$F then
call TriggerExecute(Th)
endif
if S[ID]==9 then
call TriggerExecute(qh)
endif
if S[ID]==$D then
call TriggerExecute(uh)
endif
if S[ID]==8 then
call TriggerExecute(wh)
endif
if(GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0O8')>0 or GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0OF')>0)and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<17 then
call TriggerExecute(bg)
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0RC')>0 then
call Vov(uv[ID],T,GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0RC')*I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*6.*Ar[ID],1,1,0,"","")
endif
if oX[ID]then
call Vov(No[ID],T,GetUnitAbilityLevel(hv[ID],'A0RI')*I2R(GetHeroInt(hv[ID],true))*$4B0*Ar[ID],1,1,1,"","")
endif
if S[ID]==$C then
call TriggerExecute(Qh)
if not La then
call n8v(AddSpecialEffectTarget("Abilities\\Spells\\Items\\OrbCorruption\\OrbCorruptionSpecialArt.mdx",T,"chest"),.5)
endif
if pV[ID]then
call Vov(uv[ID],T,GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0PI')*I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*1200.*Ar[ID],1,1,0,"","")
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0PL')>0 then
if qV[ID]>=5 then
call iMv(No[ID],Ar[ID]*GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0PL')*I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*1000.,550,GetUnitX(D),GetUnitY(D))
set qV[ID]=0
else
set qV[ID]=qV[ID]+1
endif
endif
endif
if S[ID]==6 then
call TriggerExecute(sh)
endif
if S[ID]==$B then
call TriggerExecute(Uh)
endif
if Ya[ID]then
call iMv(No[ID],Ar[ID]*GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0II')*I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*800.,750,GetUnitX(T),GetUnitY(T))
endif
if S[ID]==5 then
call TriggerExecute(ph)
endif
if S[ID]==18 then
call TriggerExecute(Wh)
endif
if S[ID]==17 then
set yX[ID]=yX[ID]+1
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0U4')>0 and yX[ID]>=9 then
call TriggerExecute(wG)
set yX[ID]=0
elseif GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0UB')>0 and yX[ID]>=60 then
call TriggerExecute(eh)
set yX[ID]=0
endif
if VO[ID]then
call Vov(No[ID],T,GetUnitAbilityLevel(hv[ID],'A0U8')*I2R(GetHeroInt(hv[ID],true))*$4B0*Ar[ID],1,1,1,"","")
endif
endif
if S[ID]==19 then
call TriggerExecute(yh)
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=20+Va[ID]and hi[ID]>0 then
if La then
call UnitDamageTargetBJ(No[ID],T,I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*hi[ID]*1.5*SE[ID],ATTACK_TYPE_NORMAL,DAMAGE_TYPE_MAGIC)
else
call Vov(No[ID],T,I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*hi[ID]*1.5*SE[ID],1,1,3,"Abilities\\Spells\\Human\\MarkOfChaos\\MarkOfChaosTarget.mdl","origin")
endif
endif
if FV[ID]>=.01 then
call UnitDamageTargetBJ(Ai[ID],T,(FV[ID]+Ma[ID])*(GetEventDamage()*.5),ATTACK_TYPE_CHAOS,DAMAGE_TYPE_UNIVERSAL)
endif
else
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0RF')>0 then
call Vov(No[ID],T,GetUnitAbilityLevel(hv[ID],'A0RE')*I2R(GetHeroInt(hv[ID],true))*240.*Ar[ID],1,1,1,"","")
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0W0')>0 then
call Vov(No[ID],T,GetUnitAbilityLevel(hv[ID],'A0VZ')*I2R(GetHeroInt(hv[ID],true))*80.*Ar[ID]*CV[ID],1,1,1,"","")
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1.5 then
call TriggerExecute(nh)
endif
endif
if D==uv[ID]then
if vn[ID]then
call Vov(No[ID],T,GetUnitAbilityLevel(hv[ID],'A0IJ')*I2R(GetHeroInt(hv[ID],true))*1000.*Ar[ID],1,1,1,"","")
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(hv[ID],'B00T')>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<$F then
call TriggerExecute(NF)
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(T,'B01E')>0 then
call Vov(Ai[ID],T,((di[ID]*500)+(di[ID]*I2R(GetHeroInt(hv[ID],true))*(500*Hj[ID])))*Ar[ID],1,1,0,"","")
endif
if vV[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<7 then
call UnitDamageTargetBJ(No[ID],T,GetEventDamage()*vV[ID],ATTACK_TYPE_CHAOS,DAMAGE_TYPE_UNIVERSAL)
if not La then
call CreateTextTagLocBJ("매직 크리티컬!!",LT,$A,$F,$FF,0,0,0)
call SetTextTagPermanent(bj_lastCreatedTextTag,false)
call SetTextTagLifespan(bj_lastCreatedTextTag,3)
call SetTextTagVelocityBJ(bj_lastCreatedTextTag,40,90)
endif
endif
endif
endif
if(BlzGetUnitIntegerField((T),UNIT_IF_DEFENSE_TYPE))==5 then
call BlzSetEventDamage(((GetEventDamage()*.00001)*1.))
endif
if Lr[ID]>=.01 and D!=Ai[ID]then
call UnitDamageTargetBJ(Ai[ID],T,Lr[ID]*(GetEventDamage()*.14),ATTACK_TYPE_CHAOS,DAMAGE_TYPE_UNIVERSAL)
endif
call RemoveLocation(LT)
set LT=null
set D=null
set T=null
endfunction
function jbx takes nothing returns nothing
local integer i=1
set Mh=CreateTrigger()
call TriggerAddAction(Mh,function jGx)
loop
exitwhen i>$C
set Hj[i]=1
set i=i+1
endloop
endfunction
function jhx takes nothing returns nothing
local unit T=GetTriggerUnit()
local unit D=GetEventDamageSource()
local integer ID=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(D)))
if mX[ID]then
set mX[ID]=false
call TriggerExecute(AF)
endif
if PV[ID]then
set PV[ID]=false
call ConditionalTriggerExecute(DF)
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'B00T')>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<$F then
call ConditionalTriggerExecute(NF)
endif
set D=null
set T=null
endfunction
function jjx takes nothing returns nothing
local unit T=GetTriggerUnit()
local unit D=GetEventDamageSource()
local integer ID=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(D)))
if IsUnitType(D,UNIT_TYPE_HERO)then
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A05A')>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=$A+sn[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(lf)
endif
if fi[ID]then
call Vov(uv[ID],T,(di[ID]+Jn[ID])*I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*500*CV[ID]*Ar[ID],1,1,0,"","")
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'B00A')>0 then
call Vov(uv[ID],T,GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0FV')*I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*250.*CV[ID]*Ar[ID],1,1,0,"","")
endif
if sn[ID]>0 then
call Vov(uv[ID],T,qn[ID]*I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*4000.*CV[ID]*Ar[ID],1,1,0,"","")
endif
if ZX[ID]then
set ZX[ID]=false
call TriggerExecute(kf)
endif
if LX[ID]then
set LX[ID]=false
call TriggerExecute(Pf)
endif
if PX[ID]then
set PX[ID]=false
call TriggerExecute(Qf)
endif
endif
set D=null
set T=null
endfunction
function jkx takes nothing returns nothing
local unit T=GetTriggerUnit()
local unit D=GetEventDamageSource()
local integer ID=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(D)))
if RV[ID]>0 then
set RV[ID]=RV[ID]-1
if La then
call Vov(uv[ID],T,GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0NC')*I2R(GetHeroInt(hv[ID],true))*$96*Ar[ID],1,1,1,"","")
else
call Vov(uv[ID],T,GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0NC')*I2R(GetHeroInt(hv[ID],true))*$96*Ar[ID],1,1,1,"Majesty_Skill02.mdl","origin")
endif
endif
if IV[ID]then
set IV[ID]=false
call TriggerExecute(og)
endif
if AV[ID]then
set AV[ID]=false
call TriggerExecute(ig)
endif
if mi[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=$A then
call TriggerExecute(ag)
endif
if bV[ID]then
set bV[ID]=false
call TriggerExecute(Vg)
endif
if BV[ID]then
set BV[ID]=false
call TriggerExecute(Xg)
endif
if dV[ID]then
call Vov(uv[ID],T,I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*I2R(GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0NJ'))*2000.*CV[ID]*Ar[ID],1.,1.,1.,"","")
if not La then
call SetUnitX(DV[ID],GetUnitX(D))
call SetUnitY(DV[ID],GetUnitY(D))
call SetUnitAnimation(DV[ID],"attack")
endif
endif
if fV[ID]then
set fV[ID]=false
call TriggerExecute(Ig)
endif
if sX[ID]then
set sX[ID]=false
call TriggerExecute(Ng)
endif
set D=null
set T=null
endfunction
function jlx takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ID=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetEventDamageSource())))
if MV[ID]then
set MV[ID]=false
call TriggerExecute(bG)
endif
if QV[ID]then
set QV[ID]=false
call TriggerExecute(cG)
endif
endfunction
function jmx takes nothing returns nothing
local unit T=GetTriggerUnit()
local unit D=GetEventDamageSource()
local integer ID=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(D)))
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0JR')>0 then
set cn[ID]=cn[ID]+1
if cn[ID]>=20-GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0JV')*dn[ID]then
set cn[ID]=0
if Bn[ID]<50+5*GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0JV')then
set Bn[ID]=Bn[ID]+1
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetOwningPlayer(D),0,0,"|CFF00A5FF공력의구 갯수 :  |CFFFF0000"+I2S(Bn[ID]))
endif
endif
if Cn[ID]and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=20 then
set Bn[ID]=Bn[ID]-1
call Vov(uv[ID],T,GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0JR')*I2R(GetHeroInt(hv[ID],true))*1500.*Ar[ID],1,1,0,"","")
call DisplayTextToPlayer(GetOwningPlayer(D),0,0,"|CFF00A5FF공력의구 갯수 :  |CFFFF0000"+I2S(Bn[ID]))
endif
endif
set D=null
set T=null
endfunction
function jpx takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ID=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetEventDamageSource())))
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=5*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(mF)
endif
if ii[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=3*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(MF)
endif
if ai[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=2.4*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(pF)
endif
if di[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1.8*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(PF)
endif
if mi[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(qF)
endif
if Ui[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.6*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(QF)
endif
if Ua[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.5*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(sF)
endif
if ha[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.5*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(SF)
endif
if qn[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.5*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(tF)
endif
if MX[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=5*ln[ID]then
if qX[ID]==false then
call TriggerExecute(TF)
endif
endif
endfunction
function jqx takes nothing returns nothing
local unit T=GetTriggerUnit()
local unit D=GetEventDamageSource()
local integer ID=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetEventDamageSource())))
local integer R=0
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=5*ln[ID]then
set R=GetRandomInt(1,2)
if R==1 then
call TriggerExecute(mF)
elseif R==2 then
call TriggerExecute(Gg)
endif
endif
if ii[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=2.7*ln[ID]then
set R=GetRandomInt(1,3)
if R==1 then
call TriggerExecute(MF)
elseif R==2 then
call TriggerExecute(hg)
elseif R==3 then
call TriggerExecute(uF)
endif
endif
if ai[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=2*ln[ID]then
set R=GetRandomInt(1,3)
if R==1 then
call TriggerExecute(pF)
elseif R==2 then
call TriggerExecute(Hg)
elseif R==3 then
call TriggerExecute(UF)
endif
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'B017')>0 then
call Vov(uv[ID],T,ai[ID]*I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*200.*Ar[ID],1,1,0,"","")
endif
if di[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1.5*ln[ID]then
set R=GetRandomInt(1,3)
if R==1 then
call TriggerExecute(PF)
elseif R==2 then
call TriggerExecute(jg)
elseif R==3 then
call TriggerExecute(wF)
endif
endif
if mi[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1*ln[ID]then
set R=GetRandomInt(1,3)
if R==1 then
call TriggerExecute(qF)
elseif R==2 then
call TriggerExecute(Jg)
elseif R==3 then
call TriggerExecute(WF)
endif
endif
if Ui[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.7*ln[ID]then
set R=GetRandomInt(1,3)
if R==1 then
call TriggerExecute(QF)
elseif R==2 then
call TriggerExecute(kg)
elseif R==3 then
call TriggerExecute(yF)
endif
endif
if LV[ID]then
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.5*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(Mg)
endif
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=$C*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(Kg)
endif
endif
if Ua[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.5*ln[ID]then
set R=GetRandomInt(1,3)
if R==1 then
call TriggerExecute(sF)
elseif R==2 then
call TriggerExecute(lg)
elseif R==3 then
call TriggerExecute(YF)
endif
endif
if ha[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.5*ln[ID]then
set R=GetRandomInt(1,3)
if R==1 then
call TriggerExecute(SF)
elseif R==2 then
call TriggerExecute(Lg)
elseif R==3 then
call TriggerExecute(zF)
endif
endif
if qn[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.5*ln[ID]then
set R=GetRandomInt(1,3)
if R==1 then
call TriggerExecute(tF)
elseif R==2 then
call TriggerExecute(mg)
elseif R==3 then
call TriggerExecute(ZF)
endif
endif
if MX[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=5*ln[ID]and not QX[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(UG)
endif
set D=null
set T=null
endfunction
function jsx takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ID=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetEventDamageSource())))
if GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=2.5*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(MG)
endif
if ii[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=2*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(pG)
endif
if ai[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=2*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(PG)
endif
if di[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1.3*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(qG)
endif
if di[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(QG)
endif
if Ui[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(sG)
endif
if Ua[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.5*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(SG)
endif
if ha[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.5*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(tG)
endif
if qn[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.5*ln[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(TG)
endif
if MX[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=5*ln[ID]then
if QX[ID]==false then
call TriggerExecute(uG)
endif
endif
endfunction
function jtx takes nothing returns nothing
local integer ID=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(GetEventDamageSource())))
if ha[ID]>0 then
if TimerGetRemaining(EE[ID])<=0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=.5*ln[ID]then
if KE[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(sg)
call TriggerExecute(Tg)
else
call TriggerExecute(sg)
endif
endif
elseif TimerGetRemaining(EE[ID])<=0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=3.*ln[ID]then
if KE[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(sg)
call TriggerExecute(tg)
else
call TriggerExecute(sg)
endif
endif
if qn[ID]>0 then
if TimerGetRemaining(AE[ID])<=0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=2*ln[ID]then
if KE[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(Ug)
call TriggerExecute(yg)
else
call TriggerExecute(Ug)
endif
endif
elseif ii[ID]>0 and TimerGetRemaining(AE[ID])<=0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=2.*ln[ID]then
if KE[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(Ug)
call TriggerExecute(Yg)
else
call TriggerExecute(Ug)
endif
endif
if ai[ID]>0 and TimerGetRemaining(NE[ID])<=0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1.5*ln[ID]then
if KE[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(zg)
call TriggerExecute(vG)
else
call TriggerExecute(zg)
endif
endif
if di[ID]>0 and TimerGetRemaining(bE[ID])<=0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1.5*ln[ID]then
if KE[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(eG)
call TriggerExecute(oG)
else
call TriggerExecute(eG)
endif
endif
if mi[ID]>0 and TimerGetRemaining(BE[ID])<=0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1.1*ln[ID]then
if KE[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(rG)
call TriggerExecute(aG)
else
call TriggerExecute(rG)
endif
endif
if Ui[ID]>0 and TimerGetRemaining(hE[ID])<=0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1.1*ln[ID]then
if KE[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(nG)
call TriggerExecute(EG)
else
call TriggerExecute(nG)
endif
endif
if Ua[ID]>0 and TimerGetRemaining(HE[ID])<=0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1*ln[ID]then
if KE[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(XG)
call TriggerExecute(RG)
else
call TriggerExecute(XG)
endif
endif
endfunction

function jyx takes nothing returns nothing
local unit T=GetTriggerUnit()
local unit D=GetEventDamageSource()
local integer ID=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(D)))
if ri[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=5. then
call TriggerExecute(rh)
endif
if ii[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=3. then
call TriggerExecute(ih)
endif
if fO[ID]then
call Vov(uv[ID],T,mi[ID]*I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*170.*Ar[ID],1,1,0,"","")
endif
if qn[ID]>0 and GetRandomReal(0,'d')<=1.5 and fO[ID]then
call TriggerExecute(Ih)
endif
set D=null
set T=null
endfunction
function jzx takes nothing returns nothing
local unit T=GetTriggerUnit()
local unit D=GetEventDamageSource()
local integer ID=(1+GetPlayerId(GetOwningPlayer(D)))
if Ui[ID]>0 and(BlzGetUnitAbilityCooldownRemaining((D),('A0Y9')))==0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((D),('A0Y9'),((59*sV[ID])*1.))
call TriggerExecute(dh)
endif
if hj[ID]then
call Vov(uv[ID],T,((Ui[ID]*$514)+(Ui[ID]*I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*($514*Hj[ID])))*Ar[ID],1,1,0,"","")
endif
if di[ID]>0 and(BlzGetUnitAbilityCooldownRemaining((D),('A0Y7')))==0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((D),('A0Y7'),((30*sV[ID])*1.))
call TriggerExecute(ch)
endif
if IsUnitInGroup(T,Gj[ID])then
call Vov(Ai[ID],T,((di[ID]*500)+(di[ID]*I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*(500*Hj[ID])))*Ar[ID],1,1,0,"","")
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0Y4')>0 and ri[ID]>0 and(BlzGetUnitAbilityCooldownRemaining((D),('A0Y4')))==0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((D),('A0Y4'),((5*sV[ID])*1.))
call TriggerExecute(Nh)
endif
if GetUnitAbilityLevel(D,'A0Y5')>0 and ii[ID]>0 and(BlzGetUnitAbilityCooldownRemaining((D),('A0Y5')))==0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((D),('A0Y5'),(($F*sV[ID])*1.))
call TriggerExecute(bh)
endif
if ai[ID]>0 and(BlzGetUnitAbilityCooldownRemaining((D),('A0Y6')))==0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((D),('A0Y6'),((60*sV[ID])*1.))
call TriggerExecute(Bh)
endif
if gj[ID]then
call Vov(uv[ID],T,((ai[ID]*300)+(ai[ID]*I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*(300*Hj[ID])))*Ar[ID],1,1,0,"","")
endif
if mi[ID]>0 and(BlzGetUnitAbilityCooldownRemaining((D),('A0Y8')))==0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((D),('A0Y8'),((30*sV[ID])*1.))
call TriggerExecute(Ch)
endif
if Ua[ID]>0 and(BlzGetUnitAbilityCooldownRemaining((D),('A0YA')))==0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((D),('A0YA'),((60*sV[ID])*1.))
call TriggerExecute(Dh)
endif
if ha[ID]>0 and(BlzGetUnitAbilityCooldownRemaining((D),('A0YB')))==0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((D),('A0YB'),((60*sV[ID])*1.))
call TriggerExecute(fh)
endif
if jj[ID]then
set Jj[ID]=Jj[ID]+1
if Jj[ID]==$F then
set Jj[ID]=0
call iMv(uv[ID],((I2R(ha[ID])*$FA0)+(I2R(GetHeroInt(D,true))*ha[ID]*($FA0*Hj[ID])))*Ar[ID],640,GetUnitX(D),GetUnitY(D))
if not La then
call DestroyEffect(AddSpecialEffect("Crusader SkillSQC.mdx",GetUnitX(T),GetUnitY(T)))
endif
endif
endif
if qn[ID]>0 and(BlzGetUnitAbilityCooldownRemaining((D),('A0YC')))==0 then
call BlzStartUnitAbilityCooldown((D),('A0YC'),((60*sV[ID])*1.))
call TriggerExecute(Fh)
endif
set D=null
set T=null
endfunction

function j1x takes nothing returns boolean
local integer xsv=xiv
local integer Eov=vv
set qm=true
set vv=xsv
set ev=vv
set Wm[xsv]=true
call TriggerExecute(Tm[xsv])
set qm=false
if Wm[xsv]then
call V9v(xsv)
endif
set vv=Eov
set ev=vv
call TimerStart(rp,0,false,function Eev)
return true
endfunction
function j2x takes nothing returns boolean
local integer xsv=xiv
set Tm[xsv]=null
set um[xsv]=null
set wm[xsv]=0
set Wm[xsv]=false
call xTv(xsv)
return true
endfunction
function j3x takes nothing returns boolean
local integer xsv=xiv
call V6v(Ep[xsv])
set Ep[xsv]=0
return true
endfunction
function j4x takes nothing returns boolean
local integer xsv=xiv
set Op=xsv
call TriggerEvaluate(Rp)
return true
endfunction
function j5x takes nothing returns boolean
local integer xsv=xiv
set Ap[xsv]=xsv
set Bq[xsv]=xsv
set cs[xsv]=xsv
set Dt[xsv]=xsv
set Gu[xsv]=xsv
set hw[xsv]=xsv
set Hy[xsv]=xsv
set jz[xsv]=xsv
set L0[xsv]=xsv
set Q2[xsv]=xsv
set t4[xsv]=xsv
set T6[xsv]=xsv
return true
endfunction
function j6x takes nothing returns boolean
local integer xsv=xiv
local integer i=0
if not T8[xsv]then
return true
endif
loop
if Uj[vrv[xsv]+i]!=null then
call RemoveLocation(Uj[vrv[xsv]+i])
set Uj[vrv[xsv]+i]=null
endif
if Yj[viv[xsv]+i]!=null then
call RemoveLocation(Yj[viv[xsv]+i])
set Yj[viv[xsv]+i]=null
endif
if eJ[vav[xsv]+i]!=null then
call RemoveLocation(eJ[vav[xsv]+i])
set eJ[vav[xsv]+i]=null
endif
if iJ[vnv[xsv]+i]!=null then
call RemoveLocation(iJ[vnv[xsv]+i])
set iJ[vnv[xsv]+i]=null
endif
if EJ[vVv[xsv]+i]!=null then
call RemoveLocation(EJ[vVv[xsv]+i])
set EJ[vVv[xsv]+i]=null
endif
if IJ[vEv[xsv]+i]!=null then
call RemoveLocation(IJ[vEv[xsv]+i])
set IJ[vEv[xsv]+i]=null
endif
set SJ[u8[xsv]+i]=false
set UJ[U8[xsv]+i]=false
set YJ[w8[xsv]+i]=false
set ek[W8[xsv]+i]=false
set ik[y8[xsv]+i]=false
set Ek[Y8[xsv]+i]=false
set Ik[z8[xsv]+i]=0
set Bk[Z8[xsv]+i]=0
set Dk[vvv[xsv]+i]=0
set Gk[vev[xsv]+i]=0
set Jk[vxv[xsv]+i]=0
set Lk[vov[xsv]+i]=0
set Pk[vbv[xsv]+i]=.0
set Sk[vBv[xsv]+i]=.0
set Uk[vcv[xsv]+i]=.0
set Yk[vCv[xsv]+i]=.0
set eK[vdv[xsv]+i]=.0
set iK[vDv[xsv]+i]=.0
set EK[vfv[xsv]+i]=null
set IK[vFv[xsv]+i]=null
set BK[vgv[xsv]+i]=null
set DK[vGv[xsv]+i]=null
set GK[vhv[xsv]+i]=null
set JK[vHv[xsv]+i]=null
set LK[vjv[xsv]+i]=null

function JEx takes nothing returns boolean
local integer xsv=xiv
call TriggerRemoveAction(hm[xsv],Jm[xsv])
if Gm[xsv]!=null then
call RemoveRegion(Gm[xsv])
endif
call RemoveSavedInteger(mm,0,GetHandleId(hm[xsv]))
call iGv(hm[xsv])
call iGv(Hm[xsv])
set lm[Km[xsv]]=lm[xsv]
set Km[lm[xsv]]=Km[xsv]
return true
endfunction

function JXx takes nothing returns boolean
local integer xsv=x8v()
call SaveInteger(mm,0,GetHandleId(hm[xsv]),xsv)
set e4v=xsv
return true
endfunction
function JOx takes nothing returns boolean
call aSv(e5v)
return true
endfunction
function JRx takes nothing returns boolean
call auv(e5v,xvv)
return true
endfunction
function JIx takes nothing returns boolean
call a2v(e5v,e9v)
return true
endfunction
function JAx takes nothing returns boolean
call a4v(e5v,xev)
return true
endfunction
function JNx takes nothing returns boolean
call a6v(e5v,xxv,xov,xrv)
return true
endfunction
function Jbx takes nothing returns boolean
call nvv(e5v,e6v,e7v)
return true
endfunction

call nov(e5v)
return true

return true

return true

return true

call nnv(e5v)
return true
endfunction
function Jfx takes nothing returns boolean
call nVv(e5v,e8v,e9v)
return true
endfunction
function JFx takes nothing returns boolean
local integer i=0
local integer o=-1
local boolean oops=false
if(s)then
return true
else
set s=true
endif
set P=InitHashtable()
loop
exitwhen(i==M)
set egv[i]=CreateTimer()
call SaveInteger(P,0,GetHandleId((egv[i])),(Q))
set i=i+1
endloop
set q=M
return true
endfunction
function Jgx takes nothing returns boolean
set e4v=aPv(e5v)
return true
endfunction

call TriggerAddCondition(ekv,Condition(function j1x))
